me=\"s\" placeholder=\"Search games...\" required=\"\">\n                <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"post_type\" value=\"game\">\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"wp-block-search__button has-icon\" aria-label=\"Search\">\n                    <svg class=\"search-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><path d=\"M13 5c-3.3 0-6 2.7-6 6 0 1.4.5 2.7 1.3 3.7l-3.8 3.8 1.1 1.1 3.8-3.8c1 .8 2.3 1.3 3.7 1.3 3.3 0 6-2.7 6-6S16.3 5 13 5zm0 10.5c-2.5 0-4.5-2-4.5-4.5s2-4.5 4.5-4.5 4.5 2 4.5 4.5-2 4.5-4.5 4.5z\"></path></svg>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n        </form>\n        <button id=\"wg-close-mobile-search\" class=\"wg-icon-button wg-mobile-search-close\" aria-label=\"Close Search\">\n            <span class=\"dashicons dashicons-no-alt\"></span>\n        </button>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener(\'DOMContentLoaded\', function() {\n            var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);\n            var q = urlParams.get(\'s\');\n            if (q) {\n                var inputs = document.querySelectorAll(\'.wg-header-search-input\');\n                inputs.forEach(function(input) { input.value = q; });\n            }\n\n            // Mobile search overlay toggle\n            var mobileSearchBtn = document.getElementById(\'wg-mobile-search-btn\');\n            var closeSearchBtn = document.getElementById(\'wg-close-mobile-search\');\n            var searchOverlay = document.getElementById(\'wg-mobile-search-overlay\');\n\n            if (mobileSearchBtn && searchOverlay) {\n                mobileSearchBtn.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n                    searchOverlay.classList.add(\'is-active\');\n                    var input = searchOverlay.querySelector(\'input[type=\"search\"]\');\n                    if(input) input.focus();\n                });\n            }\n\n            if (closeSearchBtn && searchOverlay) {\n                closeSearchBtn.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n                    searchOverlay.classList.remove(\'is-active\');\n                });\n            }\n        });\n    </script>\n<!-- /wp:html --></header>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Header','','publish','closed','closed','','header','','','2026-06-30 08:52:00','2026-06-30 08:52:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/header/',0,'wp_template_part','',0),(71,1,'2026-06-30 09:16:14','2026-06-30 09:16:14','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Welcome to MiniWebGames.com!</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Mission </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">At MiniWebGames, we believe that entertainment should be instant, relaxing, and accessible to everyone. In a world full of complex gaming setups and endless app downloads, our mission is simple: to provide a clean, lightning-fast platform where you can enjoy high-quality browser games with just a single click. Whether you are looking for a quick brain workout during your lunch break or a relaxing melodic journey after a long day, you have found the right place.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What We Offer: A Hub of Interactive Entertainment </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Our platform features a carefully curated and constantly growing collection of HTML5 games, designed for players of all skill levels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">A core highlight of our catalog is our <strong>Music Games</strong> hub. We celebrate the colorful world of rhythm and sound through interactive browser experiences. From fast-paced beat challenges that test your reaction speed to relaxing melody creation tools, we gather music-focused entertainment for everyone. You can immerse yourself in rhythm games with synchronized patterns, explore music-creation tools for custom sound combinations, or enjoy instrument simulators—all bringing an energetic and creative atmosphere directly to your screen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beyond music, our library is continuously expanding with fresh adventures, classic puzzles, and innovative indie projects to ensure every visit offers something new to discover.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Power of HTML5: Play Instantly, Everywhere </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">We leverage the true power of modern HTML5 technology to put the player first. What does this mean for you?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Zero Downloads:</strong> There is no need to endure long waiting times or apply through app stores. Click a game, and the fun begins instantly.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Cross-Device Compatibility:</strong> Whether you are browsing on a classic desktop, a macOS laptop, a tablet, or a smartphone, our games adapt flawlessly to your screen.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Lightweight Performance:</strong> Hosted on high-speed servers, our games ensure smooth controls, fast load times, and responsive gameplay across all modern browsers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Promise to You </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">We are committed to maintaining a user-friendly environment. Our team frequently updates the game collections, introduces seasonal events, and ensures simple navigation for faster discovery. We focus on catchy soundtracks, vibrant visuals, and, most importantly, a safe and enjoyable web experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get in Touch </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Your feedback helps us grow! If you have any questions, suggestions, or just want to say hello, feel free to reach out to us at: <strong>thanhlong.bkpro@.com</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Join the fascinating world of MiniWebGames today. It’s time to explore new sounds, challenge your reflexes, and discover exciting digital worlds right now!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2026-07-08 02:09:34','2026-07-08 02:09:34','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?page_id=71',0,'page','',0),(72,1,'2026-06-30 09:16:14','2026-06-30 09:16:14','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>About Us</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2026-06-30 09:16:14','2026-06-30 09:16:14','',71,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=72',0,'revision','',0),(73,1,'2026-06-30 09:16:26','2026-06-30 09:16:26','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">We\'d Love to Hear From You!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Whether you need assistance, have a suggestion for a new game, or just want to share your feedback about our platform, our team is always ready to help. At MiniWebGames, we are committed to providing you with the best, interruption-free gaming experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Reach Us</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Email Support:</strong> For general inquiries, technical support, or partnership proposals, please drop us a line at <strong>thanhlong.bkpro@gmail.com</strong>. We make every effort to review all emails and reply within 24-48 business hours.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Connect With Us:</strong> Want to see our latest game updates, high-score challenges, or relaxing gameplay videos? Join our growing community on our social channels:<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Youtube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@miniwebgames\">https://www.youtube.com/@miniwebgames</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61591336000883\">https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61591336000883</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/miniwebgames/\">https://www.instagram.com/miniwebgames/</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Threads: <a href=\"https://www.threads.com/@miniwebgames\">https://www.threads.com/@miniwebgames</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tiktok: <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@miniwebgames\">https://www.tiktok.com/@miniwebgames</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>X (Twitter): <a href=\"https://x.com/MiniWebGames\">https://x.com/MiniWebGames</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Send Us a Message directly </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[contact-form-7 id=\"f02882b\" title=\"Contact Form\"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Important Note for Users: </strong>We value your privacy. Any information you submit through this form or via email will strictly be used to assist you and will not be shared with third parties.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Contact Us','','publish','closed','closed','','contact-us','','','2026-07-08 02:22:57','2026-07-08 02:22:57','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?page_id=73',0,'page','',0),(74,1,'2026-06-30 09:16:26','2026-06-30 09:16:26','','Contact Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','73-revision-v1','','','2026-06-30 09:16:26','2026-06-30 09:16:26','',73,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=74',0,'revision','',0),(77,1,'2026-06-30 09:17:25','2026-06-30 09:17:25','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who we are</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Our website address is: http://miniwebgames.local.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Comments</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Media</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cookies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Embedded content from other websites</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who we share your data with</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How long we retain your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What rights you have over your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Where your data is sent</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','3-revision-v1','','','2026-06-30 09:17:25','2026-06-30 09:17:25','',3,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=77',0,'revision','',0),(78,1,'2026-06-30 09:18:12','2026-06-30 09:18:12','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 8, 2026</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Welcome to <strong>MiniWebGames</strong> (\"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\"). These Terms of Service (\"Terms\") govern your access to and use of <strong><a href=\"https://miniwebgames.com\">https://miniwebgames.com</a></strong> (\"Website\"). By using our Website, you agree to these Terms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Use of the Website</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">MiniWebGames provides free browser-based games for personal, non-commercial entertainment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">You agree to use the Website only for lawful purposes and in a manner that does not interfere with the operation of the Website or the experience of other users.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. User Account