:18','2026-07-02 06:12:18','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HTML5 Game Top Sprunki Phases</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','HTML5 Game Top Sprunki Phases','','publish','open','open','','html5-game-top-sprunki-phases','','','2026-07-02 06:12:59','2026-07-02 06:12:59','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=129',0,'post','',0),(130,1,'2026-07-02 06:12:18','2026-07-02 06:12:18','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HTML5 Game Top Sprunki Phases</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','HTML5 Game Top Sprunki Phases','','inherit','closed','closed','','129-revision-v1','','','2026-07-02 06:12:18','2026-07-02 06:12:18','',129,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=130',0,'revision','',0),(132,1,'2026-07-02 07:16:44','2026-07-02 07:16:44','','sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki','','','2026-07-02 07:16:44','2026-07-02 07:16:44','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(134,1,'2026-07-02 07:17:08','2026-07-02 07:17:08','','music','','inherit','open','closed','','music','','','2026-07-02 07:17:08','2026-07-02 07:17:08','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/music.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(137,1,'2026-07-02 08:01:11','2026-07-02 08:01:11','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Game - Play Free Online Music Creation Game</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Game</strong> is a creative browser-based music game where every sound you choose becomes part of an original song. Instead of chasing high scores or defeating enemies, you\'ll build rhythmic compositions by mixing beats, melodies, vocals, and effects. With two distinct themes—including a darker horror-inspired mode—the game encourages experimentation and rewards creativity, making every session sound completely different from the last.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Overview</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Music, Rhythm, Creative, Casual</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Platform</strong></td><td>Web Browser (HTML5)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Drag and combine sound icons to create custom music tracks</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Main Objective</strong></td><td>Mix different character sounds to compose unique songs and discover new musical combinations</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki transforms music creation into an interactive game. Every character represents a unique sound element, such as percussion, melody, vocals, or special effects. Drag a sound icon onto a character to activate it, then continue adding more performers until your mix feels complete.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Up to seven sounds can play together at once, allowing you to create anything from simple rhythms to layered musical arrangements. There is no correct order, no required combinations, and no time pressure. Experimenting with different sound sets is the heart of the gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game also features two different musical styles:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Normal Mode</strong> offers colorful visuals and upbeat sounds for cheerful compositions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Horror Mode</strong> changes the atmosphere completely with eerie visuals, distorted effects, and unsettling audio that creates darker musical pieces.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">You can mute individual performers, replace sounds, or rebuild your composition whenever inspiration strikes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>PC</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Drag and drop sound icons onto characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Left Click:</strong> Activate, remove, or swap sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Mobile</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Tap and drag sound icons</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Tap characters to change or remove sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">No keyboard controls are required.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Create unlimited original music combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Two completely different themes: Normal and Horror.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix beats, melodies, vocals, and sound effects freely.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple drag-and-drop controls suitable for all skill levels.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Instantly edit your composition without restarting.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Distinctive characters with their own musical identities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Relaxing gameplay with no timers or failure conditions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips &amp; Tricks</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with a beat before adding melodies and vocals for a balanced track.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Test unexpected character combinations—you may discover your favorite sound.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mute feature to highlight specific instruments during your mix.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try using fewer active characters to create cleaner, more memorable rhythms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Switch to Horror Mode for entirely different audio textures and creative inspiration.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why You\'ll Love This Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki stands out because it treats every player like a music producer rather than a competitor. The open-ended design means there are countless ways to build songs, and every combination produces something unique. Whether you enjoy relaxing creativity or experimenting with unusual soundscapes, it\'s easy to lose yourself while creating your own musical style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">If you enjoy Sprunki, you may also like:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Incredibox</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Friday Night Funkin\'</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 5</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Snow Day</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Is Sprunki free to play?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Yes. Sprunki can be played directly in your browser without purchasing the game.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Do I need musical experience?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Not at all. The interface is designed so anyone can create enjoyable music through simple drag-and-drop actions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the difference between Normal Mode and Horror Mode?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Normal Mode focuses on upbeat visuals and cheerful sounds, while Horror Mode replaces them with darker graphics and haunting audio effects.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Can I replay the game with different results?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Absolutely. Since you can mix sounds in countless ways, every session can produce a completely different musical composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki is a refreshing music creation game that blends creativity with simple gameplay. Instead of following strict objectives, you\'re encouraged to experiment with sounds and discover your own musical ideas. With colorful visuals, a spooky alternate mode, and endless combinations to explore, it\'s an enjoyable browser game for anyone who loves interactive music.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Game Original','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-game','','','2026-07-03 01:26:43','2026-07-03 01:26:43','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=137',0,'game','',0),(138,1,'2026-07-02 07:49:57','2026-07-02 07:49:57','','Sprunki Game','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-game-2','','','2026-07-03 01:26:43','2026-07-03 01:26:43','',137,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-game.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(146,1,'2026-07-03 01:35:11','2026-07-03 01:35:11','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Chilly Guy: Sprunki</strong> blends relaxing music creation with light progression, making every session both calming and rewarding. As you build rhythmic compositions, you\'ll unlock fresh environments and musical styles that transform the atmosphere of the game. Simple controls make it easy to jump in, while the steady flow of new themes and collectibles encourages you to keep experimenting with different sounds and melodies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":150,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/chilly-guy-sprunki-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-150\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Music, Rhythm, Casual, HTML5</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Objective</strong></td><td>Collect hearts to unlock new musical worlds and create enjoyable sound combinations.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Interact with characters to produce music, earn hearts, and explore additional themes as you progress.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The adventure begins in a bright grassy landscape filled with cheerful tunes. As you gather hearts, additional music themes become available, introducing new visual settings and different audio styles. Along the way, you can continue experimenting with sounds while discovering new creative possibilities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Playing Chilly Guy: Sprunki is straightforward, making it suitable for both casual players and music enthusiasts.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse or touchscreen to interact with Chill Guy and the available musical elements. Every successful interaction contributes toward collecting hearts, which serve as the game\'s progression system. As your collection grows, new environments and musical themes become accessible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Besides unlocking content, the game also lets you capture memorable musical moments to revisit or share later. The main objective is to continue expanding your collection of hearts while creating enjoyable musical arrangements throughout each stage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Click interactive elements and characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mobile:</strong> Tap the screen to interact.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Relaxing music gameplay with accessible controls.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlockable themes featuring unique visual and audio styles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Heart collection system that rewards steady progression.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Record your favorite musical moments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Browser-based gameplay with no installation required.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Prioritize actions that generate hearts automatically to unlock new content more quickly.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Playing with headphones makes it easier to appreciate the different layers of each musical arrangement.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Save recordings of your favorite sessions so you can compare different sound combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Spend time experimenting with newly unlocked themes, as each offers a distinct musical atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Game</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 5</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Incredibox</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Chilly Guy: Sprunki offers a relaxing alternative to traditional rhythm games by focusing on creativity instead of competition. Unlockable music themes, simple controls, and satisfying progression make it an enjoyable browser game for players who like experimenting with sounds while discovering new musical environments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Chilly Guy: Sprunki','','publish','open','closed','','chilly-guy-sprunki','','','2026-07-03 01:37:48','2026-07-03 01:37:48','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=146',0,'game','',0),(150,1,'2026-07-03 01:33:15','2026-07-03 01:33:15','','chilly-guy-sprunki-2','','inherit','open','closed','','chilly-guy-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-03 01:33:15','2026-07-03 01:33:15','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/chilly-guy-sprunki-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(151,1,'2026-07-03 01:33:15','2026-07-03 01:33:15','','Chilly Guy: Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','chilly-guy-sprunki-3','','','2026-07-03 01:35:11','2026-07-03 01:35:11','',146,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/chilly-guy-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(154,1,'2026-07-03 01:44:59','2026-07-03 01:44:59','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 5</strong> expands the familiar music-mixing formula with fresh locations, collectible progression, and interactive sound design. Every rhythm you create helps unlock new environments, each featuring its own atmosphere and visual style. Instead of following a fixed path, you\'re encouraged to experiment with different sound combinations while gradually opening new areas to explore. The result is a relaxing yet rewarding browser game that keeps every session feeling different.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Music, Rhythm, Casual, HTML5</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Objective</strong></td><td>Create music, collect hearts, and unlock new themed environments.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Mix sounds, interact with the guide character, and progress by earning hearts through musical creations.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game begins in a colorful landscape where every sound contributes to your progress. As your heart collection grows, additional locations become available, introducing darker scenery and entirely new moods. Each environment offers a fresh backdrop for experimenting with musical arrangements without changing the game\'s easy-to-learn mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 5 uses simple point-and-click controls that allow you to focus on creativity instead of complicated mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click or tap the available characters and sound elements to build your musical composition. The friendly sun character also provides another way to collect hearts, helping you unlock new stages more quickly. Up to seven sounds can be active simultaneously, giving you plenty of freedom to layer beats, melodies, and effects.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The main objective is to earn enough hearts to access every available theme while creating enjoyable musical mixes. You can also use the built-in photo feature to capture memorable moments from your favorite sessions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Click characters and interactive objects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mobile:</strong> Tap the screen to activate sounds and collect hearts.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Three unlockable environments with distinct visual themes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Heart-based progression system that rewards continued play.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Layer multiple sounds to create original music.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Built-in snapshot feature for saving memorable moments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Browser-based gameplay with quick loading and simple controls.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Activate multiple sound sources to collect hearts more efficiently.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Interact with the guide character whenever possible for additional progress.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try different sound combinations before unlocking the next environment to discover unique musical styles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Capture screenshots of your favorite compositions so you can recreate them later.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Game</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Incredibox: Kochari</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Chilly Guy: Sprunki</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 5 combines creative music-making with steady progression, giving players a reason to keep experimenting long after the first song. Unlockable environments, intuitive controls, and flexible sound mixing make it an enjoyable HTML5 game for anyone who likes rhythm-based creativity without competitive pressure.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Phase 5','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-5','','','2026-07-03 01:44:59','2026-07-03 01:44:59','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=154',0,'game','',0),(155,1,'2026-07-03 01:40:24','2026-07-03 01:40:24','','Sprunki Phase 5','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-5-2','','','2026-07-03 01:44:59','2026-07-03 01:44:59','',154,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-5-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(156,1,'2026-07-03 01:50:22','2026-07-03 01:50:22','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Parasites</strong> takes the familiar music-mixing gameplay of the Sprunki series and places it inside a bleak, corrupted world. Instead of bright melodies and cheerful visuals, you\'ll create haunting soundtracks surrounded by abandoned landscapes and infected characters. The contrast between creative freedom and unsettling atmosphere gives this browser game a distinct personality, making each musical composition feel like part of a larger story.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Music, Rhythm, Horror, HTML5</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Objective</strong></td><td>Combine character sounds to compose unique tracks while exploring a parasite-ravaged world.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Drag sound icons onto characters, layer different audio elements, and experiment with dark musical arrangements.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game\'s setting revolves around a once-thriving world that has been overtaken by a mysterious parasite. The infection has transformed both the environment and its inhabitants, replacing cheerful performances with eerie vocals, distorted effects, and unsettling rhythms. Every new combination changes the mood of your composition, encouraging creative experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Parasites keeps its controls simple while offering plenty of room for creativity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose a sound from the available collection, then drag it onto one of the characters to activate that audio layer. Each character can hold a single sound at a time, allowing you to build your composition piece by piece. Mix percussion, melodies, vocals, and special effects until you create a soundtrack that matches the game\'s haunting atmosphere.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">For players seeking a more intense experience, Dark Mode introduces even stranger visuals and more chaotic sound combinations, creating an entirely different musical mood.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Drag and drop sound icons onto characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mobile:</strong> Tap and drag sounds to assign them to performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dark post-apocalyptic setting with horror-inspired visuals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag-and-drop music creation that is easy to learn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Distinctive infected characters with unique sound effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Optional Dark Mode for an even more unsettling atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless possibilities for creating original musical compositions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with rhythmic sounds before adding melodies and effects to build a balanced composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace individual sounds instead of restarting to quickly test new combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Explore Dark Mode after learning the standard sound library to appreciate the dramatic audio changes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix contrasting sound types to create more memorable and layered tracks.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Game</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki New Version</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 5</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Parasites offers a darker take on interactive music creation without changing the accessible gameplay that made the series popular. The unsettling world, eerie soundtrack, and creative freedom combine to deliver a memorable browser game for players who enjoy horror themes and experimental rhythm experiences.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Parasites','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-parasites','','','2026-07-03 01:50:22','2026-07-03 01:50:22','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=156',0,'game','',0),(157,1,'2026-07-03 01:47:17','2026-07-03 01:47:17','','sprunki-parasites-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-parasites-2','','','2026-07-03 01:47:17','2026-07-03 01:47:17','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-parasites-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(158,1,'2026-07-03 01:47:18','2026-07-03 01:47:18','','Sprunki Parasites','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-parasites-3','','','2026-07-03 01:50:22','2026-07-03 01:50:22','',156,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-parasites.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(159,1,'2026-07-03 01:56:30','2026-07-03 01:56:30','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki New Version</strong> refreshes the classic music-making formula with expanded creative tools, flexible playback speeds, and multiple visual themes. Every session lets you experiment with rhythm in your own way, whether you prefer relaxing melodies or darker soundscapes. From adjusting the tempo to layering every available sound into one performance, this browser game offers plenty of opportunities to create original mixes without requiring any musical experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Music, Rhythm, Casual, HTML5</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Objective</strong></td><td>Create custom musical compositions by combining different sounds and exploring multiple game modes.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Select audio elements, assign them to characters, adjust playback speed, and build your own musical arrangements.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki New Version expands on the original gameplay by giving players greater control over how their music sounds. You can experiment with different tempos, switch between contrasting environments, and combine multiple sound layers to create anything from calm rhythms to energetic performances.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The gameplay is designed around simple drag-and-drop interactions, allowing you to focus on creativity rather than complicated mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose sounds from the available library and assign them to the performers. As more characters become active, your composition grows with additional beats, melodies, vocals, and effects. You can adjust the playback speed between slower and faster settings to hear how the same arrangement changes with tempo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Switch between the peaceful Steppe environment and the darker Hell Mode whenever you want a different atmosphere. For the fullest audio experience, activate Full Mix mode to hear every available sound playing together.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Click and drag sounds onto characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mobile:</strong> Tap and drag sound icons to assign them.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Adjustable playback speed from <strong>0.5x to 2.0x</strong>.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Full Mix mode that plays all available sound elements simultaneously.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Two contrasting visual themes with Normal and Hell environments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy drag-and-drop music creation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Browser-based gameplay with no download required.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start at normal speed before experimenting with faster or slower playback.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build your song one sound at a time to keep the mix balanced.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Compare the same composition in both visual modes for a different audio atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use Full Mix after creating your own arrangement to hear every sound working together.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Snow Day</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Parasites</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Game</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki New Version gives players more freedom to shape their music through flexible tempo controls, themed environments, and expanded sound options. Its intuitive interface makes experimenting enjoyable, while the added features encourage returning to create fresh compositions every time you play.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki New Version (Speed Change)','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-new-version-speed-change','','','2026-07-03 01:57:17','2026-07-03 01:57:17','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=159',0,'game','',0),(160,1,'2026-07-03 01:53:28','2026-07-03 01:53:28','','sprunki-new-version-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-new-version-2','','','2026-07-03 01:53:28','2026-07-03 01:53:28','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-new-version-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(161,1,'2026-07-03 01:53:29','2026-07-03 01:53:29','','Sprunki New Version','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-new-version','','','2026-07-03 01:56:30','2026-07-03 01:56:30','',159,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-new-version.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(162,1,'2026-07-03 02:02:22','2026-07-03 02:02:22','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Snow Day</strong> brings a frosty twist to the popular music-mixing series with snow-covered scenery, holiday-inspired visuals, and an atmospheric soundtrack. Every character contributes a different musical element, allowing you to compose original tunes while exploring a charming winter setting. As you experiment with sound combinations, the game can shift from cozy seasonal vibes to a chilling alternate world, giving each play session a fresh musical mood.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":164,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-snow-day-3-1-1024x565.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-164\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Music, Rhythm, Casual, HTML5</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Objective</strong></td><td>Create unique musical compositions by combining character sounds in a winter-themed environment.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Assign sounds to characters, layer up to seven audio tracks, and experiment with different musical styles across two contrasting modes.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The snowy landscape serves as more than just a backdrop. Characters dressed for winter each contribute distinctive beats, melodies, vocals, or effects that can be mixed into your own soundtrack. Activating the darker game mode dramatically changes both the visuals and the audio, encouraging players to discover entirely new musical combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Snow Day uses intuitive drag-and-drop controls, making it easy to begin composing music within seconds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose characters and assign sounds to build your performance one layer at a time. You can activate as many as seven sound elements simultaneously, creating anything from simple rhythms to rich musical arrangements. Feel free to swap sounds, remove performers, or rebuild your composition whenever inspiration strikes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">When you\'re ready for a different atmosphere, switch to Dark Mode to hear familiar sounds transformed into eerie variations that match the game\'s colder, mysterious setting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Drag and drop sounds onto characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mobile:</strong> Tap and drag sound icons to assign them.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Winter-themed visuals filled with seasonal decorations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Layer up to seven sounds to create custom music.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dark Mode with alternate graphics and haunting audio.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unique characters featuring individual musical roles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Instant browser gameplay with no download required.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build your song around a steady rhythm before adding melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with different character combinations to discover unexpected harmonies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Compare the same arrangement in Normal Mode and Dark Mode to hear dramatic changes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Keep your mix balanced by replacing individual sounds instead of starting over.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Game</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki New Version</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 5</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Snow Day combines creative music-making with a memorable winter atmosphere that feels both relaxing and mysterious. The seasonal visuals, flexible sound mixing, and alternate Dark Mode offer plenty of reasons to keep experimenting, making it an enjoyable browser game for anyone who loves rhythm-based creativity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Snow Day','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-snow-day','','','2026-07-03 02:02:22','2026-07-03 02:02:22','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=162',0,'game','',0),(163,1,'2026-07-03 01:58:37','2026-07-03 01:58:37','','sprunki-snow-day-3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-snow-day-3','','','2026-07-03 01:58:37','2026-07-03 01:58:37','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-snow-day-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(164,1,'2026-07-03 01:58:38','2026-07-03 01:58:38','','Sprunki Snow Day','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-snow-day-2','','','2026-07-03 02:02:22','2026-07-03 02:02:22','',162,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-snow-day-3-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(165,1,'2026-07-03 02:08:00','2026-07-03 02:08:00','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 3</strong> transforms music creation into a dark, atmospheric adventure where every beat adds to an eerie soundtrack. Instead of colorful stages and cheerful melodies, this installment features unsettling visuals, monstrous performers, and haunting audio effects. Mixing sounds is still the core of the experience, but the horror-inspired presentation gives every composition a suspenseful edge, making it one of the most distinctive entries in the Sprunki series.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":166,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-3-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-166\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Category</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Genre</strong></td><td>Horror, Music, Rhythm, HTML5</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Objective</strong></td><td>Build haunting musical compositions by assigning sounds to creepy characters.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gameplay</strong></td><td>Drag musical icons onto performers, combine different audio layers, and experiment with dark-themed arrangements.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlike other Sprunki games that offer multiple environments, Phase 3 focuses entirely on a horror setting. Seven eerie characters stand ready to perform, each becoming part of your composition once assigned a sound. There are no scores or timers, allowing you to create music at your own pace while exploring different combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 3 is controlled entirely with your mouse or touchscreen, making it easy to jump into your first composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose a musical icon and drag it onto one of the available characters. Every icon can only be assigned once, so selecting the right performer for each sound requires a little planning. As more sounds are added, your composition grows into a complete horror-inspired soundtrack.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">If you want to revise your arrangement, simply remove a sound from a character and replace it with another. The objective is to experiment with different combinations until you\'ve created a chilling musical performance that matches the game\'s eerie atmosphere.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mouse:</strong> Drag and drop sound icons onto characters, then click to remove or replace them.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Mobile:</strong> Tap and drag sounds to assign them to performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Horror-themed visuals with creepy animated characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag-and-drop music creation that\'s easy to learn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unique sound library featuring eerie beats and effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Freedom to remix and replace sounds at any time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Save your favorite musical creations to revisit or share.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with rhythm sounds before adding melodies and effects for a smoother composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Since each sound icon can only be used once, choose placements carefully.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace individual sounds instead of rebuilding the entire track when experimenting.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Wear headphones to hear subtle background effects and layered audio more clearly.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Incredibox</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 5</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Parasites</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 3 combines creative music mixing with a chilling horror atmosphere that sets it apart from traditional rhythm games. The eerie characters, haunting sound library, and unrestricted gameplay encourage endless experimentation, making it a memorable browser game for players who enjoy spooky themes and original musical creations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Phase 3','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-3','','','2026-07-03 02:08:00','2026-07-03 02:08:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=165',0,'game','',0),(166,1,'2026-07-03 02:04:30','2026-07-03 02:04:30','','sprunki-phase-3-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-3-2','','','2026-07-03 02:04:30','2026-07-03 02:04:30','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-3-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(167,1,'2026-07-03 02:04:30','2026-07-03 02:04:30','','Sprunki Phase 3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-3-3','','','2026-07-03 02:08:00','2026-07-03 02:08:00','',165,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-3-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(168,1,'2026-07-03 02:17:56','2026-07-03 02:17:56','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Create Original Beats with a Creative Twist</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Music and imagination come together in <strong>Sprunki Retake</strong>, a browser-based rhythm game where every sound you choose shapes a brand-new performance. Instead of following preset songs, you\'re free to experiment with different characters, combine unique audio loops, and build your own musical masterpiece. A surprising horror-inspired mode adds another layer of creativity, making every session feel fresh and unpredictable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":169,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Retake</strong> is a casual music creation game inspired by interactive beat-making experiences. Rather than focusing on speed or reflexes, the game encourages players to explore sound combinations and compose original tracks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each character represents a different musical element, such as percussion, melodies, vocals, or special effects. Dragging characters onto the stage activates their sounds, allowing you to layer beats into a complete performance. Since every combination produces a different result, experimentation becomes the heart of the gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">One of the game\'s most memorable features is its hidden dark mode. Introducing the mysterious black character transforms the cheerful atmosphere into a haunting musical experience. The visuals become darker, character designs change dramatically, and the soundtrack shifts toward eerie rhythms without changing the core mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag characters onto the performance stage.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click a character to remove or replace it.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix different performers to create new musical arrangements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with an empty stage and gradually add musical performers. Every character contributes a unique sound, allowing you to build layered songs at your own pace. Swap performers freely until you discover a rhythm that matches your style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlocking the hidden horror-themed version introduces alternate visuals and darker sound effects, encouraging players to experiment with even more combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no traditional score or timer. Success comes from creating original music, discovering interesting sound combinations, and exploring every available character and theme.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Interactive drag-and-drop music creation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unique characters with individual sound effects</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Hidden horror mode with darker visuals and audio</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlimited beat combinations for endless creativity</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy browser gameplay with no musical experience required</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with percussion before adding melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace one character at a time to hear how each sound changes the composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try every available character to unlock new musical possibilities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Activate the black character to discover the game\'s hidden horror theme.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Listen carefully to balance your track instead of filling every slot immediately.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 3</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Incredibox</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Incredibox</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Retake</strong> offers a creative playground where players become music producers without needing any musical background. Its simple controls, endless sound combinations, and unexpected horror transformation make it a memorable browser game that rewards curiosity and experimentation every time you play.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Retake','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-retake','','','2026-07-03 03:04:24','2026-07-03 03:04:24','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=168',0,'game','',0),(169,1,'2026-07-03 02:14:43','2026-07-03 02:14:43','','sprunki-retake-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-2','','','2026-07-03 02:14:43','2026-07-03 02:14:43','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(170,1,'2026-07-03 02:14:44','2026-07-03 02:14:44','','Sprunki Retake','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-3','','','2026-07-03 02:17:56','2026-07-03 02:17:56','',168,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(171,1,'2026-07-03 02:27:42','2026-07-03 02:27:42','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Phase 4: Build Spooky Beats in a Halloween Music Adventure</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 4</strong> transforms music creation into a haunting performance filled with creepy visuals and energetic sound mixing. Set against a Halloween-inspired backdrop, the game lets you arrange original rock-inspired beats by combining different musical characters. Every new combination changes the rhythm, giving players complete freedom to experiment while enjoying an eerie atmosphere that stands out from traditional browser music games.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 4</strong> is a casual music-making game that blends rhythm, creativity, and horror-themed visuals into a simple browser experience. Instead of following pre-made songs, players create their own soundtracks by arranging performers with different musical roles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each available character represents a unique audio loop, including percussion, vocals, melodies, or special effects. By placing performers on the stage, you gradually build a complete musical composition. Since every sound can be mixed with others, countless musical combinations are possible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The Halloween setting gives the game its signature personality. Dark environments, glowing red lighting, and spooky character designs create an unsettling mood, while the music evolves from silence into a lively performance as your band comes together.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to select musical icons.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag sounds onto available performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remove or swap characters to change your composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with an empty stage and choose up to seven different musical performers. Each character immediately begins playing its assigned sound, adding another layer to your song. Continue experimenting by replacing beats and testing new arrangements until the performance sounds exactly the way you want.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no time limit, allowing you to focus entirely on creativity rather than speed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to compose an original music mix by combining different sounds and discovering the arrangements that best match your personal style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Halloween-inspired graphics with a spooky atmosphere</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag-and-drop music creation mechanics</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Up to seven active performers in one composition</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Large variety of beat and sound combinations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy-to-learn controls for quick music making</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with a steady rhythm before adding melodies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment by replacing one performer at a time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use all seven character slots to create fuller tracks.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay different combinations to discover hidden musical harmony.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Listen carefully to how each new sound affects the overall composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Parasites</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">FNF vs Huggy Wuggy</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Phase 4</strong> offers a refreshing blend of music creation and Halloween-inspired style. Its accessible controls, flexible beat mixing, and atmospheric presentation encourage players to create unique compositions without pressure. Every session becomes an opportunity to experiment with new sounds and build an original performance from scratch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Phase 4','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-4','','','2026-07-03 02:27:42','2026-07-03 02:27:42','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=171',0,'game','',0),(172,1,'2026-07-03 02:24:22','2026-07-03 02:24:22','','Sprunki Phase 4','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-4-2','','','2026-07-03 02:27:42','2026-07-03 02:27:42','',171,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-4-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(173,1,'2026-07-03 02:37:19','2026-07-03 02:37:19','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki OC: Compose Custom Beats with an Expanded Sound Library</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki OC</strong> builds on the familiar rhythm-mixing formula by introducing a larger collection of sounds and more opportunities for musical experimentation. Every session begins with a blank stage and endless creative potential, allowing players to arrange characters into original performances. With dozens of unique sound icons and an optional horror transformation, the game rewards curiosity and encourages players to discover fresh musical combinations through simple drag-and-drop gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":175,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-oc.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-175\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki OC</strong> is a casual browser music game focused on creativity rather than competition. Instead of completing levels or chasing high scores, players become composers by combining characters that each produce a distinct musical loop.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">One of the biggest additions in this version is its expanded sound collection. With <strong>36 musical icons</strong> available, players can mix percussion, melodies, vocals, and sound effects into countless original arrangements. Every change immediately affects the performance, making experimentation an important part of the experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game also includes a hidden horror mode that dramatically changes the atmosphere. Activating the special black icon transforms the cheerful stage into a darker performance with eerie visuals and haunting audio while keeping the same intuitive gameplay mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to drag musical icons onto performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click or replace characters to edit your composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Activate the black icon to enter the horror-themed version.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin by selecting sounds from the collection and assigning them to the seven available performers. As each character joins the stage, another musical layer is added to your composition. Continue swapping sounds, adjusting the lineup, and experimenting with different combinations until your mix feels complete.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Since there is no timer or fixed solution, every performance can be completely different from the last.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to create a unique musical arrangement by exploring different sound combinations and making the most of the game\'s expanded audio library.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Large collection of <strong>36 unique musical icons</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple drag-and-drop music creation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Seven performers available in every composition</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Hidden horror mode with alternate visuals and sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless combinations for personalized music mixes</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with rhythm sounds before adding melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Test different character arrangements to discover unexpected harmonies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace one sound at a time to hear subtle differences.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Save your favorite combinations by remembering your character order.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Explore horror mode to experience an entirely different musical atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 4</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Incredibox</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki OC</strong> expands the creative possibilities of the Sprunki series with a wider selection of sounds and flexible music-building tools. Its easy controls, replay value, and hidden horror theme make it an enjoyable choice for players who love experimenting with rhythm and creating original musical performances directly in their browser.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki OC','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-oc','','','2026-07-03 03:03:13','2026-07-03 03:03:13','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=173',0,'game','',0),(174,1,'2026-07-03 02:34:25','2026-07-03 02:34:25','','sprunki-oc-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-oc-2','','','2026-07-03 02:34:25','2026-07-03 02:34:25','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-oc-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(175,1,'2026-07-03 02:34:26','2026-07-03 02:34:26','','Sprunki OC','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-oc-3','','','2026-07-03 02:37:19','2026-07-03 02:37:19','',173,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-oc.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(176,1,'2026-07-03 02:41:52','2026-07-03 02:41:52','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Infected: Create Chilling Music in a Haunted Rhythm World</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dark visuals, mysterious characters, and creative beat mixing make <strong>Sprunki Infected</strong> a memorable addition to the Sprunki series. Instead of performing on a cheerful stage, you\'ll compose original tracks inside a world threatened by a strange infection. Every sound you assign changes both the music and the appearance of your performers, turning each session into a unique blend of rhythm, creativity, and horror-inspired storytelling.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Infected</strong> is a casual music creation game that reimagines the classic Sprunki formula with a darker atmosphere. Players experiment with sound loops by arranging musical performers, gradually building original compositions without time limits or scoring systems.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game features seven playable characters that can be customized using <strong>20 different musical icons</strong>. Each icon represents a distinct rhythm, melody, vocal effect, or instrumental sound. As characters receive new sounds, their appearance changes to match their musical role, creating a lively audiovisual performance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">A haunting setting sets this version apart. Shadowy skies, glowing red scenery, and unsettling animated details create constant tension while still leaving creativity at the center of the gameplay. Rather than fighting enemies directly, players use music to transform the stage and complete their own unique compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag musical icons onto characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace or remove sounds at any time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with different combinations until you\'re satisfied with your mix.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose sounds from the available collection and assign them to the seven performers on stage. Every added character introduces another musical layer, allowing your composition to grow naturally. Rearrange performers whenever you want to hear fresh rhythms or improve the overall balance of your track.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Because there are no strict objectives or penalties, players are free to experiment as much as they like.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The goal is to create an original music mix by combining sounds creatively while exploring the game\'s eerie atmosphere and visual transformations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Horror-themed environments with dark visual effects</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Twenty unique musical icons for creative mixing</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Seven customizable performers on every stage</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple drag-and-drop controls</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlimited replay value through endless sound combinations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build a steady rhythm before layering melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Swap individual sounds instead of changing the entire lineup at once.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try every musical icon to discover new combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Watch how character appearances change as new sounds are assigned.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay your favorite arrangements and refine them with small adjustments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 3</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 4</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Infected</strong> combines music creation with a suspenseful horror setting that feels different from traditional rhythm games. Its flexible gameplay, distinctive visual style, and wide range of sound combinations make it an entertaining browser game for players who enjoy experimenting with original musical creations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Infected','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-infected','','','2026-07-03 02:41:52','2026-07-03 02:41:52','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=176',0,'game','',0),(177,1,'2026-07-03 02:38:08','2026-07-03 02:38:08','','Sprunki Infected','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-infected-2','','','2026-07-03 02:41:52','2026-07-03 02:41:52','',176,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-infected-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(178,1,'2026-07-03 02:48:44','2026-07-03 02:48:44','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Remastered: Mix Original Tracks with Enhanced Visuals</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Remastered</strong> refreshes the classic music-making formula with polished visuals, improved sound design, and endless creative freedom. Instead of following a fixed soundtrack, you build your own by combining musical characters into unique performances. Every new arrangement creates a different rhythm, making the game an enjoyable playground for players who love experimenting with sound while uncovering a mysterious darker side hidden beneath its colorful appearance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":180,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-remastered-1024x566.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-180\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Remastered</strong> is a casual browser music game centered on creativity and experimentation. It modernizes the familiar Sprunki experience with upgraded graphics and smoother audio while preserving the simple drag-and-drop gameplay that made the original so popular.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to compose original songs by assigning different musical roles to a cast of animated performers. Each character contributes a unique beat, melody, vocal loop, or sound effect. As you continue adding performers, individual sounds blend into a complete musical arrangement that reflects your own style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beyond its cheerful presentation, the game also hides an alternate horror-themed mode. Activating the mysterious black character transforms the stage with darker visuals, unsettling sound effects, and redesigned performers, creating an entirely different atmosphere without changing the core mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to drag musical icons onto characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click performers to remove or replace sounds.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag the black character onto the stage to activate horror mode.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with an empty lineup and assign sounds to the available performers. Every character adds another musical layer, allowing your composition to grow piece by piece. Rearrange sounds, swap performers, and test different combinations until you create a mix that matches your creative vision.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There are no timers, scores, or failure conditions, so every session focuses entirely on experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The goal is to produce an original musical composition by exploring different sound combinations and discovering the creative possibilities hidden within every performer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Enhanced graphics and improved sound quality</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy drag-and-drop music creation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Countless combinations of beats and performers</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Hidden horror mode with alternate visuals and audio</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Relaxing gameplay without time limits or pressure</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with rhythm loops before adding melodies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Make small adjustments to hear how each sound changes the overall mix.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with unusual combinations to create unique tracks.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Explore the hidden horror mode for an entirely different experience.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay your favorite arrangements and refine them over time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Infected</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki OC</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Remastered</strong> successfully blends accessible music creation with polished presentation and impressive replay value. Its upgraded visuals, flexible sound mixing, and hidden horror transformation keep every performance feeling fresh, making it an excellent browser game for anyone who enjoys creating original music without complicated controls.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Remastered','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-remastered','','','2026-07-03 03:02:22','2026-07-03 03:02:22','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?po