small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Doors</strong> puts a playful spin on music creation by blending colorful visuals with quirky monster-inspired characters. Instead of following a scripted rhythm, players build original songs by combining animated performers, each contributing a unique sound. The unusual mix of cheerful environments and spooky character designs gives every composition its own personality, making the game entertaining for anyone who enjoys experimenting with music in a relaxed browser experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":186,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-doors.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-186\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Doors</strong> is a casual rhythm and music creation game where imagination is more important than precision. Players arrange animated characters on stage, layering sounds together to create original musical performances without worrying about scores or time limits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Every performer represents a different musical element, including beats, melodies, vocals, and sound effects. Assigning sounds to characters instantly changes both the audio and the visual performance, allowing songs to evolve naturally with every new addition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlike other Sprunki-inspired titles that separate cheerful and horror gameplay, <strong>Sprunki Doors</strong> combines both styles into a single experience. Bright backgrounds are filled with amusing monster characters, creating a playful contrast that gives the game its distinctive atmosphere.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag musical icons onto performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remove or replace sounds with a simple click.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with different character combinations to create new musical arrangements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose sounds from the available collection and place them on the performers waiting on stage. Each new character introduces another audio layer, gradually transforming a quiet scene into a lively musical performance. Continue adjusting your lineup until every sound works together in harmony.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Certain sound combinations may also trigger hidden animations, encouraging players to keep experimenting with new arrangements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to create your own original soundtrack by mixing different performers and discovering creative combinations that produce engaging musical performances.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Bright visuals paired with humorous monster characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag-and-drop music creation system</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unique combinations of beats, melodies, and vocals</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Hidden animations unlocked through specific sound mixes</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Relaxed gameplay with unlimited creative freedom</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build your composition one sound at a time instead of filling every slot immediately.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix rhythm and melody evenly for a more balanced performance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try unusual character combinations to uncover hidden animations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace individual sounds to fine-tune your music without starting over.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay your favorite arrangements and experiment with small changes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Remastered</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki OC</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Doors</strong> offers a refreshing take on browser-based music games by combining cheerful visuals, quirky monster designs, and creative sound mixing. With intuitive controls, countless musical possibilities, and hidden surprises to discover, it\'s an enjoyable choice for players who love building original songs at their own pace.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Doors','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-doors','','','2026-07-03 03:01:27','2026-07-03 03:01:27','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=184',0,'game','',0),(185,1,'2026-07-03 02:58:23','2026-07-03 02:58:23','','sprunki-doors1','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-doors1','','','2026-07-03 02:58:23','2026-07-03 02:58:23','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-doors1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(186,1,'2026-07-03 02:58:24','2026-07-03 02:58:24','','Sprunki Doors','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-doors-2','','','2026-07-03 03:01:27','2026-07-03 03:01:27','',184,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-doors.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(187,1,'2026-07-03 03:10:42','2026-07-03 03:10:42','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SprunkioPhobia: Create Haunting Soundtracks in a Horror Music Game</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>SprunkioPhobia</strong> combines music creation with psychological horror, offering a rhythm experience unlike traditional beat-making games. Instead of composing upbeat melodies on a cheerful stage, you\'ll arrange eerie sounds among unsettling characters and dark environments. Every musical choice shapes the atmosphere, making each composition feel like part of a suspenseful story while still giving players complete creative freedom to experiment with unique sound combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":189,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkiophobia-fix-1024x566.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-189\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>SprunkioPhobia</strong> is a casual music creation game with a strong horror theme. It keeps the familiar drag-and-drop mechanics of Sprunki-inspired games while introducing darker visuals, unsettling animations, and chilling audio effects that transform the mood of every performance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to create original musical compositions by assigning different sound icons to animated performers. Each character contributes a unique musical role, such as percussion, melodies, vocals, or atmospheric effects. Combining these elements produces layered tracks that can range from mysterious to intensely dramatic.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlike traditional rhythm games that focus on timing and accuracy, <strong>SprunkioPhobia</strong> emphasizes experimentation. Players are encouraged to rearrange performers, replace sounds, and refine their compositions until every element fits together perfectly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to drag musical icons onto the available characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click performers to remove or replace assigned sounds.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rearrange your lineup freely to explore different musical combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with an empty stage and select sounds from the available collection. Each icon can be assigned to a performer, adding another layer to your composition. As more characters join the performance, your soundtrack becomes richer and more immersive.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">You can continue adjusting your arrangement throughout the session, making it easy to experiment with different styles and discover new musical possibilities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The goal is to build an original horror-inspired soundtrack by combining musical elements creatively and producing a complete performance that matches your artistic vision.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dark horror-inspired visuals and atmospheric environments</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Creative drag-and-drop music composition</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Animated performers with unique musical roles</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Flexible sound combinations for endless experimentation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Relaxed gameplay with no timers or score requirements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with ambient sounds before adding stronger rhythms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace one musical icon at a time to hear subtle differences.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Balance melodies and effects to avoid overwhelming your mix.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with every available character to discover fresh combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay your favorite arrangements and refine them with small adjustments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"