World: Grow Musical Masterpieces in a Charming Garden</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki x Dandy’s World</strong> blends cheerful garden scenery with creative music-making, offering a refreshing twist on the classic Sprunki formula. Instead of managing crops, you\'ll organize animated performers and combine unique sound effects inspired by the whimsical world of Dandy. The relaxing daytime setting, hidden nighttime mode, and endless sound combinations make every performance feel fresh and rewarding.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":192,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-x-dandys-world-1024x566.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-192\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki x Dandy’s World</strong> is a casual browser music game that combines rhythm creation with colorful fantasy-inspired visuals. Players become the conductor of a lively cast of animated characters, arranging sounds to build original musical performances.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game features a collection of themed musical icons inspired by objects found throughout Dandy\'s world, including flowers, cups, ribbons, and other playful items. Each icon represents a different beat, melody, vocal effect, or instrumental sound. Assigning these sounds to performers gradually transforms a quiet garden into a vibrant musical stage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Although the game begins with a bright and welcoming atmosphere, it also includes a hidden nighttime mode. Activating the final icon changes the environment into a darker version filled with eerie visuals, ghostly characters, and unsettling sound effects, adding extra variety without changing the core gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to drag musical icons onto the seven performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click a character to remove or replace assigned sounds.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Activate the special nighttime icon to switch to the darker theme.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with an empty stage and select sounds from the available collection. Each performer contributes a unique musical layer, allowing you to build rich compositions one sound at a time. Continue experimenting by swapping icons and adjusting your lineup until your performance feels complete.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game encourages creativity, so there are no time limits or scoring systems to interrupt your music-making process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to compose an original soundtrack by combining different performers, discovering harmonious sound combinations, and exploring both the daytime and nighttime versions of the garden.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Colorful garden-themed music creation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unique sound icons inspired by Dandy\'s World</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Seven animated performers with customizable audio roles</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Hidden nighttime mode with spooky visuals and sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless combinations for creating original songs</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with rhythmic sounds before adding melodies and effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with different icon placements to discover new musical styles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Explore the nighttime mode for alternate visuals and soundscapes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace one performer at a time to fine-tune your composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay your favorite mixes and improve them with small adjustments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Incredibox: Kochari</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Chilly Guy: Sprunki</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Remastered</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki x Dandy’s World</strong> delivers a creative music experience wrapped in a charming fantasy setting. Its intuitive controls, imaginative sound library, and hidden nighttime transformation offer plenty of replay value, making it an excellent browser game for players who enjoy composing original music while exploring a playful and visually appealing world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki x Dandy’s World','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-x-dandys-world','','','2026-07-03 03:21:29','2026-07-03 03:21:29','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=190',0,'game','',0),(191,1,'2026-07-03 03:17:38','2026-07-03 03:17:38','','sprunki-x-dandys-world-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-x-dandys-world-2','','','2026-07-03 03:17:38','2026-07-03 03:17:38','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-x-dandys-world-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(192,1,'2026-07-03 03:17:40','2026-07-03 03:17:40','','Sprunki x Dandy’s World','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-x-dandys-world-3','','','2026-07-03 03:21:29','2026-07-03 03:21:29','',190,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-x-dandys-world.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(193,1,'2026-07-03 03:27:03','2026-07-03 03:27:03','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunked: Build Original Beats With a Creative Music Mixer</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Music games are at their best when they encourage creativity, and <strong>Sprunked</strong> does exactly that. Instead of following preset songs, you create your own sound by combining different musical elements and assigning them to animated performers. Every arrangement produces a unique rhythm, making each session feel fresh. With an easy drag-and-drop interface and an optional horror-themed variation, the game offers plenty of reasons to keep experimenting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":194,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunked-2.png1_.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunked</strong> is a browser-based music creation game that blends rhythm, creativity, and experimentation. Rather than chasing high scores, your goal is to assemble an entertaining musical performance by mixing vocals, beats, melodies, and effects.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">A group of seven performers serves as your virtual band. Each character can be assigned a different sound icon, allowing you to build layered compositions with countless possible combinations. Swapping sounds instantly changes the overall rhythm, encouraging players to test new arrangements until they discover a mix they enjoy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game also includes two distinct visual styles. Players begin in the standard mode, while a hidden trigger unlocks a darker horror version that changes the atmosphere without altering the core mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Playing Sprunked is simple and beginner-friendly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag a music icon onto one of the seven performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each assigned icon activates a unique musical sound or vocal effect.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue assigning sounds until every character joins the performance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click a performer to remove or replace their current sound.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with different combinations to create a personalized musical masterpiece.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag the special black icon onto a character to activate Horror Mode and discover an alternate presentation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no single correct arrangement. Success comes from creating a composition that sounds satisfying to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Create custom songs using simple drag-and-drop controls.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix dozens of unique sound icons into original compositions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build performances with seven animated band members.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Switch between Normal Mode and Horror Mode.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless replay value through countless sound combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with percussion before adding vocals and melodies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace one sound at a time to hear how each change affects the mix.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Balance different sound types instead of using similar effects together.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try Horror Mode after mastering the standard version for a fresh atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Save your favorite combinations by remembering the icon placements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Doors</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">SprunkioPhobia</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunked transforms music creation into a relaxing and creative browser game that rewards experimentation instead of perfection. Its accessible controls, flexible sound mixing, and optional horror theme make it enjoyable for both newcomers and players who love crafting original musical performances.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunked','','publish','open','closed','','sprunked','','','2026-07-03 03:27:03','2026-07-03 03:27:03','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=193',0,'game','',0),(194,1,'2026-07-03 03:24:00','2026-07-03 03:24:00','','sprunked-2.png1_','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunked-2-png1_','','','2026-07-03 03:24:00','2026-07-03 03:24:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunked-2.png1_.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(195,1,'2026-07-03 03:24:00','2026-07-03 03:24:00','','Sprunked','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunked-2','','','2026-07-03 03:27:03','2026-07-03 03:27:03','',193,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunked.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(196,1,'2026-07-03 03:31:28','2026-07-03 03:31:28','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Cats: Mix Adorable Feline Beats Into Your Own Music</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Not every music game needs flashy visuals or complicated mechanics to be entertaining. <strong>Sprunki Cats</strong> combines charming cat-inspired characters with interactive music creation, giving players a lighthearted way to build original tracks. Every sound you assign adds another layer to the performance, making each session different from the last. Whether you enjoy experimenting with rhythms or simply love cute animal-themed games, Sprunki Cats delivers a relaxing creative experience right in your browser.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Cats</strong> is a casual music-mixing game inspired by the popular Sprunki formula, but with a cast of playful feline performers. Instead of following a fixed soundtrack, you become the producer, selecting sounds and arranging them into a unique musical composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each cat represents a different musical role, such as percussion, vocals, melodies, or sound effects. By combining these audio elements, you can create everything from calm tunes to energetic beats. The game encourages creativity, allowing players to swap sounds freely until they discover a mix they enjoy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple controls and instant feedback make Sprunki Cats accessible for beginners while still providing enough variety for players who like experimenting with different musical styles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Creating music in Sprunki Cats only takes a few clicks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag sound icons onto the cat characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each assigned icon activates a unique beat, vocal, melody, or effect.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue adding sounds until every performer joins the band.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remove or replace sounds at any time to test new combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Keep experimenting to build a soundtrack that matches your own style.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There are no timers or score limits, so you can focus entirely on creating music at your own pace.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Cute cat-themed performers with expressive animations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy drag-and-drop music creation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Wide variety of beats, vocals, and sound effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Countless sound combinations for endless creativity.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Play instantly in your browser without downloads.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with a steady rhythm before adding melodies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix different sound categories to create balanced compositions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace individual sounds instead of rebuilding the entire track.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try unusual combinations—you may discover surprisingly catchy tunes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Listen carefully to how each new layer changes the overall rhythm.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunked</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 3</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Cats offers a fun twist on interactive music creation by replacing traditional performers with lovable feline musicians. Its accessible gameplay, charming visuals, and nearly endless sound combinations make it an excellent choice for players who enjoy casual creativity and browser-based rhythm games.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Cats','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-cats','','','2026-07-03 03:31:28','2026-07-03 03:31:28','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=196',0,'game','',0),(197,1,'2026-07-03 03:28:15','2026-07-03 03:28:15','','Sprunki Cats','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-cats-2','','','2026-07-03 03:31:28','2026-07-03 03:31:28','',196,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-cats.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(198,1,'2026-07-03 03:36:28','2026-07-03 03:36:28','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki\'s World: Create Original Songs in a Colorful Music Playground</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Creativity takes center stage in <strong>Sprunki\'s World</strong>, a browser-based music game where every sound is shaped by your imagination. Instead of following a fixed rhythm, you\'re free to arrange beats, melodies, and vocal effects into your own original compositions. The simple controls make it easy to jump in, while the wide variety of sound combinations keeps every performance fresh. With an optional horror-inspired mode, the game also offers a darker atmosphere for players looking to remix their music with a spooky twist.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":199,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkis-world2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-199\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki\'s World</strong> is a casual music creation game that combines rhythm, creativity, and interactive sound mixing. Rather than completing traditional levels, players build custom musical performances by assigning different audio effects to a group of animated characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each available sound icon introduces a new beat, melody, vocal, or special effect. Mixing these elements together creates a unique soundtrack that reflects your own style. Since every icon interacts differently with the others, even small adjustments can completely change the mood of your composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beyond its colorful presentation, the game also includes an alternate Horror Mode that transforms the visual atmosphere while preserving the same creative gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The controls are designed for quick experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag sound icons onto the performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Every assigned icon activates a different musical element.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Fill the group with a variety of sounds to build a complete performance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click a character to remove or replace its current sound.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Activate Horror Mode using the special black icon for an alternate visual experience.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no score or timer to beat. Your objective is simply to create music that sounds enjoyable and explore new combinations through experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Creative drag-and-drop music composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Large collection of unique beats, vocals, and sound effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Animated performers that react to every sound assignment.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Optional Horror Mode with a darker visual style.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless replay value through countless musical combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Listen to each sound individually before combining multiple effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build your rhythm first, then layer melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Don\'t hesitate to replace sounds until the mix feels balanced.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Explore every available icon to discover hidden musical possibilities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Switch to Horror Mode after creating a standard track to hear your composition in a new atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Doors</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Cats</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki 2</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki\'s World encourages players to experiment without pressure, making every session a new musical adventure. Its intuitive controls, creative freedom, and distinctive visual styles make it an excellent browser game for anyone who enjoys composing original beats and discovering fresh sound combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki\'s World','','publish','open','closed','','sprunkis-world','','','2026-07-03 03:46:44','2026-07-03 03:46:44','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=198',0,'game','',0),(199,1,'2026-07-03 03:33:27','2026-07-03 03:33:27','','sprunkis-world2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkis-world2','','','2026-07-03 03:33:27','2026-07-03 03:33:27','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkis-world2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(200,1,'2026-07-03 03:33:28','2026-07-03 03:33:28','','Sprunki\'s World','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkis-world-2','','','2026-07-03 03:36:28','2026-07-03 03:36:28','',198,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkis-world.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(201,1,'2026-07-03 03:42:04','2026-07-03 03:42:04','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki: Run Before It\'s Too Late! – Escape the Maze Before the Monster Finds You</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Quick decisions can mean the difference between freedom and failure in <strong>Sprunki: Run Before It\'s Too Late!</strong> This survival maze game combines exploration, resource collection, and constant danger into a fast-paced challenge. Every hallway hides either valuable cash or a deadly encounter, forcing you to think ahead while staying one step ahead of a relentless pursuer. The deeper you venture into the maze, the greater the tension becomes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":202,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-run-before-it-s-too-late2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-202\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki: Run Before It\'s Too Late!</strong> is a casual survival and maze escape game built around exploration and quick reactions. Your objective is simple in theory: collect enough money scattered throughout the maze and locate the exit before the monster catches you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The maze is filled with winding corridors, dead ends, and hidden routes that make navigation increasingly difficult. While searching for cash, you\'ll need to stay alert because the creature constantly patrols the area, turning every decision into a risk.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game offers multiple difficulty settings, allowing both beginners and experienced players to test their survival skills. Higher difficulties make escaping much more demanding by increasing the overall challenge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Learning the controls takes only a moment, but surviving requires careful planning.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use <strong>WASD</strong> or the <strong>Arrow Keys</strong> to move through the maze.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Move the <strong>mouse</strong> to rotate the camera and improve your view.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Explore corridors to collect the required amount of money.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Avoid direct contact with the monster at all costs.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Once you\'ve gathered enough cash, locate the exit door and escape before being caught.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each successful escape depends on balancing exploration with safe movement rather than rushing blindly through the maze.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Suspenseful survival gameplay with constant monster pursuit.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Multiple difficulty modes ranging from Easy to Impossible.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Large maze filled with hidden paths and collectibles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple keyboard and mouse controls for smooth navigation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Increasing tension that rewards observation and quick decision-making.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Memorize important landmarks while exploring the maze.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rotate the camera often to avoid walking into dangerous corners.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Don\'t collect money randomly—plan an efficient route.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">If you discover the exit early, remember its location for later.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Stay calm when the monster appears; sudden panic often leads to mistakes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunked</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki\'s World</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Doors</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki: Run Before It\'s Too Late! blends maze exploration with survival horror to create a tense browser game that rewards smart navigation and quick thinking. With adjustable difficulty levels and unpredictable encounters, every escape attempt feels different, making it an entertaining challenge for players who enjoy suspense-filled adventures.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki: Run before it\'s too late!','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-run-before-its-too-late','','','2026-07-03 03:46:29','2026-07-03 03:46:29','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=201',0,'game','',0),(202,1,'2026-07-03 03:38:13','2026-07-03 03:38:13','','sprunki-run-before-it-s-too-late2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-run-before-it-s-too-late2','','','2026-07-03 03:38:13','2026-07-03 03:38:13','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-run-before-it-s-too-late2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(203,1,'2026-07-03 03:38:14','2026-07-03 03:38:14','','Sprunki: Run before it\'s too late!','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-run-before-its-too-late-2','','','2026-07-03 03:42:04','2026-07-03 03:42:04','',201,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-run-before-it-s-too-late.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(204,1,'2026-07-03 03:46:06','2026-07-03 03:46:06','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Retake 2: Craft Desert-Inspired Beats With Creative Sound Mixing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">A fresh setting can completely change the mood of a music game, and <strong>Sprunki Retake 2</strong> proves that with its desert-inspired theme. Surrounded by sandy landscapes and animated performers, players are free to arrange original soundtracks using an intuitive drag-and-drop system. Every combination produces a different musical result, encouraging experimentation rather than perfection. The addition of a one-click Horror Mode adds another layer of variety for those who enjoy darker visual and audio effects.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":205,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-2-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-205\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Retake 2</strong> is a browser-based music creation game where imagination takes the lead. Instead of following predefined songs, you assemble your own performance by assigning unique sounds to a cast of animated characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each sound icon contributes something different, from rhythmic beats and vocal samples to melodies and special effects. Mixing these elements allows you to create tracks that range from calm and relaxing to energetic and dramatic. Since sounds can be replaced at any moment, there is always room to improve or completely redesign your composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlike many music games, switching between the standard presentation and the horror-themed version is effortless. A single click instantly changes the atmosphere without interrupting your creative process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The controls are simple enough for anyone to start composing immediately.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your <strong>mouse</strong> to drag sound icons onto the performers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Every icon activates a different musical effect.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue assigning sounds until your group performs a complete composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace or remove sounds whenever you want to experiment with new combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click the final icon to instantly toggle between Normal Mode and Horror Mode.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There are no fixed objectives or scores. Your goal is to create music that matches your personal style through endless experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Desert-themed visuals inspired by wide open landscapes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Drag-and-drop sound mixing with intuitive controls.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Large selection of unique musical icons and audio effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Instant switching between Normal Mode and Horror Mode.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlimited replay value through countless sound combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with rhythmic sounds before adding melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Test bright and dark sound icons to create different musical moods.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace one sound at a time to hear its individual impact.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try Horror Mode after completing a normal composition for a completely different atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Don\'t be afraid to remix your entire track—unexpected combinations often produce the best results.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Zombies Can Sing Too</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">SprunkioPhobia</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Retake 2 expands the familiar Sprunki music formula with a distinctive desert setting and flexible sound design. Its accessible controls, creative freedom, and instant Horror Mode make every session an opportunity to build original tracks while discovering new musical combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Retake 2','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-2','','','2026-07-03 03:46:06','2026-07-03 03:46:06','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=204',0,'game','',0),(205,1,'2026-07-03 03:43:02','2026-07-03 03:43:02','','sprunki-retake-2-3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-2-3','','','2026-07-03 03:43:02','2026-07-03 03:43:02','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-2-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(206,1,'2026-07-03 03:43:03','2026-07-03 03:43:03','','Sprunki Retake 2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-2-2','','','2026-07-03 03:46:06','2026-07-03 03:46:06','',204,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-2-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(207,1,'2026-07-03 03:52:22','2026-07-03 03:52:22','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Five Nights with Sprunki: Survive Every Shift in This Chilling Horror Game</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dark hallways, limited resources, and a mysterious creature create constant tension in <strong>Five Nights with Sprunki</strong>. Instead of relying on action, the game challenges your observation, timing, and decision-making as you defend a small security office throughout the night. Every sound and camera movement matters, turning even quiet moments into suspenseful encounters. The longer you survive, the more demanding each new night becomes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":208,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/five-nights-with-sprunki-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-208\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Five Nights with Sprunki</strong> is a browser-based survival horror game centered on security management and strategic resource use. Players take on the role of a night guard assigned to monitor a building while preventing a frightening Sprunki creature from reaching the security room.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each shift lasts from midnight until 6:00 AM. Throughout the night, you\'ll switch between security cameras, monitor suspicious activity, and react quickly whenever the creature approaches. Every action consumes valuable time and attention, so balancing surveillance with defense is essential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">As additional nights unlock, the challenge gradually increases. Faster enemy movements and greater pressure require better planning and sharper reactions, rewarding players who learn the creature\'s behavior.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mastering the controls is the first step toward surviving all five nights.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Move your <strong>mouse</strong> to the bottom of the screen to open the security camera interface.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Select different camera feeds to monitor the building.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Press the <strong>door control buttons</strong> to close or open the security room entrances.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Activate the <strong>corridor lights</strong> to check nearby areas and discourage unexpected attacks.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue managing your defenses until the clock reaches <strong>6:00 AM</strong>.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Completing each night unlocks the next stage, where surviving becomes increasingly difficult.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Suspenseful survival horror focused on observation and strategy.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Security camera system for tracking enemy movement.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Interactive doors and hallway lights for defensive gameplay.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Multiple nights with steadily increasing difficulty.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Atmospheric visuals and tense audio that heighten every encounter.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Check cameras regularly, but avoid staying on one feed for too long.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use doors only when necessary to avoid wasting valuable resources.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Flash hallway lights before opening a door if you suspect danger nearby.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Learn the creature\'s movement patterns to react more efficiently.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Stay calm during sudden scares—quick decisions often determine whether you survive.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Game</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Remastered</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki: Run Before It\'s Too Late!</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Five Nights with Sprunki delivers a suspense-filled survival experience where patience and awareness matter more than quick reflexes. Its combination of security management, escalating difficulty, and unpredictable scares creates an engaging horror challenge that encourages players to improve with every attempt.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Five Nights with Sprunki','','publish','open','closed','','five-nights-with-sprunki','','','2026-07-03 03:52:22','2026-07-03 03:52:22','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=207',0,'game','',0),(208,1,'2026-07-03 03:49:17','2026-07-03 03:49:17','','five-nights-with-sprunki-2','','inherit','open','closed','','five-nights-with-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-03 03:49:17','2026-07-03 03:49:17','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/five-nights-with-sprunki-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(209,1,'2026-07-03 03:49:18','2026-07-03 03:49:18','','Five Nights with Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','five-nights-with-sprunki-3','','','2026-07-03 03:52:22','2026-07-03 03:52:22','',207,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/five-nights-with-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(210,1,'2026-07-03 03:56:57','2026-07-03 03:56:57','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Sprinkle: Create Cheerful Beats in a Colorful Music Adventure</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Bright visuals and playful sound design give <strong>Sprunki Sprinkle</strong> its own personality among browser-based music games. Instead of chasing points or completing difficult levels, you\'ll spend your time experimenting with rhythms, vocals, and melodies to produce original songs. Every performer adds a new musical layer, making it easy to build lively compositions while enjoying the game\'s cheerful atmosphere and creative freedom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":212,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprinkle.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-212\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Sprinkle</strong> is a casual music creation game that focuses on creativity rather than competition. Inspired by the Sprunki universe, this version introduces redesigned characters, fresh visual themes, and a collection of new sounds that encourage players to experiment with different musical styles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to arrange sound icons across a group of animated performers and combine them into a complete musical performance. Every icon represents a unique beat, melody, vocal, or sound effect. As you mix and match these elements, your composition evolves into a soundtrack that reflects your own creative choices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Because there are no time limits or scoring systems, players can freely modify every arrangement until they find a combination they enjoy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game is easy to learn, even for first-time players.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your <strong>mouse</strong> to drag sound icons onto the Sprunki characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each icon activates a different musical element.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue assigning sounds to build a layered performance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remove or replace icons whenever you want to experiment with a new arrangement.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Keep adjusting your mix until you\'ve created a song that matches your style.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no right or wrong combination, making every play session a unique creative experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Colorful character redesigns inspired by the Sprunki universe.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Intuitive drag-and-drop music creation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Wide variety of beats, vocals, and sound effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlimited musical combinations with no creative restrictions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Browser-based gameplay with no downloads required.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with a rhythmic foundation before adding melodies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Combine different sound categories to create richer compositions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replace individual icons instead of rebuilding the entire song.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Listen carefully to how each new sound changes the overall rhythm.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Experiment with unexpected combinations—you might discover your favorite track.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki: Run Before It\'s Too Late!</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Zombies Can Sing Too</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunked</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Sprinkle turns music creation into a relaxing and imaginative browser game where every player becomes the composer. With charming visuals, accessible controls, and nearly endless sound combinations, it offers a satisfying creative experience for anyone who enjoys experimenting with rhythm and original musical ideas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Sprinkle','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-sprinkle','','','2026-07-03 03:56:57','2026-07-03 03:56:57','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=210',0,'game','',0),(211,1,'2026-07-03 03:54:14','2026-07-03 03:54:14','','sprunki-sprinkle-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sprinkle-2','','','2026-07-03 03:54:14','2026-07-03 03:54:14','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprinkle-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(212,1,'2026-07-03 03:54:14','2026-07-03 03:54:14','','Sprunki Sprinkle','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sprinkle-3','','','2026-07-03 03:56:57','2026-07-03 03:56:57','',210,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprinkle.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(213,1,'2026-07-03 04:02:46','2026-07-03 04:02:46','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Clicker: Build Beats One Click at a Time</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Clicker blends idle progression with rhythm-inspired entertainment, creating a simple game that\'s surprisingly hard to put down. Every click earns points while unlocking colorful characters, catchy sound loops, and visual surprises. Fast-paced bonus icons and rewarding upgrades keep the action moving, making each session feel satisfying whether you play for a few minutes or settle in for a longer score-chasing run.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":214,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-clicker-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-214\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Clicker is a browser-based clicker game with musical elements. Instead of simply collecting points, every interaction contributes to an evolving audiovisual experience as new characters and effects become available.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to earn as many points as possible through active clicking and passive income upgrades. Along the way, you\'ll unlock additional Sprunki characters, weather effects, and fresh musical styles that give each stage a different atmosphere.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Gameplay is easy to understand from the very first click. Tap the main character or press the spacebar to generate points. Occasionally, special Sprunki icons fly across the screen. Clicking these before they disappear rewards valuable bonus points, helping you unlock new content much faster.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Starting the game takes only a few seconds, but building an efficient point-generating system requires smart upgrade choices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Controls</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click the main character with your mouse.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Press the <strong>Spacebar</strong> as an alternative way to click.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click flying Sprunki bonus icons whenever they appear.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Every click increases your score. Spend your earned points on upgrades that strengthen manual clicks or automatically generate points over time. As your total score grows, additional characters and visual effects become available, giving the game a fresh look and sound.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Goal</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue expanding your score, unlock every available character, and maximize your point production through a combination of active clicking and automated upgrades.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple click-based gameplay with instant progression.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Manual and automatic upgrades for faster point generation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Bonus Sprunki icons that provide extra rewards.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlockable characters featuring different visual styles and music.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dynamic weather effects that refresh the game\'s presentation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Purchase automatic upgrades early to build passive income.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\