his information only to respond to your inquiry, provide support, and improve our services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Cookies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Keep you signed in.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Remember your preferences.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Improve website performance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Measure traffic and usage.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Support advertising services.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can manage cookies through your browser settings. Some features may not function properly if cookies are disabled.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A separate Cookie Policy provides additional details about our use of cookies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Google Analytics</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use Google Analytics to better understand how visitors use our Website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google Analytics may collect information such as:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Device information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Browser type</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>IP address</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pages visited</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Session duration</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Interactions with the Website</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!--