Games offers games developed by us and by third-party developers or publishers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some games may be embedded from external platforms or use third-party services. These services may collect information according to their own privacy policies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are not responsible for the privacy practices of third-party websites or services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Third-Party Services</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may use trusted third-party providers to operate and improve our Website, including services for:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Website hosting</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Analytics</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Advertising</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Authentication</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Email delivery</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Security</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Customer support</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These providers may process information only as necessary to perform their services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Data Retention</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Provide our services</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Maintain user accounts</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Respond to inquiries</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Comply with legal obligations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Resolve disputes</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Enforce our policies</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Information that is no longer required may be deleted or anonymized.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">11. International Data Transfers</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your information may be processed or stored in countries other than your own.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By using our Website, you understand that your information may be transferred internationally where permitted by applicable law.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We take reasonable measures to protect transferred data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">12. Data Security</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational safeguards to protect your information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, no method of transmission or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">13. Children\'s Privacy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MiniWebGames is intended for a general audience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children in violation of applicable laws.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us. We will take appropriate steps to remove the information when required.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">14. Your Privacy Rights</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Access your personal information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Correct inaccurate information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Request deletion of your information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Restrict or object to certain processing.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Withdraw consent where applicable.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Request a copy of your personal data.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To exercise these rights, please contact us.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">15. California Privacy Rights</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are a California resident, you may have additional rights under applicable California privacy laws, including the right to know, access, delete, and correct certain personal information, subject to legal exceptions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MiniWebGames does not sell personal information as defined by applicable California privacy laws.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">16. European Privacy Rights</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), the United Kingdom, or Switzerland, you may have rights under applicable data protection laws, including the GDPR.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where required, we process personal information based on legal grounds such as your consent, contractual necessity, legal obligations, or our legitimate interests.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">17. Your Choices</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You may:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Update your account information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Manage cookies through your browser.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Control advertising preferences through Google.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Stop using our Website at any time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Contact us to request account deletion where applicable.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">18. Third-Party Links</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Website may contain links to third-party websites, games, or services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or policies of third-party websites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">19. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our services, legal requirements, or business practices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The updated version will be posted on this page with a revised <strong>Effective Date</strong>. Your continued use of the Website after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">20. Contact Us</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us through our <strong>Contact Us</strong> page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Website:</strong> MiniWebGames</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Contact Page:</strong> <a>https://miniwebgames.com/contact-us</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">21. Your Consent</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By accessing or using MiniWebGames, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to the collection, use, and disclosure of your information as described herein.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Effective Date</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 8, 2026</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 8, 2026</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','3-revision-v1','','','2026-07-08 04:20:23','2026-07-08 04:20:23','',3,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=243',0,'revision','',0),(245,1,'2026-07-08 04:23:23','2026-07-08 04:23:23','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 8, 2026</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Privacy Policy</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Welcome to <strong>MiniWebGames</strong> (\"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you visit <strong><a href=\"https://miniwebgames.com\">https://miniwebgames.com</a></strong> (\"Website\"). By using our Website, you agree to this Privacy Policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-head