ze\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Advertising partners may use cookies and similar technologies as described in our Privacy Policy and Cookie Policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Privacy</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Your use of the Website is also governed by our:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Privacy Policy</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Cookie Policy</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">By using the Website, you acknowledge that you have read these policies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Disclaimer</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The Website and its content are provided on an <strong>\"AS IS\"</strong> and <strong>\"AS AVAILABLE\"</strong> basis.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">We do not guarantee uninterrupted access, error-free operation, or that every game or feature will always be available.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Limitation of Liability</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">To the maximum extent permitted by law, MiniWebGames shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Nothing in these Terms limits rights that cannot be excluded under applicable law.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Changes to These Terms</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">We may update these Terms from time to time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Any changes will become effective when posted on this page with an updated <strong>Effective Date</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Your continued use of the Website after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">11. Termination</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">We may suspend or terminate access to the Website or user accounts if these Terms are violated or if necessary to protect the Website, its users, or applicable legal requirements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">12. Contact Us</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">If you have any questions regarding these Terms, please contact us through our <strong>Contact Us</strong> page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href=\"https://miniwebgames.com\">https://miniwebgames.com</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Contact Page:</strong> <a href=\"https://miniwebgames.local/contact-us/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"73\">https://miniwebgames.com/contact-us</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 8, 2026</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 8, 2026</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Terms Of Service','','inherit','closed','closed','','78-revision-v1','','','2026-07-08 05:33:56','2026-07-08 05:33:56','',78,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=258',0,'revision','',0),(259,1,'2026-07-08 07:11:52','2026-07-08 07:11:52','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki has become one of the most popular fan-made music games inspired by Incredibox, attracting millions of players with its creative gameplay and unforgettable cast of characters. Every Sprunki character contributes a unique sound, allowing players to combine beats, melodies, vocals, and effects into original musical compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Whether you\'re playing for the first time or trying to discover every hidden combination, understanding each character is the key to creating better mixes. Every icon has its own personality, sound style, and role within a song, making each performance feel different depending on the characters you choose.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">One of the reasons Sprunki remains so addictive is the variety of characters available. Bright and cheerful performers in Normal Mode transform into eerie, unsettling versions in Horror Mode, creating an entirely different musical experience while keeping the same core gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">This guide introduces every major Sprunki character, explains how they are grouped, and helps you understand how each one contributes to your music. Whether you\'re looking for your favorite character, exploring Horror Mode, or simply learning how the game works, you\'ll find everything you need right here.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Table of Contents</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">What Are Sprunki Characters?</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">How Characters Work</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Character Groups</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beat Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Melody Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Effects Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Vocal Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Special Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Normal Mode vs Horror Mode</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Best Character Combinations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Frequently Asked Questions</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Are Sprunki Characters?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki characters are the heart of the game. Instead of controlling movement or combat, players build music by dragging different characters onto the stage. Each character represents a specific sound element, allowing anyone to create original songs without musical experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Every character belongs to a particular audio category. Some produce strong drum beats, while others create melodies, vocal lines, sound effects, or background harmonies. Combining these sounds in different ways results in nearly endless musical possibilities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Unlike many rhythm games that require precise timing, Sprunki encourages experimentation. There are no right or wrong combinations. Players can freely mix characters to discover new rhythms, hidden animations, and unique musical styles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">As new Sprunki versions and fan-made mods continue to appear, the roster has expanded significantly. While some characters have become community favorites, every character plays an important role in shaping the game\'s creative identity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How Sprunki Characters Work</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The gameplay of Sprunki is simple enough for beginners yet flexible enough for experienced players.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Every character represents one looping sound. When placed on the stage, that sound begins playing continuously until the character is removed or replaced. As more characters are added, the individual loops blend together to form a complete musical composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Most songs are built by combining four essential sound categories:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beats provide rhythm and timing.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Melodies create the main tune.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Effects add texture and atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Vocals bring personality and energy.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Because every loop is synchronized automatically, players can focus entirely on creativity rather than technical music production. Even simple combinations often produce surprisingly polished results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Many experienced players enjoy experimenting with different arrangements to discover hidden bonuses, unlock special animations, or recreate popular songs using only Sprunki characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Groups Overview</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">To make music creation easier, Sprunki characters are generally divided into several sound groups. Each group serves a different purpose when building a song.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table has-small-font-size\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Group</th><th>Main Role</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>🥁 Beat Characters</td><td>Rhythm and percussion</td></tr><tr><td>🎵 Melody Characters</td><td>Main musical notes</td></tr><tr><td>✨ Effect Characters</td><td>Background effects and transitions</td></tr><tr><td>🎤 Vocal Characters</td><td>Singing, voices, and harmony</td></tr><tr><td>⭐ Special Characters</td><td>Hidden characters and special transformations</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Understanding these groups is the fastest way to create balanced and professional-sounding mixes. Rather than choosing characters randomly, experienced players often begin with a beat, add melodies, layer effects, and finish with vocals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">In the following sections, we\'ll explore every group in detail, starting with the Beat Characters—the rhythmic foundation of every great Sprunki composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beat Characters</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beat Characters are the rhythmic foundation of every Sprunki composition. Just like a drummer keeps a band together, these characters provide the pulse that allows melodies, vocals, and effects to blend naturally.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">For beginners, the Beat group is usually the best place to start. Building a song with a strong rhythm makes it much easier to create balanced and enjoyable music.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Although each Beat Character produces percussion sounds, every one has a unique personality and musical style. Some deliver deep bass drums, while others create electronic rhythms or mechanical beats that completely change the atmosphere of a mix.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Oren</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Oren is one of the most recognizable characters in Sprunki and is often the first character players choose when learning the game. His cheerful orange appearance and simple rhythmic loop make him an excellent introduction to music creation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rather than overwhelming the mix, Oren produces a clean, balanced beat that works well with almost every melody and vocal character. Because of this flexibility, experienced players frequently use him as the foundation of more complex compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Character Information</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table has-small-font-size\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐ Beginner</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Basic Drum Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Rhythm Foundation</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Players Like Oren</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy for beginners</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Fits almost every music style</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Creates a clean rhythm</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Excellent for experimenting</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Oren works especially well with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simon</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Pinki</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Gray</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mr. Sun</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">These combinations create energetic but balanced songs suitable for almost any Sprunki version.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">In Horror Mode, Oren transforms from a cheerful performer into a disturbing version with darker colors and unsettling facial expressions. His beat remains recognizable but becomes much heavier, helping establish the frightening atmosphere that Horror Mode is known for.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Raddy</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Raddy brings a much stronger rhythm than Oren. His aggressive appearance reflects the more powerful percussion he contributes to a song.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Players often choose Raddy when creating energetic electronic music or intense Horror Mode compositions because his beat immediately attracts attention without overpowering other characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐ Easy</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Heavy Drum Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Strong Rhythm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strengths</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Powerful percussion</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Creates energetic music</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Great for action-themed mixes</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Excellent Horror Mode rhythm</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raddy pairs well with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clukr</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jevin</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fun Bot</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Black</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These combinations produce dramatic musical arrangements with a darker atmosphere.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raddy becomes far more intimidating in Horror Mode. His appearance grows more sinister while his rhythmic loop feels heavier and more intense, making him a favorite choice for horror-themed mixes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clukr</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clukr introduces a more mechanical style of percussion. Rather than traditional drum sounds, his loop feels electronic and robotic, making him ideal for futuristic compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many advanced players use Clukr to add variety to their rhythm section instead of relying solely on traditional drum beats.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐ Easy</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Mechanical Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Electronic Rhythm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strengths</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Futuristic sound</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Works well in electronic music</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Adds texture to the rhythm section</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Easy to combine with melody characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clukr works especially well with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fun Bot</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Garnold</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Simon</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jevin</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These combinations often produce clean electronic mixes with a modern feel.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Horror Mode, Clukr\'s robotic style becomes even more unsettling. Metallic sounds feel harsher, while his appearance reflects the darker atmosphere of the game.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fun Bot</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fun Bot is one of the most unique Beat Characters because his sounds combine percussion with electronic elements. His robotic design perfectly matches his futuristic audio style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unlike traditional beat makers, Fun Bot creates rhythms that immediately give a song a digital or sci-fi feeling. This makes him one of the most memorable characters in the entire Sprunki roster.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Medium</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Electronic Percussion</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Digital Rhythm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Players Love Fun Bot</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Unique robotic sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Great for futuristic music</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fits electronic genres</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>One of the community favorites</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Recommended partners include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clukr</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Garnold</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Simon</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jevin</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Together they create polished electronic tracks with impressive depth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fun Bot undergoes one of the most dramatic transformations in Horror Mode. His mechanical appearance becomes darker and more ominous, while his electronic rhythm feels colder and more unsettling.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Garnold</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Garnold completes the Beat Character lineup with a distinctive industrial rhythm. His sounds are more layered than those of the other beat performers, making him a valuable addition to advanced music mixes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Although he may be less beginner-friendly, Garnold offers excellent flexibility once players become familiar with the game\'s mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Medium</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Industrial Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Advanced Rhythm Layer</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strengths</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Rich rhythmic texture</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Excellent for advanced compositions</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Blends well with electronic sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Adds depth to long music loops</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Garnold performs especially well alongside:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fun Bot</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clukr</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Gray</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Mr. Black</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These combinations create cinematic and dramatic musical arrangements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Horror Mode, Garnold\'s industrial rhythm becomes heavier and more mechanical. Combined with his darker appearance, he helps establish the eerie atmosphere that defines Horror Mode.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which Beat Character Should You Choose?</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Each Beat Character serves a different purpose, so the best choice depends on the style of music you want to create.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Character</th><th>Best For</th><th>Difficulty</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Oren</td><td>Beginners</td><td>⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Raddy</td><td>Powerful rhythms</td><td>⭐⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Clukr</td><td>Electronic music</td><td>⭐⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Fun Bot</td><td>Futuristic songs</td><td>⭐⭐⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Garnold</td><td>Advanced compositions</td><td>⭐⭐⭐</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For new players, <strong>Oren</strong> is the easiest starting point because his rhythm blends naturally with almost every other character. If you enjoy electronic or sci-fi inspired music, <strong>Fun Bot</strong> and <strong>Clukr</strong> are excellent choices. Players looking for darker, more dramatic compositions often prefer <strong>Raddy</strong> or <strong>Garnold</strong>, especially in Horror Mode.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','All Sprunki Characters (2026): Complete Guide to Every Character, Groups &amp; Horror Mode','','publish','open','open','','all-sprunki-characters-2026-complete-guide-to-every-character-groups-horror-mode','','','2026-07-08 07:58:04','2026-07-08 07:58:04','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=259',0,'post','',0),(260,1,'2026-07-08 07:11:52','2026-07-08 07:11:52','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki has become one of the most popular fan-made music games inspired by Incredibox, attracting millions of players with its creative gameplay and unforgettable cast of characters. Every Sprunki character contributes a unique sound, allowing players to combine beats, melodies, vocals, and effects into original musical compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Whether you\'re playing for the first time or trying to discover every hidden combination, understanding each character is the key to creating better mixes. Every icon has its own personality, sound style, and role within a song, making each performance feel different depending on the characters you choose.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">One of the reasons Sprunki remains so addictive is the variety of characters available. Bright and cheerful performers in Normal Mode transform into eerie, unsettling versions in Horror Mode, creating an entirely different musical experience while keeping the same core gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">This guide introduces every major Sprunki character, explains how they are grouped, and helps you understand how each one contributes to your music. Whether you\'re looking for your favorite character, exploring Horror Mode, or simply learning how the game works, you\'ll find everything you need right here.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Table of Contents</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>What Are Sprunki Characters?</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>How Characters Work</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Character Groups</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Beat Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Melody Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Effects Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Vocal Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Special Characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Normal Mode vs Horror Mode</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Best Character Combinations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Frequently Asked Questions</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Are Sprunki Characters?</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sprunki characters are the heart of the game. Instead of controlling movement or combat, players build music by dragging different characters onto the stage. Each character represents a specific sound element, allowing anyone to create original songs without musical experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every character belongs to a particular audio category. Some produce strong drum beats, while others create melodies, vocal lines, sound effects, or background harmonies. Combining these sounds in different ways results in nearly endless musical possibilities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unlike many rhythm games that require precise timing, Sprunki encourages experimentation. There are no right or wrong combinations. Players can freely mix characters to discover new rhythms, hidden animations, and unique musical styles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As new Sprunki versions and fan-made mods continue to appear, the roster has expanded significantly. While some characters have become community favorites, every character plays an important role in shaping the game\'s creative identity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How Sprunki Characters Work</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The gameplay of Sprunki is simple enough for beginners yet flexible enough for experienced players.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every character represents one looping sound. When placed on the stage, that sound begins playing continuously until the character is removed or replaced. As more characters are added, the individual loops blend together to form a complete musical composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Most songs are built by combining four essential sound categories:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Beats provide rhythm and timing.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Melodies create the main tune.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Effects add texture and atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Vocals bring personality and energy.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Because every loop is synchronized automatically, players can focus entirely on creativity rather than technical music production. Even simple combinations often produce surprisingly polished results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many experienced players enjoy experimenting with different arrangements to discover hidden bonuses, unlock special animations, or recreate popular songs using only Sprunki characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','All Sprunki Characters (2026): Complete Guide to Every Character, Groups &amp; Horror Mode','','inherit','closed','closed','','259-revision-v1','','','2026-07-08 07:11:52','2026-07-08 07:11:52','',259,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=260',0,'revision','',0),(262,1,'2026-07-08 07:14:21','2026-07-08 07:14:21','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki has become one of the most popular fan-made music games inspired by Incredibox, attracting millions of players with its creative gameplay and unforgettable cast of characters. Every Sprunki character contributes a unique sound, allowing players to combine beats, melodies, vocals, and effects into original musical compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Whether you\'re playing for the first time or trying to discover every hidden combination, understanding each character is the key to creating better mixes. Every icon has its own personality, sound style, and role within a song, making each performance feel different depending on the characters you choose.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">One of the reasons Sprunki remains so addictive is the variety of characters available. Bright and cheerful performers in Normal Mode transform into eerie, unsettling versions in Horror Mode, creating an entirely different musical experience while keeping the same core gameplay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} --