s</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Understanding these groups is the fastest way to create balanced and professional-sounding mixes. Rather than choosing characters randomly, experienced players often begin with a beat, add melodies, layer effects, and finish with vocals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">In the following sections, we\'ll explore every group in detail, starting with the Beat Characters—the rhythmic foundation of every great Sprunki composition.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beat Characters</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Beat Characters are the rhythmic foundation of every Sprunki composition. Just like a drummer keeps a band together, these characters provide the pulse that allows melodies, vocals, and effects to blend naturally.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">For beginners, the Beat group is usually the best place to start. Building a song with a strong rhythm makes it much easier to create balanced and enjoyable music.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Although each Beat Character produces percussion sounds, every one has a unique personality and musical style. Some deliver deep bass drums, while others create electronic rhythms or mechanical beats that completely change the atmosphere of a mix.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Oren</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Oren is one of the most recognizable characters in Sprunki and is often the first character players choose when learning the game. His cheerful orange appearance and simple rhythmic loop make him an excellent introduction to music creation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rather than overwhelming the mix, Oren produces a clean, balanced beat that works well with almost every melody and vocal character. Because of this flexibility, experienced players frequently use him as the foundation of more complex compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Character Information</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table has-small-font-size\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐ Beginner</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Basic Drum Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Rhythm Foundation</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Players Like Oren</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy for beginners</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Fits almost every music style</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Creates a clean rhythm</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Excellent for experimenting</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Oren works especially well with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simon</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Pinki</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Gray</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mr. Sun</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">These combinations create energetic but balanced songs suitable for almost any Sprunki version.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">In Horror Mode, Oren transforms from a cheerful performer into a disturbing version with darker colors and unsettling facial expressions. His beat remains recognizable but becomes much heavier, helping establish the frightening atmosphere that Horror Mode is known for.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Raddy</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Raddy brings a much stronger rhythm than Oren. His aggressive appearance reflects the more powerful percussion he contributes to a song.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Players often choose Raddy when creating energetic electronic music or intense Horror Mode compositions because his beat immediately attracts attention without overpowering other characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐ Easy</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Heavy Drum Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Strong Rhythm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strengths</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Powerful percussion</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Creates energetic music</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Great for action-themed mixes</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Excellent Horror Mode rhythm</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raddy pairs well with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clukr</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jevin</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fun Bot</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Black</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These combinations produce dramatic musical arrangements with a darker atmosphere.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raddy becomes far more intimidating in Horror Mode. His appearance grows more sinister while his rhythmic loop feels heavier and more intense, making him a favorite choice for horror-themed mixes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clukr</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clukr introduces a more mechanical style of percussion. Rather than traditional drum sounds, his loop feels electronic and robotic, making him ideal for futuristic compositions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many advanced players use Clukr to add variety to their rhythm section instead of relying solely on traditional drum beats.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐ Easy</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Mechanical Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Electronic Rhythm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strengths</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Futuristic sound</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Works well in electronic music</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Adds texture to the rhythm section</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Easy to combine with melody characters</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Clukr works especially well with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fun Bot</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Garnold</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Simon</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jevin</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These combinations often produce clean electronic mixes with a modern feel.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Horror Mode, Clukr\'s robotic style becomes even more unsettling. Metallic sounds feel harsher, while his appearance reflects the darker atmosphere of the game.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fun Bot</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fun Bot is one of the most unique Beat Characters because his sounds combine percussion with electronic elements. His robotic design perfectly matches his futuristic audio style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unlike traditional beat makers, Fun Bot creates rhythms that immediately give a song a digital or sci-fi feeling. This makes him one of the most memorable characters in the entire Sprunki roster.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Medium</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Electronic Percussion</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Digital Rhythm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Players Love Fun Bot</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Unique robotic sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Great for futuristic music</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fits electronic genres</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>One of the community favorites</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Recommended partners include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clukr</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Garnold</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Simon</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Jevin</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Together they create polished electronic tracks with impressive depth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fun Bot undergoes one of the most dramatic transformations in Horror Mode. His mechanical appearance becomes darker and more ominous, while his electronic rhythm feels colder and more unsettling.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Garnold</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Garnold completes the Beat Character lineup with a distinctive industrial rhythm. His sounds are more layered than those of the other beat performers, making him a valuable addition to advanced music mixes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Although he may be less beginner-friendly, Garnold offers excellent flexibility once players become familiar with the game\'s mechanics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Character Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Category</td><td>Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Difficulty</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Medium</td></tr><tr><td>Sound Style</td><td>Industrial Beat</td></tr><tr><td>Best Role</td><td>Advanced Rhythm Layer</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strengths</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Rich rhythmic texture</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Excellent for advanced compositions</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Blends well with electronic sounds</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Adds depth to long music loops</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Combinations</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Garnold performs especially well alongside:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fun Bot</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clukr</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Gray</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Mr. Black</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These combinations create cinematic and dramatic musical arrangements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horror Mode</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Horror Mode, Garnold\'s industrial rhythm becomes heavier and more mechanical. Combined with his darker appearance, he helps establish the eerie atmosphere that defines Horror Mode.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which Beat Character Should You Choose?</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Each Beat Character serves a different purpose, so the best choice depends on the style of music you want to create.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Character</th><th>Best For</th><th>Difficulty</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Oren</td><td>Beginners</td><td>⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Raddy</td><td>Powerful rhythms</td><td>⭐⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Clukr</td><td>Electronic music</td><td>⭐⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Fun Bot</td><td>Futuristic songs</td><td>⭐⭐⭐</td></tr><tr><td>Garnold</td><td>Advanced compositions</td><td>⭐⭐⭐</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For new players, <strong>Oren</strong> is the easiest starting point because his rhythm blends naturally with almost every other character. If you enjoy electronic or sci-fi inspired music, <strong>Fun Bot</strong> and <strong>Clukr</strong> are excellent choices. Players looking for darker, more dramatic compositions often prefer <strong>Raddy</strong> or <strong>Garnold</strong>, especially in Horror Mode.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','All Sprunki Characters (2026): Complete Guide to Every Character, Groups &amp; Horror Mode','','inherit','closed','closed','','259-revision-v1','','','2026-07-08 07:58:03','2026-07-08 07:58:03','',259,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=264',0,'revision','',0),(265,1,'2026-07-08 08:04:55','2026-07-08 08:04:55','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Monstrous Infection</strong> transforms music creation into a dark and unsettling adventure. Instead of cheerful performers, you\'ll work with infected characters whose twisted appearances and distorted sounds reshape every composition. As the infection spreads, the stage grows more chaotic, rewarding players who enjoy experimenting with eerie rhythms, creepy melodies, and unexpected audio combinations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Monstrous Infection</strong> is a browser-based horror music game that blends creative beat-making with unsettling visual effects. The goal isn\'t to complete traditional levels but to build unique musical arrangements while watching the infected world evolve around you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Players drag infected characters onto the performance stage, and each one contributes a different sound element. Some add percussion, while others introduce melodies, vocal effects, or ambient noises. As more characters join the performance, the infection intensifies, changing both the soundtrack and the appearance of the scene with darker visuals, glitches, and disturbing animations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Because there are no fixed solutions, every session becomes a new experiment where different character combinations produce fresh musical results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to select and drag characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Place them onto the stage to activate their sounds.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remove or swap characters to create different mixes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Basic Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build your soundtrack by combining infected performers in different orders. Every addition changes the atmosphere, creating new layers of music while gradually transforming the environment into a more corrupted version of the Sprunki universe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no final boss or score requirement. The objective is to discover creative sound combinations and craft haunting musical tracks through experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Horror-inspired versions of familiar Sprunki characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dynamic sound combinations with creepy audio effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Visual corruption that grows as the performance continues.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless opportunities to experiment with musical arrangements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Easy drag-and-drop gameplay suitable for quick browser sessions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Begin with only a few characters before adding more complex sound layers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rearrange performers often to discover hidden musical variations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Listen carefully to how each infected character changes the overall rhythm.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix different sound types instead of stacking similar effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Don\'t hesitate to remove characters if the composition becomes too crowded.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki The Definitive Phase 10</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki HyperShifted Phase 4 but Swap Double</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 10</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Monstrous Infection offers a fresh twist on music creation by replacing bright melodies with eerie sounds and unsettling visuals. Its open-ended design encourages creativity, making every performance feel different. Players who enjoy horror themes and experimental rhythm games will find plenty of reasons to keep creating new corrupted soundtracks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Monstrous Infection','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-monstrous-infection','','','2026-07-08 08:05:32','2026-07-08 08:05:32','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=265',0,'game','',0),(266,1,'2026-07-08 08:01:31','2026-07-08 08:01:31','','Sprunki Monstrous Infection','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-monstrous-infection-2','','','2026-07-08 08:04:55','2026-07-08 08:04:55','',265,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-monstrous-infection.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(267,1,'2026-07-08 08:10:26','2026-07-08 08:10:26','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The nightmare continues in <strong>Sprunki Monstrous Infection Part 2</strong>, where music creation takes place inside a world consumed by corruption. The sequel introduces fresh infected performers, darker visual effects, and a heavier horror atmosphere that changes with every sound you add. Instead of following a fixed path, players are encouraged to experiment freely, creating chilling tracks while watching the infected universe become increasingly unstable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Monstrous Infection Part 2</strong> is a horror-themed music game built around drag-and-drop beat making. It expands the infection storyline with redesigned characters, unsettling animations, and new audio elements that give every performance a sinister tone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to compose original tracks by arranging infected characters on the stage. Each performer contributes a unique sound, including percussion, vocals, melodies, or eerie ambient effects. Mixing different combinations produces new musical patterns, while the spreading infection gradually transforms the stage with darker visuals and glitch-inspired effects.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rather than focusing on scores or timed challenges, the game rewards creativity and encourages players to discover countless musical possibilities through experimentation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to drag characters onto the stage.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click or remove performers to adjust your composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rearrange characters to explore different sound combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Basic Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Select infected characters and combine their sounds to build layered horror-inspired music. Every new addition changes both the soundtrack and the visual atmosphere, creating an evolving performance that feels different each time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There is no traditional ending. Success comes from producing unique musical arrangements and uncovering interesting interactions between corrupted characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Expanded roster of infected Sprunki characters.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">New horror-inspired vocals, beats, and sound effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Dynamic visual changes as corruption spreads.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Endless combinations for creating original music.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple drag-and-drop controls designed for browser play.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Build your composition one layer at a time for better balance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Try unusual character combinations to unlock unexpected sounds.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rearrange performers frequently to create fresh rhythms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Mix percussion, vocals, and melodies instead of relying on one sound type.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Watch the stage carefully, as visual changes can inspire new musical ideas.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Monstrous Infection</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Phase 13</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Parodybox</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Monstrous Infection Part 2 expands the horror-inspired music formula with more corrupted characters, richer sound design, and a darker atmosphere. Its flexible gameplay makes every session feel unique, giving creative players endless opportunities to craft unsettling tracks and explore the infected world through music.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Monstrous Infection Part 2','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-monstrous-infection-part-2','','','2026-07-08 08:11:33','2026-07-08 08:11:33','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=267',0,'game','',0),(268,1,'2026-07-08 08:07:28','2026-07-08 08:07:28','','Sprunki Monstrous Infection Part 2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-monstrous-infection-part-2-2','','','2026-07-08 08:10:26','2026-07-08 08:10:26','',267,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-monstrous-infection-part-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(270,1,'2026-07-08 08:20:52','2026-07-08 08:20:52','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Music takes on a sinister edge in <strong>Sprunki Infected Remastered</strong>, a fan-made horror mod that reimagines the Sprunki universe through a spreading infection. Every corrupted performer adds unsettling vocals, eerie melodies, and glitchy effects that reshape your composition. Enhanced visuals and refined animations make each performance feel more immersive, turning simple beat-making into a suspenseful creative challenge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Infected Remastered</strong> is a horror music game that combines rhythm-based creativity with dark storytelling. Developed as a remastered version of the original infection-themed mod, it introduces upgraded graphics, smoother animations, and richer sound design while preserving the drag-and-drop gameplay fans already know.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The objective is to build original musical tracks using infected characters. Each performer represents a different audio layer, such as percussion, vocals, melodies, or special effects. As your lineup grows, the infection spreads across the stage, transforming the environment with darker colors, visual distortion, and increasingly intense audio.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The game also adds story-focused elements through unlockable scenes that provide additional background about the infection without interrupting the music-making experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Controls</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use the mouse to drag characters onto the performance stage.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Click or remove characters to change your arrangement.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Rearrange performers to experiment with new sound combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Basic Gameplay</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Choose infected characters and combine their unique sounds into a complete musical composition. Every added performer contributes another audio layer while gradually increasing the visual corruption of the stage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Winning Goal</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There are no levels or score limits. The goal is to create your own horror-inspired soundtrack and discover interesting combinations by experimenting with different character lineups.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remastered visuals with sharper character designs and animations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Improved audio featuring deeper beats and eerie vocal effects.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Progressive infection effects that transform the stage.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Story cutscenes that expand the infection narrative.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Intuitive drag-and-drop controls for quick music creation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with rhythm characters before adding melodies and vocals.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Swap performers frequently to discover fresh musical patterns.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Balance different sound types for a richer composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Watch visual changes as the infection spreads—they often signal a dramatic shift in atmosphere.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay sessions with different character combinations to uncover new arrangements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Spunba Retake</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Betters And Loses Phase 4</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Monstrous Infection</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Infected Remastered successfully blends horror themes with creative music production. Its upgraded presentation, atmospheric sound design, and flexible gameplay offer an engaging experience for players who enjoy experimenting with eerie beats while exploring a darker version of the Sprunki universe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Infected Remastered','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-infected-remastered','','','2026-07-08 08:20:52','2026-07-08 08:20:52','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=270',0,'game','',0),(271,1,'2026-07-08 08:17:04','2026-07-08 08:17:04','','Sprunki Infected Remastered','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-infected-remastered-2','','','2026-07-08 08:20:52','2026-07-08 08:20:52','',270,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-infected-remastered.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(272,1,'2026-07-15 03:23:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-15 03:23:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=272',0,'game','',0),(274,1,'2026-07-15 03:42:19','2026-07-15 03:42:19','','Sprunki Gods And Evils','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-gods-and-evils-2','','','2026-07-15 06:43:34','2026-07-15 06:43:34','',281,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-gods-and-evils-image.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(276,1,'2026-07-15 04:40:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-15 04:40:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=276',0,'game','',0),(281,1,'2026-07-15 06:43:33','2026-07-15 06:43:33','<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Sprunki Gods and Evils stands as one of the most <a href=\"https://sprunkia.com/category/sprunki-mods/\">ambitious and visually striking mods</a> in the entire Sprunki community. This celestial horror experience pits divine beings against demonic forces in a high-stakes battle for the fate of the Sprunki universe. Released as a full-scale thematic overhaul, it blends religious mythology, dark fantasy, and classic Sprunki rhythm gameplay into something truly unforgettable.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The mod reimagines beloved Sprunki characters through the lens of gods, angels, demons, and fallen entities. From purple devils with smug expressions to angelic figures with glowing halos and tragic backstories, every character carries deep symbolic weight. The striking red-to-pink gradient background and detailed icon system immediately set a dramatic, apocalyptic tone that pulls players into an epic moral conflict.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Core Concept and Lore</h2><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">At its heart, Sprunki Gods and Evils explores the eternal struggle between light and darkness. The Shift event in this universe didn’t just corrupt the characters — it fractured reality itself, forcing every Sprunki to choose (or be chosen by) a divine or infernal path. Some embraced holy power and became celestial guardians, while others surrendered to temptation and transformed into powerful demons.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Key characters include:</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A confident purple devil figure representing temptation and pride<br>A wide-eyed innocent character caught between forces<br>A blue entity with a calm yet ominous presence<br>Yellow cat-like beings showing signs of internal conflict<br>A tearful blue creature symbolizing sorrow and lost innocence<br>A top-hatted black figure embodying pure chaotic evil</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The mod doesn’t shy away from heavy themes. Many characters display visible signs of their transformation — glowing eyes, blood tears, broken halos, and demonic horns. These details make the lore feel personal and tragic rather than purely cartoonish.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gameplay and Icon System</h2><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Sprunki Gods and Evils maintains the beloved drag-and-drop rhythm mechanics while introducing a rich category system that ties directly into the divine-evil theme. The bottom interface features dozens of unique icons representing different powers and alignments:</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">DEMON and DEAD icons for fallen or corrupted characters<br>LUST, WRATH, and other sin-based categories<br>ANGEL and holy symbols for redemptive or celestial paths<br>Special icons for RADIATION, MADNESS, COMBUSTION, and more</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Mixing characters from opposing alignments often creates the most powerful and thematically resonant tracks. Players report that combining demonic and angelic sounds produces hauntingly beautiful results that feel like prayers mixed with curses.The audio design is exceptional. Holy characters tend to have ethereal, choir-like vocals or soft chimes, while demonic entities deliver distorted growls, heavy industrial beats, and reversed whispers.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The contrast creates incredible depth when building compositions.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Visually, the mod is a masterpiece of contrast. The red-pink gradient sky creates an apocalyptic yet strangely beautiful setting. Characters are rendered with high detail — from intricate horn designs to subtle glowing effects on halos and eyes.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The animation quality stands out, with many characters showing idle movements that reveal their internal struggle (twitching wings, flickering auras, or restless demonic energy).The icon row at the bottom is particularly well-designed, with each symbol glowing when active and displaying clear thematic labels. This attention to UI detail makes the mod feel premium and professionally crafted.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Several factors explain Sprunki Gods and Evils’ rapid popularity:</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Moral Complexity — Unlike pure horror mods that focus only on scares, this one explores themes of choice, redemption, and corruption.<br>High Production Values — Excellent animations, consistent art direction, and polished sound design set it apart from many fan projects.<br>Replayability — The alignment system encourages players to experiment with different combinations to discover hidden interactions and special mixes.<br>Emotional Depth — Many characters feel tragic. The contrast between their original innocent designs and their current divine or demonic states creates genuine emotional investment.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Community creators have already produced dozens of viral mixes using the mod, with particularly popular combinations featuring the top-hatted black demon alongside angelic characters for maximum dramatic effect.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips for New Players of Sprunki Gods and Evils</h2><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Start with balanced mixes of good and evil characters to understand how the system works.<br>Pay close attention to glowing icons — they often unlock special visual effects or bonus sounds.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It feels more narrative-driven than many contemporaries, which explains why players often spend hours theory-crafting about character alignments and possible redemption stories. Sprunki Gods and Evils successfully bridges cute Sprunki charm with genuine darkness, making it accessible to newer players while offering enough depth to satisfy veteran horror fans.</p><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>','Sprunki Gods And Evils','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-gods-and-evils','','','2026-07-15 06:43:34','2026-07-15 06:43:34','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=281',0,'game','',0),(282,1,'2026-07-15 06:44:17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-15 06:44:17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=282',0,'game','',0),(283,1,'2026-07-15 06:44:23','2026-07-15 06:44:23','','Sprunki Blueverse of Evil Phase 4','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-blueverse-of-evil-phase-4','','','2026-07-15 06:44:23','2026-07-15 06:44:23','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-blueverse-of-evil-phase-4.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(284,1,'2026-07-15 14:24:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2026-07-15 14:24:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=284',0,'post','',0),(286,1,'2026-07-15 15:57:24','2026-07-15 15:57:24','','Toon Cup','','inherit','open','closed','','toon-cup-2','','','2026-07-15 16:20:08','2026-07-15 16:20:08','',288,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/copa-toon.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(288,1,'2026-07-15 16:20:07','2026-07-15 16:20:07','<p>We think that cartoons are only for children and many of them are but some of them remain relevant and it can be fun to see them playing together like in <strong>Toon Cup</strong>. When it comes to Cartoon Network shows, crossovers happen now and then so a universe where several different shows collide isn\'t inconceivable. What may be a bit harder to swallow is that they\'re all coming together to play a football tournament. But hey, stranger things have happened and probably will keep happening. Pick your cast of characters, head out to the field, and kick the ball around.</p><h2>About Toon Cup</h2><p>Whether or not you\'re familiar with Cartoon Network, you can tell from the characters just what kind of experience you can expect. This game is all about several different shows coming together and sending the best they have to offer to the field. Even though there\'s not much character interaction, their stats serve to show you just what kinds of characters they are. It\'s fun to play around with different combinations, finding that perfect balance for a game-winning team that you can take to the finals. Still, teams need some leadership and strategy which is what you\'re about to bring to the drawing board.</p><h2>How to Play</h2><p>Toon Cup is <strong>a 2D football game about cartoon characters playing against each other using the mouse</strong>.</p><h3>Controls</h3><ul><li>W/Up Arrow - Move Up</li><li>S/Down Arrow - Move Down</li><li>A/Left Arrow - Move Left</li><li>D/Right Arrow - Move Right</li><li>Spacebar - Kick/Pass/Tackle</li></ul><p>The goal of the game is to score more goals than the opposing team before the timer runs out. The time and score will be shown at the top of the screen. Each team can only have three players and ball possession switches depending on which side score the last goal. You can play a single Quick Match or try to win the cup by winning multiple games in a row in the Tournament. This is also how you can unlock new characters on the main menu.</p><p>If you choose a Quick Match, you\'ll automatically be assigned a random team of three characters, but the Tournament lets you pick your team. <strong>Each player has three stats: Speed, Kicking, and Tackling</strong>. After you\'ve chosen your players, you\'ll be taken to the field. You\'ll always take control of the player closest to the ball, as indicated by a blue highlight ring. You can tackle an opposing player who has the ball to steal it. When you have the ball, you can pass it to a teammate in range or take it to the goal to try and score. To shoot, you need to hold the kick button to power the shot and aim to get it in the blue area for a perfect shot.</p><p>There are also <strong>gift boxes that will randomly appear on the field that your players can collect</strong>. Doing so can have differing effects from stunning the opposing team with thunderbolts to giving one of your players a protective shield.</p><h3>Tips and Tricks</h3><p>The key to any good team is balance. Even though <strong>some players may be stronger than others, not all of them are flawless</strong>. If you pick a player who is strong in one area, pick another player to make up for their weakest area. Do your best to keep track of your teammates and don\'t linger in one spot otherwise the opposing team will quickly gang up on you.</p><h2>Game Details</h2><ul><li>Developer: Cartoon Network Games and Turner Broadcasting System</li><li>Platforms: Web Browser (PC and mobile), iOS, and Android</li><li>Languages: English</li></ul><h2>Gameplay Footage</h2><p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wU17U6wHefs?si=0a_1rdc8auBOvW7f\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2>FAQs</h2><h3>Is Toon Cup multiplayer?</h3><p>This may be a game about two teams playing football together, but <strong>it\'s sadly a single-player game against computer opponents</strong>.</p> <h3>What are the best Sports games?</h3> <ul><!--[--><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/basketball-stars\">Basketball Stars</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/hoop-world\">Hoop World</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/ultimate-flying-car\">Ultimate Flying Car</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/copa-toon\">Toon Cup</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/flip-trickster-parkour-simulator\">Flip Trickster - Parkour Simulator</a></li><!--]--></ul><h3>What are the best online games?</h3> <ul><!--[--><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/solitaire-gpx\">Solitaire Blue</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/minesweeper\">Minesweeper</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/2048\">2048</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/mahjong-gpx\">Mahjong</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/shell-shockers\">Shell Shockers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/smash-karts\">Smash Karts</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/1v1-lol\">1v1.LOL</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/dino-game-chrome\">Dino Game</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/flappybird\">Flappy Bird</a></li><!--]--></ul>','Toon Cup','','publish','open','closed','','toon-cup','','','2026-07-15 16:20:08','2026-07-15 16:20:08','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=288',0,'game','',0),(290,1,'2026-07-15 16:30:08','2026-07-15 16:30:08','','Kopanito All-Stars Soccer','','inherit','open','closed','','kopanito-all-stars-soccer-2','','','2026-07-15 17:26:51','2026-07-15 17:26:51','',293,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/kopanito-all-stars-soccer.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(291,1,'2026-07-15 17:13:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-15 17:13:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=291',0,'game','',0),(293,1,'2026-07-15 17:26:50','2026-07-15 17:26:50','<h2>Kopanito All-Stars Soccer Game Description</h2> <p>Kopanito All-Stars Soccer offers a thrilling arcade soccer game experience with easy-to-learn controls. Engage in fast-paced soccer matches against teams from around the world. Utilize special moves like lob passes and chip shots to outsmart opponents. With its top-down soccer perspective, fun couch multiplayer, and power ups soccer mechanics, you’ll focus on strategy and precision for an exciting gameplay challenge.</p>  <h2>How to play Kopanito All-Stars Soccer?</h2> <p>Navigate menus with arrow keys and select with Enter. <br>Use S to pass<br>A for lob passes<br>Hold D to shoot<br>Change shot direction with W/S. <br>Progress by refining these controls. <br><br>Remember, aim for the corners to increase scoring chances in this indie football game and casual sports game favorite.</p> <h3>Platform</h3> <p>Browser <!--[0-->Desktop<!--]--> <!--[-1--><!--]--> <!--[-1--><!--]--></p> <h3>Release date</h3> <p>March 8, 2021</p> <h3>Last update</h3> <p>April 1, 2025</p>  <h2>FAQs</h2>  <h3>What are the best Sports games?</h3> <ul><!--[--><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/basketball-stars\">Basketball Stars</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/hoop-world\">Hoop World</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/ultimate-flying-car\">Ultimate Flying Car</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/copa-toon\">Toon Cup</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/flip-trickster-parkour-simulator\">Flip Trickster - Parkour Simulator</a></li><!--]--></ul><h3>What are the best online games?</h3> <ul><!--[--><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/solitaire-gpx\">Solitaire Blue</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/minesweeper\">Minesweeper</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/2048\">2048</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/mahjong-gpx\">Mahjong</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/shell-shockers\">Shell Shockers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/smash-karts\">Smash Karts</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/1v1-lol\">1v1.LOL</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/dino-game-chrome\">Dino Game</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/flappybird\">Flappy Bird</a></li><!--]--></ul>','Kopanito All-Stars Soccer','','publish','open','closed','','kopanito-all-stars-soccer','','','2026-07-15 17:26:51','2026-07-15 17:26:51','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=293',0,'game','',0),(294,1,'2026-07-16 03:34:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-16 03:34:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=294',0,'game','',0),(295,1,'2026-07-16 03:46:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-16 03:46:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=295',0,'game','',0),(296,1,'2026-07-16 03:46:58','2026-07-16 03:46:58','','Top 10 Soccer Managers','','inherit','open','closed','','top-10-soccer-managers','','','2026-07-16 03:46:58','2026-07-16 03:46:58','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/top-10-soccer-managers.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(298,1,'2026-07-16 04:25:17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<h2>Description</h2> <p>Top 10 Soccer Managers immerses you in dynamic football management. Control player lineups, plan match events, and use tactics to elevate your team\'s standing. Swap players wisely, drill them, and make key choices for global triumphs.</p> <h2>How to Play</h2> <p>Point and click with the <b>mouse</b> to select options. Establish your team through trades and training. Set game schedules to enhance your club\'s prominence. Ensure a well-rounded team for optimal performance.</p> <h3>What are the best Sports games?</h3> <ul><!--[--><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/basketball-stars\">Basketball Stars</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/hoop-world\">Hoop World</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/ultimate-flying-car\">Ultimate Flying Car</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/copa-toon\">Toon Cup</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/flip-trickster-parkour-simulator\">Flip Trickster - Parkour Simulator</a></li><!--]--></ul><h3>What are the best online games?</h3> <ul><!--[--><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/solitaire-gpx\">Solitaire Blue</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/minesweeper\">Minesweeper</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/2048\">2048</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/mahjong-gpx\">Mahjong</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/shell-shockers\">Shell Shockers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/smash-karts\">Smash Karts</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/1v1-lol\">1v1.LOL</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/dino-game-chrome\">Dino Game</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gamepix.com/play/flappybird\">Flappy Bird</a></li><!--]--></ul>','Top 10 Soccer Managers','','draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-16 04:25:17','2026-07-16 04:25:17','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=298',0,'game','',0),(299,1,'2026-07-20 01:31:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2026-07-20 01:31:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&p=299',0,'game','',0),(300,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:02','2026-07-20 02:22:02','','sprunki-rejoyed-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-rejoyed-2','','','2026-07-20 02:22:02','2026-07-20 02:22:02','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-rejoyed-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(301,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:04','2026-07-20 02:22:04','','Sprunki Rejoyed','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-rejoyed-3','','','2026-07-20 02:22:04','2026-07-20 02:22:04','',302,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-rejoyed.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(302,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:04','2026-07-20 02:22:04','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Rejoyed</strong>, an enjoyable music game, delivers a fresh twist on the beloved Sprunki universe with a stunningly reimagined design. This innovative mod transforms your favorite characters into humans-like versions while preserving their signature charm. Placed within the intriguing universe of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a>, the game puts you into an enchanting music playground and gives you the key to become a producer. Let’s make your relaxing time more exciting now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-rejoyed-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"341\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Warning!</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This interesting mod contains unsettling imagery. These eerie elements can surprise you, making you frightened and affecting your gaming experience. So, beware when switching to Horror mode!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Rejoyed</strong> masterfully blends creativity with relaxation, offering a unique musical playground free of complicated rules. For this, you will have to work hard for the main goal of creating music. With the drag-and-drop mechanics, you are a real composer who brings charming music to in-game life. Each beautiful soundtrack will gradually echo under your magical hand and creative mind.</span></p>','Sprunki Rejoyed','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-rejoyed','','','2026-07-20 02:22:04','2026-07-20 02:22:04','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-rejoyed/',0,'game','',0),(303,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:04','2026-07-20 02:22:04','','sprunki-rainbow-friends-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-rainbow-friends-2','','','2026-07-20 02:22:04','2026-07-20 02:22:04','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-rainbow-friends-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(304,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:06','2026-07-20 02:22:06','','Sprunki Rainbow Friends','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-rainbow-friends-3','','','2026-07-20 02:22:06','2026-07-20 02:22:06','',305,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-rainbow-friends.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(305,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:06','2026-07-20 02:22:06','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Rainbow Friends</strong> welcomes you to the fairy tale, where music and color come together to create the most fascinating moment. In this vibrant world, you are a musician, guiding a group of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> figures to create beautiful melodies. Enter the game and receive this ultimate music journey now!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">CREATE THE COLORFUL WORLD</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>At the moment you enter <strong>Sprunki Rainbow Friends</strong>, you take on the important role of painting Sprunki characters. By arranging music boxes onto your figures, you can take them to a colorful and lively virtual stage.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-rainbow-friends-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"349\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Game Mode</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This music game offers only a <em>single mode</em> of gameplay. You can explore all features of the normal version and create your pleasant track with the brightest sounds.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS </h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li><h3>What types of players is this game suitable for?</h3></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> This title is an ideal choice for music lovers who enjoy creating music and casual players who are searching for casual games. </p><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li><h3>Where can I play the game? </h3></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Players can easily access the game via their browser.</span> </p><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li><h3>How to play the game? </h3></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>You can enjoy the music game with the drag-and-drop mechanics. Drag musical icons on your characters, and click once on Sprunkis’ body to remove beats!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Rhythm Games For All</span></h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-cats\">Sprunki Cats</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/zombies-can-sing-too\">Zombies Can Sing Too</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Rainbow Friends','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-rainbow-friends','','','2026-07-20 02:22:06','2026-07-20 02:22:06','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-rainbow-friends/',0,'game','',0),(306,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:07','2026-07-20 02:22:07','','sprunki-night-time-2.png1_','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-night-time-2-png1_','','','2026-07-20 02:22:07','2026-07-20 02:22:07','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-night-time-2.png1_.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(307,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:08','2026-07-20 02:22:08','','Sprunki Night Time','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-night-time-2','','','2026-07-20 02:22:08','2026-07-20 02:22:08','',308,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-night-time.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(308,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:08','2026-07-20 02:22:08','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Get ready to lose yourself in the enchanting rhythm of <strong>Sprunki Night Time</strong>, a dazzling twist on the Sprunki experience. This time, you will step into a modern city bathed in the glow of the night. In the game, skyscrapers tower over one another, casting golden lights that illuminate the night. Step into the role of a music composer; you will host a concert in front of the charming atmosphere. Join your music journey now!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dark Tone Design</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Sprunki characters stand against the dark yet charming city. Everything seems to settle into a relaxing pace after a long bustle and hustle day. It is time for you to play music and lull the citizens into a peaceful sleep.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-night-time-2.png1_.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">COMPOSE IMPRESSIVE SOUNDTRACKS</h2><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Explore Creative and Unique Gameplay</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Night Time</strong> puts you on a new mission—unlocking <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters and discovering music boxes. At the beginning, the music game features only two available figures and several musical icons. As you join the game, you need to constantly click on the avatars and icons to unlock them.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sprunki Characters</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>There are eight Sprunki characters in this mod. As you unlock one character, the next will pop out with a lock on its head. The number of clicks required to unlock avatars will increase gradually, testing your patience.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iconic Music With Sprunki</h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-oc\">Sprunki OC</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Night Time','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-night-time','','','2026-07-20 02:22:08','2026-07-20 02:22:08','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-night-time/',0,'game','',0),(309,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:08','2026-07-20 02:22:08','','sprunki-mustard-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-mustard-2','','','2026-07-20 02:22:08','2026-07-20 02:22:08','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-mustard-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(310,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:10','2026-07-20 02:22:10','','Sprunki Mustard','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-mustard-3','','','2026-07-20 02:22:10','2026-07-20 02:22:10','',311,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-mustard.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(311,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:10','2026-07-20 02:22:10','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sprunki Mustard</strong> is a popular music mixing game, letting you take the role of a genius composer to create music! In this casual game, you will have access to all essential ingredients - beatboxers, melodies, and special effects. Mix and match these elements to create fascinating tunes that reflect your unique style. Let’s start composing music!</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-mustard-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"419\"></h3><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sprunki Mustard Gameplay</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Mustard</strong> invites you to wake the seven <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters. They are standing boringly on the olive drab stage. With your creativity, you can change the atmosphere there. What you need to do is use your mouse to customize characters with various music. You can completely change sounds with a simple click on the character until you create a top-notch symphony! </span></p><h3>Jealousy of Sprunki Characters<strong> </strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This title features 25 musical icons, each with its own distinctive beat. You start with the first 20 icons, which keep the stage’s olive-green tone intact. But the excitement kicks up a notch when you select the twenty-first icon. This icon introduces vibrant green and pink hues to the stage, transforming the mood instantly. Besides, when you activate the twenty-second figure, the entire band comes alive, dancing to your tune with a new bandmaster leading the charge.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Check Out Other Hot Games</span></h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></li></ul><div class=\"game-preview__title\"> </div>','Sprunki Mustard','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-mustard','','','2026-07-20 02:22:10','2026-07-20 02:22:10','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-mustard/',0,'game','',0),(312,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:10','2026-07-20 02:22:10','','sprunkys-skibidi-titans-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkys-skibidi-titans-2','','','2026-07-20 02:22:10','2026-07-20 02:22:10','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkys-skibidi-titans-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(313,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:11','2026-07-20 02:22:11','','Sprunkys Skibidi Titans','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkys-skibidi-titans-3','','','2026-07-20 02:22:12','2026-07-20 02:22:12','',314,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkys-skibidi-titans.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(314,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:12','2026-07-20 02:22:12','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunkys Skibidi Titans</strong> delivers an unforgettable fusion of charismatic speaker men, and mysterious Skibidi monsters. This music creation game introduces you to hilarious Skibidi characters who are part of a band. As the role of composer, you will guide them to generate enchanting music. Join now and showcase your musical talents!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkys-skibidi-titans-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"266\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Game features</h3><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Unique Characters: </strong><span>Each figure is a delight to discover, featuring distinctive designs and humorous animations of the Skibidi characters. Their unique style makes them exotic to play and watch as they perform.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Catchy Soundtrack: </strong><span>The game features a variety of catchy songs, from rock to both normal and horror themes. Each of them is tailored to a particular rhythm that keeps the player engaged.</span></li></ul><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">CREATE MUSIC WITH THE EXOTIC CONCERT BAND</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunkys Skibidi Titans</strong> makes your music-produce dreams come true with easy-to-learn mechanics that players can enjoy. At the bottom of the screen are music boxes that power your Sprunki characters. You just need to drag these items onto your characters. These figures will immediately change into new outfits and play their own music. If you want to put thrilling elements to your compositions, simply click on the last icon to switch to Horror Mode.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Best Rhythm Games</h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-mustard\">Sprunki Mustard</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-night-time\">Sprunki Night Time</a></li></ul>','Sprunkys Skibidi Titans','','private','open','closed','','sprunkys-skibidi-titans','','','2026-07-20 02:22:12','2026-07-20 02:22:12','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunkys-skibidi-titans/',0,'game','',0),(315,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:12','2026-07-20 02:22:12','','sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger-2','','','2026-07-20 02:22:12','2026-07-20 02:22:12','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(316,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:13','2026-07-20 02:22:13','','Sprunki Abgerny Gyatt Burger','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger-3','','','2026-07-20 02:22:13','2026-07-20 02:22:13','',317,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(317,1,'2026-07-20 02:22:13','2026-07-20 02:22:13','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Welcome to <strong>Sprunki Abgerny Gyatt Burger</strong>, a captivating music game where you can unleash your unique tracks and express your personality. This simple gameplay makes it an ideal choice to unwind after a long day. Besides, with its creative element, this platform offers a fantastic playground for musical imagination. Start composing music with your exotic style now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"347\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Enchanting Game Theme</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This creation game draws you into a charming landscape that seems to be the sunset. In the foreground, adorable characters eagerly await your musical creations, their hilarious expressions and darkened chests adding a whimsical touch. In the backdrop, the setting sun gives way to a darkening sky, creating a magical atmosphere for relaxation and inspiration.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Playing <strong>Sprunki Abgerny Gyatt Burger</strong> is simple but intriguing. First, when you access the game, you will see the game’s instructions at the top of the screen. Following these guidelines not only unlocks music boxes but also provides an introduction to basic musical concepts. Once you’ve explored all the music icons, you’re free to create your own melodies in any style you like. With no restrictions on creativity, this playground lets you combine melodies to your heart’s content.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rhythm and Play</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uncover the enchanting blend of rhythm and gameplay in today’s most captivating titles:</p><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sprunki Incredibox</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-night-time\">Sprunki Night Time</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Abgerny Gyatt Burger','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger','','','2026-07-20 02:22:13','2026-07-20 02:22:13','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-abgerny-gyatt-burger/',0,'game','',0),(318,1,'2026-07-20 06:09:54','2026-07-20 06:09:54','','sprunki-scooter-racing-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-scooter-racing-2','','','2026-07-20 06:09:54','2026-07-20 06:09:54','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-scooter-racing-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(319,1,'2026-07-20 06:09:55','2026-07-20 06:09:55','','Sprunki: Scooter Racing!','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-scooter-racing-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:00','2026-07-20 06:10:00','',320,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-scooter-racing.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(320,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:00','2026-07-20 06:10:00','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Welcome to <strong>Sprunki: Scooter Racing!</strong>—a game where Sprunki characters take on the racing genre, creating one of the most exhilarating adventures. With addictive gameplay and stunning 3D graphics, this driving game is the perfect choice for your free time. Can you navigate through unexpected hurdles and secure a spot at the top of the leaderboard? Join the race now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-scooter-racing-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"317\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki: Scooter Racing!</strong> invites you to join the race with nine opponents. In this game, you will take control of Black Sprunki, riding a black scooter and moving forward. Along the way, you’ll encounter numerous challenging obstacles, including sharp turns, barriers and more that test your reflexes and driving skills. Each obstacle requires quick thinking and precise control to overcome. This game offers you several stations during the race. If you crash into any obstacle, you can respawn at the nearest station. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Controls</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To control the character\'s movement, players can use arrow keys. If you need to jump over the barriers or gaps, you can press the spacebar key. </span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">WHO LOVES PLAYING THE GAME</h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Players who have a passion for racing games want to enjoy virtual races with adorable cartoon-style visuals. </span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Individuals who are <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> fans would like to meet Sprunki characters in the new appearance and challenges.</span></li></ul>','Sprunki: Scooter Racing!','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-scooter-racing','','','2026-07-20 06:10:00','2026-07-20 06:10:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-scooter-racing/',0,'game','',0),(321,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:01','2026-07-20 06:10:01','','sprunki-halloween-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-halloween-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:01','2026-07-20 06:10:01','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-halloween-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(322,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:03','2026-07-20 06:10:03','','Sprunki Halloween','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-halloween-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:03','2026-07-20 06:10:03','',323,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-halloween.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(323,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:03','2026-07-20 06:10:03','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>If you crave a spooky Halloween theme, <strong>Sprunki Halloween</strong> is a must-try. This creation game plunges players into an exciting world. In this playground, music and spooky elements collide, creating a fantastic Halloween atmosphere. Prepare to lose yourself in the rhythms of the holiday!</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Halloween Theme</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>One of the game’s standout features is its dynamic Halloween theme. Players can join two distinct music modes: Normal and Horror. While Normal mode delivers lighthearted fun, the true chills await in Horror mode. As the horror mode activates, the bright sky darkens, and the sun sets with dim red lights as the backdrop. This time, <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> figures take on the appearance of various eerie characters, such as mummies, captains, and so on. They promise to give you an unforgettable Halloween experience.</span></p><p><span><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-halloween-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">COMPOSE MUSIC FOR A FASCINATING HOLIDAY </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Halloween</strong> makes gameplay simple and accessible, enhancing player enjoyment with intuitive mechanics. Players can easily select and drag musical icons onto the avatars. All set the stage for a dazzling dance performance. Specifically, Horror mode is triggered by an eerie pumpkin icon, bringing even more festive charm as you select it. Whether you are gearing up for Halloween or seeking a casual gaming escape, this game always provides you with the most excellent experience.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Enjoy Another Option</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unless you want to explore more music games, <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-rejoyed\">Sprunki Rejoyed</a> is an option worth considering.</p>','Sprunki Halloween','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-halloween','','','2026-07-20 06:10:03','2026-07-20 06:10:03','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-halloween/',0,'game','',0),(324,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:04','2026-07-20 06:10:04','','sprunki-fundamental-paper-education-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-fundamental-paper-education-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:04','2026-07-20 06:10:04','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-fundamental-paper-education-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(325,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:06','2026-07-20 06:10:06','','Sprunki Fundamental Paper Education','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-fundamental-paper-education-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:07','2026-07-20 06:10:07','',326,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-fundamental-paper-education.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(326,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:07','2026-07-20 06:10:07','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Fundamental Paper Education</strong> is a unique and fresh version in the series of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> music games. This playground remains the task of generating exotic music from the available ingredients. Each track will echo excitingly, demonstrating your music talents and your creativity. Jump into this music stage now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-fundamental-paper-education-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"379\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fundamental Paper Education Theme</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Playing this creation game, players have the chance to meet charismatic paper characters from the delightful YouTube series “Fundamental Paper Education\". Each of them has a unique voice, mood, and manner of performance, representing particular educational elements. From subjects to students and teachers, all aim to support you in creating the most amazing melodies.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>Sprunki Fundamental Paper Education</strong>, your task is to choose characters and combine them to create a track that will ignite the heart of listeners. Every new pairing transforms the soundtrack into a fresh piece of art and provides you with exciting moments. This innovative game not only enhances your understanding of rhythm and harmony but also encourages creative expression. As you experiment with different characters and sounds, you\'ll discover unique arrangements that resonate with your personal style.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Feel The Beat With Sprunki</h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/\">Sprunki Game</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-2\">Sprunki 2</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Fundamental Paper Education','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-fundamental-paper-education','','','2026-07-20 06:10:07','2026-07-20 06:10:07','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-fundamental-paper-education/',0,'game','',0),(327,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:08','2026-07-20 06:10:08','','sprunki-musical-balls-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-musical-balls-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:08','2026-07-20 06:10:08','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-musical-balls-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(328,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:09','2026-07-20 06:10:09','','Sprunki: Musical Balls!','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-musical-balls-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:09','2026-07-20 06:10:09','',329,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-musical-balls.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(329,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:09','2026-07-20 06:10:09','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sprunki: Musical Balls!</strong> throws you into a delightful playground where the music game and shooting genre meet and combine. This game will take you to meet funny Sprunki characters in a new form and explore exciting melodies, effects and rhythms. Each of your shots will contribute to the exciting atmosphere for you and lift your spirits. Dive into the game and prove your shooting skills in this music adventure today!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-musical-balls-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"369\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAME INSTRUCTION</h2><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Explore the Game’s Mission </h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In <strong>Sprunki: Musical Balls!</strong>, your main task is to shoot Sprunki balloons into identical ones to create a new color. You will have the chance to experience different levels, each featuring its unique goals. Your primary objective is to finish the game’s mission with the number of available balls. The game ends if players run out of balls or fail to complete tasks.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">How to play</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To play this music game, what you need to do is control your mouse to shoot the accessible ball. When the two resemble balls meet each other, the new one will appear. Players can use the power-ups, including bombs and multicolored balls, to make their game more intriguing.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tips and Tricks</h3><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Plan Your Shot: </strong>When you start to shoot a ball, there will be a white line that showcases the ball line. Take advantage of this feature to make a perfect shot.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong>Save the Balls: </strong></strong>Each level has a limited number of balloons available, and they can increase or decrease depending on your shot. Throw two <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> balls of the same color together to create a new one and keep you staying longer in the game!</li></ul><h2>Music Games You’ll Love</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/fnf-vs-jumbo-josh-brah\">FNF vs Jumbo Josh Brah</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/fnf-13th-friday-night-funk-blood\">FNF 13th Friday Night: Funk Blood</a></li></ul>','Sprunki: Musical Balls!','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-musical-balls','','','2026-07-20 06:10:09','2026-07-20 06:10:09','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-musical-balls/',0,'game','',0),(330,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:12','2026-07-20 06:10:12','','Sprunki The Lost File','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-the-lost-file-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:19','2026-07-20 06:10:19','',331,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-lost-file-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(331,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:19','2026-07-20 06:10:19','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Welcome to <strong>Sprunki The Lost File</strong>, a horrifying rhythm game where music becomes a mystery, and every sound opens doors to the unknown. This playground immerses players in a surreal, shadowy atmosphere, blurring the boundaries between reality and illusion. An unsettling sense of mystery permeates every corner, beckoning players to uncover the truth beneath the catastrophic event. Start creating music and explore the secrets now!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>Sprunki The Lost File</strong>, you will try on the role of a conductor who has assembled a unique assembly of Sprunkies—strange and frightening creatures whose essence is embodied in sounds. Your objective is to drag beats, melodies, effects, and rhythms to create music. They will come alive right after you combine them with the musical icon. As you experiment with different combinations, you\'ll uncover hidden layers of sound that reveal the backstory of the Sprunkies. Each session will challenge your creativity, pushing you to discover new melodies that resonate with the truth of their lost lives.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Who Will Love This Game?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>With the eerie music, unsettling visuals and haunting atmosphere, this playground is perfect for those who love a chilling challenge. If you are a fan of horror and rhythm games, step into this mysterious world and uncover the dark secrets within!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top Rhythm Games About Sprunki</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li></ul>','Sprunki The Lost File','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-the-lost-file','','','2026-07-20 06:10:19','2026-07-20 06:10:19','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-the-lost-file/',0,'game','',0),(332,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:21','2026-07-20 06:10:21','','sprunki-cool-as-ice-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-cool-as-ice-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:21','2026-07-20 06:10:21','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-cool-as-ice-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(333,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:22','2026-07-20 06:10:22','','Sprunki Cool As Ice','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-cool-as-ice-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:23','2026-07-20 06:10:23','',334,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-cool-as-ice.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(334,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:23','2026-07-20 06:10:23','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Cool As Ice</strong> is a captivating music game featuring a freezing winter theme. In this rhythm game, you will encounter all the characters in ice blue standing on the frosty stage. By blending characters with musical elements, players can craft immersive songs and create melodies that showcase their unique style. Are you ready for your music-composing journey?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-cool-as-ice-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"380\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Discover Attractive Features</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Winter Theme: </strong><span>The game features characters dressed in winter costumes, each offering unique sounds and visual styles. The sight of blue ice and falling snow evokes a deep sense of winter.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Surprise Animation:</strong><span> Certain character combinations unlock special animations and surprises.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Classic and Horror Theme: </strong><span>Players can switch to the horror theme to enjoy the creepy music at any time.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY<strong> </strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To begin your musical adventure in <strong>Sprunki Cool As Ice</strong>, players have to select a character and send them to the choir to create the unique soundtrack. Each character brings a distinct sound, allowing you to freely combine them for countless musical possibilities. If you want to take a dark turn, simply add the mysterious figure in the lower right corner to unlock eerie, spine-chilling tracks. With every combination, you will discover new harmonies, surprising animations, and the magic of ice-cold music!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Feel the Beat with other Sprunki games!</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-fundamental-paper-education\">Sprunki Fundamental Paper Education</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-scooter-racing\">Sprunki: Scooter Racing!</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-2\">Sprunki Retake 2</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Cool As Ice','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-cool-as-ice','','','2026-07-20 06:10:23','2026-07-20 06:10:23','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-cool-as-ice/',0,'game','',0),(335,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:24','2026-07-20 06:10:24','','Sprunki Phase 777','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-777-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:24','2026-07-20 06:10:24','',336,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-777.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(336,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:24','2026-07-20 06:10:24','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>Sprunki Phase 777</em></strong><span> is a reimagined version of the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a></span><span> series, offering players an exciting opportunity to create spine-chilling soundtracks. Whether you\'re a music enthusiast or a casual player, this game invites you to experiment with beats, effects, vocals, and melodies to compose eerie tracks that reflect your unique style. The game challenges your creativity and musical ear as you craft haunting compositions in a world of mystery.</span></p><h2>Explore the Haunting Sprunki Characters</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In<strong> <em>Sprunki Phase 777</em></strong><span>, you’ll encounter seven eerie characters, each standing under dim red lights, as well as twenty music boxes at the bottom of the screen. Each character has its own mysterious personality, with some whispering in the background while others produce chilling screams. As you interact with them, placing music boxes or mixing elements, these characters undergo eerie transformations, influencing both their visual appearance and the soundtrack you\'re creating.</span></p><h2>Gameplay Overview – Create and Experiment with Sound</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To start crafting your haunting soundtracks in </span><strong><em>Sprunki Phase 777</em></strong><span>, you\'ll need to customize avatars by adding music boxes. These boxes introduce new sound effects, from subtle echoes to intense shrieks, as you combine different icons and sounds. The game provides endless possibilities for experimentation, allowing you to mix and match sounds, adjust rhythms, and create a composition that feels uniquely yours. The more you explore, the more opportunities you’ll have to build your chilling masterpiece.</span></p><h3>How to play</h3><ol style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Customize characters</strong><span>: Start by selecting one of the seven Sprunki characters. Each character has different emotional tones that will affect the atmosphere of the game.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Add music boxes</strong><span>: Drag music boxes from the bottom of the screen and place them on your characters. Each box introduces new sounds, effects, and rhythmic elements to your composition.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Experiment and mix</strong><span>: Play with different combinations of sounds, vocals, and effects. The game allows you to freely experiment, so don’t be afraid to get creative!</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Create your masterpiece</strong><span>: Once you\'ve crafted your track, save it, and share it with the </span><em><span>Sprunki</span></em><span> community or on social media. Show off your spine-chilling compositions to the world.</span></li></ol><h3>Where to play and pricing</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>Sprunki Phase 777</em></strong><span> is available on all browsers</span><span>. The game is free to play, with optional in-app purchases for additional customization options, sound packs, and effects.</span></p><h2>Conclusion</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The revised article now offers readers a clearer understanding of how to play <strong><em>Sprunki Phase 777</em></strong>, what makes the game unique, and how they can get started. The explanations around character customization, the role of music boxes, and the creative freedom within the game are now more specific and understandable. Additionally, the game’s availability and pricing details enhance transparency and provide readers with practical information on where to access the game.</p>','Sprunki Phase 777','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-777','','','2026-07-20 06:10:24','2026-07-20 06:10:24','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-777/',0,'game','',0),(337,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:26','2026-07-20 06:10:26','','Sprunki Sprunked','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sprunked-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:26','2026-07-20 06:10:26','',338,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprunked.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(338,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:26','2026-07-20 06:10:26','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Step into the world of </span><strong><em>Sprunki Sprunked</em></strong><span>, where you can create and shape your own music while interacting with a cast of quirky, customizable characters. Whether you\'re a seasoned music producer or just someone who loves rhythm games, this is your chance to craft unique beats and have fun along the way.</span></p><h2>Enchanting music world</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In </span><strong><em>Sprunki Sprunked</em></strong><span>, you’ll meet a variety of cartoon characters, each with their own musical quirks. These charming hand-drawn characters start on a vibrant stage with blue and green as the primary colors. As you create music, your characters change in appearance, adding new colors and accessories to match the beats you\'re crafting. Their outfits and styles evolve as your tunes progress, making each musical moment feel fresh and fun.</span></p><h2>Gameplay Overview</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>Sprunki Sprunked</em></strong><span> offers two exciting play modes: </span><strong>Normal</strong><span> and </span><strong>Horror</strong><span>. Here’s a breakdown of what to expect:</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Normal Mode</strong><span>: This mode greets you with a lively and colorful atmosphere. The characters wear adorable costumes, and the music you create is light-hearted and fun. It’s a great mode for players who want to focus on music creation without distractions.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Horror Mode</strong><span>: For a darker twist, switch to Horror Mode by clicking the hat icon on any character. When you switch, everything changes: the characters take on creepy, unsettling forms, the stage becomes eerie, and the music shifts to a spooky vibe. This mode adds a challenge by forcing you to maintain rhythm in a more unsettling atmosphere. The eerie visuals and eerie sounds keep you on your toes!</span></li></ul><h3>Music creation and customization</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In </span><strong><em>Sprunki Sprunked</em></strong><span>, you get to create music by combining different beats and sounds using the game’s intuitive interface. As you interact with the characters, their presence influences your music—whether by adding new instruments, changing the tempo, or altering the rhythm. The more you play, the more you unlock, from new instruments to unique character accessories that enhance the music creation experience.</span></p><h3><strong>Where to play</strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><span>Sprunki Sprunked</span></em><span> is available for download on </span><strong>PC</strong><span> and </span><strong>mobile devices</strong><span>. The game is free to play with optional in-game purchases for extra features, such as character customization and unique music packs.</span></p><h3>Get started</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Ready to dive into the rhythm and create your own beats? Play </span><strong><em>Sprunki Sprunked</em></strong><span> now and embark on your music-making adventure. Whether you’re looking for a relaxing time in Normal Mode or a spooky challenge in Horror Mode, </span><strong><em>Sprunki Sprunked</em></strong><span> offers a fun and dynamic way to express yourself through music.</span></p><p>For more tips and updates, check out our community forum or watch gameplay tutorials on how to master music creation in <em>Sprunki Sprunked</em>.</p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rhythm Ready?</h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-the-lost-file\">Sprunki The Lost File</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-3\">Sprunki Phase 3</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Sprunked','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-sprunked','','','2026-07-20 06:10:26','2026-07-20 06:10:26','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-sprunked/',0,'game','',0),(339,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:29','2026-07-20 06:10:29','','Sprunki PopIt','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-popit-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:29','2026-07-20 06:10:29','',340,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-popit.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(340,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:29','2026-07-20 06:10:29','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>Sprunki PopIt</em></strong><span> is the perfect casual game to help you unwind, offering a fun and relaxing experience for players of all ages. With its charming graphics, soothing music, and simple gameplay, <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-popit\">Sprunki PopIt</a></span><span> lets you take a break from the daily grind and immerse yourself in a calming world of bubble-popping fun.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gameplay Overview</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In </span><strong><em>Sprunki PopIt</em></strong><span>, your goal is to pop all the bubbles that appear on the bodies of the adorable <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters. These characters come in different shapes and colors, with bubbles of various sizes. All you need to do is use your mouse to click on the bubbles, popping them to clear the screen and move on to the next level.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>As you progress, new challenges emerge. Watch out for the moving sun and butterflies that drift across the screen. If you accidentally click on them instead of the bubbles, the level will reset, giving you another chance to pop all the bubbles without distractions. It’s a fun and light-hearted way to test your timing and focus.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Why You’ll Love This Game</h3><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Soothing Visuals and Music</strong><span>: The calming graphics and gentle background music make </span><em><span>Sprunki PopIt</span></em><span> the perfect game for relaxation. The vibrant colors and whimsical animations add a touch of joy as you play, helping to create a peaceful atmosphere.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Simple Yet Engaging Gameplay</strong><span>: With easy point-and-click mechanics, </span><em><span>Sprunki PopIt</span></em><span> is incredibly easy to pick up and play. Whether you\'re new to gaming or just looking for a quick way to de-stress, this game offers a refreshing break with minimal effort.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Perfect for Relaxing Moments</strong><span>: Whether you need a mental break, want to unwind after a busy day, or just want to enjoy a soothing game, </span><strong><em>Sprunki PopIt</em></strong><span> provides the perfect escape. The slow-paced, bubble-popping action allows you to relax and enjoy the game at your own pace.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Platform and Accessibility</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>Sprunki PopIt</em></strong><span> is available on both </span><strong>mobile devices</strong><span> and </span><strong>web browsers</strong><span>. The game is free to play, with optional in-app purchases for additional features and customizations. You can easily pick it up and start playing anytime, anywhere—whether you\'re at home or on the go.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Conclusion</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>Sprunki PopIt</em></strong><span> offers an enjoyable and relaxing experience for players looking for a lighthearted game to help them relax. With simple controls, charming visuals, and calming gameplay, it\'s an ideal choice for anyone seeking a peaceful break. Whether you’re popping bubbles for fun or just looking for a stress-free distraction, </span><em><span>Sprunki PopIt</span></em><span> provides the perfect balance of easy fun and tranquility.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Click <strong><em>Sprunki PopIt</em></strong> today and let the soothing challenge begin!</p>','Sprunki PopIt','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-popit','','','2026-07-20 06:10:29','2026-07-20 06:10:29','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-popit/',0,'game','',0),(341,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:31','2026-07-20 06:10:31','','squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2-3','','inherit','open','closed','','squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:31','2026-07-20 06:10:31','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(342,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:32','2026-07-20 06:10:32','','Squid Sprunki Shooter Game 2','','inherit','open','closed','','squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:32','2026-07-20 06:10:32','',343,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(343,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:32','2026-07-20 06:10:32','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Squid Sprunki Shooter Game 2</strong> is a thrilling rhythm-based action game that blends fast-paced shooting mechanics with beat synchronization. Inspired by Squid Game and Sprunki characters, this innovative shooting experience challenges your precision and reflexes. Immerse yourself in the action asn test your timing in every shot!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"397\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">A Perfect Fusion of Action Rhythm</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This game merges the intense competition of Squid Game with the charm of Sprunki. Featuring familiar characters like Squid soldiers and Sprunki, it delivers a high-energy shooting experience that keeps you on your toes.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY MECHANICS</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Squid Sprunki Shooter Game 2</strong> introduces a unique synchronization system where every action—shooting, dodging, and reloading—aligns with the beat. This musical twist adds a fresh dynamic to traditional shooter gameplay, making each battle feel like a performance.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In this game, you will assume as a shooter - Sprunki, facing off against all Squid game soldiers. As you start a level, your character automatically moves forward, aiming at targets, Squid game soldiers. There will be a crosshair from your weapon guiding your shots. Your mission is to click the mouse at the right moment to take down enemies. This game is a platform leaving no mistakes! Failing to shoot or missing any Squid soldiers leads to instant defeat.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">New Sprunki Games to Try</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-777\">Sprunki Phase 777</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-cool-as-ice\">Sprunki Cool As Ice</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-musical-balls\">Sprunki: Musical Balls!</a></li></ul>','Squid Sprunki Shooter Game 2','','private','open','closed','','squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:32','2026-07-20 06:10:32','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2/',0,'game','',0),(344,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:33','2026-07-20 06:10:33','','sprunki-pyramixed-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-pyramixed-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:33','2026-07-20 06:10:33','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-pyramixed-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(345,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:34','2026-07-20 06:10:34','','Sprunki Pyramixed','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-pyramixed-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:34','2026-07-20 06:10:34','',346,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-pyramixed.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(346,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:34','2026-07-20 06:10:34','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Pyramixed</strong> is a unique innovation of the popular rhythm game, Incredibox Sprunki, with more techno sounds and effects. This version still plunges you into the enchanting music playground where you take the role of composer. With your imagination and music talents, you will create immersive soundtracks in your own desire. Get ready to combine music now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-pyramixed-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"378\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Creating music in <strong>Sprunki Pyramixed</strong> is straightforward with incredible available ingredients. They are beats, effects, vocals and melodies uncovered behind the colorful icon at the bottom of the screen. With simple clicks and drags, your captivating creations will echo, bringing music to the boring atmosphere. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In addition to the Normal mode, this version still offers the horror theme. As you wear the iconic black bowler hat on any character, the dark force will wake up and destroy the enchanting atmosphere. Everything from the background to <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters and even music will change, adding a creepy layout to this game. You can combine music with these new effects, immersing yourself in eerie sounds. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Two More Icons</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>When you enter the games, you will see two locks at the middle top of the screen. These locks hide an intriguing question! Answering this question correctly, two mysterious musical icons will unlock, adding more choices for your creations.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Expand Your Sprunki Game List</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-night-time\">Sprunki Night Time</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-mustard\">Sprunki Mustard</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Pyramixed','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-pyramixed','','','2026-07-20 06:10:34','2026-07-20 06:10:34','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-pyramixed/',0,'game','',0),(347,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:36','2026-07-20 06:10:36','','sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:36','2026-07-20 06:10:36','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(348,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:37','2026-07-20 06:10:37','','Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:38','2026-07-20 06:10:38','',349,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(349,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:38','2026-07-20 06:10:38','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends</strong> invites you to the colorful fairytale. In this creation game, you seem to step into the enchanting music world and meet charming animals. In the company of these adorable characters, you will start your music journey, taking the first step toward your career. It sounds intriguing, doesn’t it? Why don\'t you try now? Your “companions” are waiting for you to create unique soundtracks!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"303\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Iconic Designs of Music Players</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Instead of encountering lovely Sprunki characters, this music game lets you meet seven adorable characters with two rabbit teeth. They are sitting on the ground and waiting for you to make the atmosphere chaotic. As you combine your characters with music icons, they immediately put on colorful costumes of animals. Blending with the appealing purple backdrop, you seem to immerse yourself in the fairy forest. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends</strong> shares the same click-and-drag mechanics as other <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> games. Your mission is simple: click on your favorite musical boxes and combine them with seven characters on the stages. The game does not offer restrictions, allowing you to edit until your pleasant soundtrack is born. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Moreover, you can completely enjoy Horror mode with the last musical icon on the list. As you style any character with this box, the theme game will change and put you into the spine-thrilling atmosphere. </span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top Sprunki Games to Check Out</h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-sprinkle\">Sprunki Sprinkle</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends','','','2026-07-20 06:10:38','2026-07-20 06:10:38','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends/',0,'game','',0),(350,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:40','2026-07-20 06:10:40','','sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:40','2026-07-20 06:10:40','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(351,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:41','2026-07-20 06:10:41','','Sprunki But Everyone is Alive','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:42','2026-07-20 06:10:42','',352,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(352,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:42','2026-07-20 06:10:42','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki But Everyone is Alive</strong> is a cool twist on the regular music game, <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a>. In this version, you will encounter all Sprunki characters who are super lively and full of energy. They appear on the screen with several pains but have the wound bandaged with white gauze. On the bright and clear backdrop, your characters await you to release amazing songs, marking your unique style. Get ready to compose music now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"373\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>Sprunki But Everyone is Alive</strong>, players will have the chance to produce their own soundtracks from 20 distinct sounds. Your objective is to combine music boxes with Sprunki characters on the screen and then wait for music to echo. In addition, this rhythm game allows you to save your creations and enjoy them later. Besides, you can fully share your product with other players, showcasing your creations and expressing joy.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">A Little Eerie</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Although all Sprunki characters are alive, the black bowler hat symbols for the horror mod exist. As you style your character with this mod, a little creepy sound will echo and accompany you throughout your music journey. Yet, your character will not change a lot apart from more white gauze on their body.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Discover More Sprunki Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-x-dandys-world\">Sprunki x Dandy’s World</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-mr-fun-computers-incredibox-mod\">Sprunki Mr Fun Computers Incredibox Mod</a></li></ul>','Sprunki But Everyone is Alive','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive','','','2026-07-20 06:10:42','2026-07-20 06:10:42','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive/',0,'game','',0),(353,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:45','2026-07-20 06:10:45','','Sprunki Phase 6 Definitive','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-6-definitive-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:50','2026-07-20 06:10:50','',354,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-6-definitive-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(354,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:50','2026-07-20 06:10:50','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Phase 6 Definitive</strong> is a groundbreaking music-creation game that marries inventive beat-making with a dark, atmospheric twist. This fan-made version invites you into a mysterious realm with haunting characters and unsettling melodies converging to redefine creative expression. Are you ready to explore a spooky world where every note sends shivers down your spine?</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Staying true to its core musical mechanics, <strong>Sprunki Phase 6 Definitive</strong> elevates the experience with a grimmer, more immersive vibe. In this rhythm game, your task is to arrange unique characters, each contributing layers of melody and beat, to craft one-a-kind-of eerie tracks. As you explore various character combinations, you\'ll discover distinctive soundscapes that can evoke chills. With each creation, the haunting visuals and eerie sound effects will immerse you deeper into the world of Sprunki, challenging your creativity and rhythm skills like never before.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Who Does Enjoy This Game?</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>This game is a perfect match for those who find joy in mixing artistic creativity with a hint of horror. </span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Music lovers who appreciate a unique, atmospheric twist will relish the character of constructing haunting tunes amid an eerie backdrop.</span></li></ul><h2><span>More Phase, More Fun</span></h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-777\">Sprunki Phase 777</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><span><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></span></li></ul>','Sprunki Phase 6 Definitive','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-6-definitive','','','2026-07-20 06:10:50','2026-07-20 06:10:50','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-6-definitive/',0,'game','',0),(355,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:51','2026-07-20 06:10:51','','sprunki-music-scary-beat-box-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-music-scary-beat-box-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:51','2026-07-20 06:10:51','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-music-scary-beat-box-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(356,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:52','2026-07-20 06:10:52','','Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-music-scary-beat-box-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:52','2026-07-20 06:10:52','',357,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-music-scary-beat-box.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(357,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:52','2026-07-20 06:10:52','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box</strong> is an addictive rhythm game where rhythm meets a chilling adventure. This music game allows you to create music freely to express your imagination and personality with different modes. Each mode will present a fresh and exciting musical challenge, featuring a comfortable playground. Brace yourself for the ultimate, intriguing music-creating journey now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-music-scary-beat-box-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"389\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dive into Four Music Modes</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The Rhythm Mode:</strong><span> You will encounter seven spine-chilling Sprunki characters standing under the rainy and stormy stage. This version features 19 music boxes, in which some require watching short videos to open.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The Monster Mode:</strong><span> All characters will be on the red dim light backdrop with a haunting appearance. As you customize them with music boxes, there will be spine-chilling monsters popping up with creepy sounds.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The Joker Mode:</strong><span> This time you will encounter seven jokers and have the chance to create delightful soundtracks with only eight musical icons. When you wake up, your character will play music; they will change their outfit and move heads according to music.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The Beat Mode: </strong><span>Players will create songs with a regular Sprunki game without horror elements. This mode offers 19 sounds and requires you to watch a short video to unlock only Mr. Computer.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To play <strong>Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box</strong>, you can follow the steps below: </span></p><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Choose mode: </strong><span>Players need to choose one among four music modes: Rhythm, Monster, Joker, and Beat.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Combine music:</strong><span> This game retains the click-and-drag music! You have to use your mouse to click on your favorite sounds and then style any characters. </span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong>Swift sounds: </strong></strong><span>You can endlessly change music boxes until the most pleasant soundtrack release.</span></li></ul><h2><span>Love Sprunki? Check out more</span></h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive\">Sprunki But Everyone is Alive</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2\">Squid Sprunki Shooter Game 2</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-pyramixed\">Sprunki Pyramixed</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-music-scary-beat-box','','','2026-07-20 06:10:52','2026-07-20 06:10:52','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-music-scary-beat-box/',0,'game','',0),(358,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:54','2026-07-20 06:10:54','','sprunki-puppets-3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-puppets-3','','','2026-07-20 06:10:54','2026-07-20 06:10:54','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-puppets-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(359,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:55','2026-07-20 06:10:55','','Sprunki Puppets','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-puppets-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:57','2026-07-20 06:10:57','',360,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-puppets-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(360,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:57','2026-07-20 06:10:57','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Puppets</strong> welcomes you to the sparkling festive stage and invites you to compose immersive music creations. This rhythm game will deliver you into the colorful Christmas theme, with puppet characters creating a delightful soundtrack for this holiday. Let your own music product echo this popular festival!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-puppets-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"352\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Discover Novel Features</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Funny puppet characters</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Enchanting sounds and animation</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Christmas them with in-game sparkling LEDs</span></li></ul><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To create music in <strong>Sprunki Puppets</strong>, players need to add angry puppet characters to the avatars on the scene. Firstly, you need to choose your favorite music boxes from the 20 icons. Then, you simply click on these musical icons and arrange them onto <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters on the screen. As the avatar\'s appearance changes, the sounds will also adjust accordingly. That time, with a simple click on any body, you can remove its sound and alter it with another one. Simply continue until you find the best tracks to release your unique songs. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unlock the Horror Mode</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In order to engage in the horror theme in this version, players need to drag the question mark icon onto an avatar. This mode requires you to watch a video to explore the mystery. As the horror mode runs, this game will add haunting elements to puppets, the Christmas stage, and music.</span></p><h2>Explore Music Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends\">Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-pyramixed\">Sprunki Pyramixed</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Puppets','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-puppets','','','2026-07-20 06:10:57','2026-07-20 06:10:57','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-puppets/',0,'game','',0),(361,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:58','2026-07-20 06:10:58','','sprunki-max-design-pro-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-max-design-pro-2','','','2026-07-20 06:10:58','2026-07-20 06:10:58','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-max-design-pro-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(362,1,'2026-07-20 06:10:59','2026-07-20 06:10:59','','Sprunki Max Design Pro','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-max-design-pro-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:00','2026-07-20 06:11:00','',363,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-max-design-pro.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(363,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:00','2026-07-20 06:11:00','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Max Design Pro</strong> is an innovative music creation game that brings together the imaginative world of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> with the creative flair of Max Design Pro. This game invites you to explore a dynamic universe where you can craft music from available ingredients, allowing endless creative possibilities. Whether you are a seasoned musician or a newbie, the game puts you into an engaging experience that blends fun and creativity.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-max-design-pro-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"382\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Creative World of Max Design Pro</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This game features a super-fun fusion of Sprunki with popular animation Max Design Pro. Originating from Belarus, Max Design Pro is a popular YouTuber known for his animated series featuring Max the Monkey and its colorful family. This ensemble includes memorable characters, including Max, Jimmy, Hope, Martha, Jeff, Angus, Billy, Duncan, Nugget, and Evil Max. Each character steps into the music game with a distinct music talent, enriching the game’s narrative and gameplay. Their unique elements not only add charm and depth to the story but also inspire players to experiment with different combinations.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY INSTRUCTION</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The gameplay in <strong>Sprunki Max Design Pro</strong> is both intuitive and captivating, featuring two distinct modes: <strong><em>Normal</em> </strong>and <strong><em>Horror</em></strong>. In the <strong><em>Normal</em></strong> mode, players can immerse themselves in a world of delightful sounds and charming characters. Every interaction in this mode is designed to evoke a sense of wonder and creativity. On the other hand, the <strong><em>Horror</em></strong> mode transforms the ambience into one of eerie soundscapes and unsettling characters. This theme also provides a thrilling experience that encourages players to think creatively.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Have Fun with Sprunki</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-4\">Sprunki Phase 4</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Max Design Pro','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-max-design-pro','','','2026-07-20 06:11:00','2026-07-20 06:11:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-max-design-pro/',0,'game','',0),(364,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:01','2026-07-20 06:11:01','','endless-sprunki-2','','inherit','open','closed','','endless-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:01','2026-07-20 06:11:01','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/endless-sprunki-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(365,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:02','2026-07-20 06:11:02','','Endless Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','endless-sprunki-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:02','2026-07-20 06:11:02','',366,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/endless-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(366,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:02','2026-07-20 06:11:02','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Endless Sprunki</strong> is an intriguing arcade game that invites you into a charming, skill-testing realm. This casual game provides an immersive experience that immerses you in a lively world. In this dynamic playground, your goal is to launch a Sprunki character across various platforms while keeping control and momentum. Every move challenges your accuracy and strategy—how far can you send your Sprunki on this magical journey?</span></p><p><span><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/endless-sprunki-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"250\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p><span>To play <strong>Endless Sprunki</strong>, you can follow the step-by-step instructions below:</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Control Mechanics: </strong><span>Direct your Sprunki by clicking the screen, release your shot, then release to give it a boost. Each click launches your character toward the next platform.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Aiming Strategy: </strong><span>Carefully aim at the upcoming platform, considering both its distance and height. Your precision in targeting is key to progressing.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Power Adjustment: </strong><span>Utilize the hold-and-release system to set the velocity of your shot.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Progression: </strong><span>Every successful launch propels you to a platform with new challenges. Mastering the mechanics not only helps you achieve more platforms but also boosts your overall score.</span></li></ul><h3>Tips and Tricks</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Master the Controls: </strong><span>Focus on perfecting your timing and release technique to maximize your shot accuracy.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Gauge Distances: </strong><span>Monitor the distance between platforms to ascertain the appropriate force required for each launch.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Watch for Cues: </strong><span>Notice the visual details in each platform’s position; they can provide hints on adjusting your aim for upcoming throws.</span></li><li><strong><strong>Practice Makes Perfect: </strong></strong>Every attempt is an opportunity to refine your skills and sharpen your instincts. Keep practicing to reach greater distances and higher scores.</li></ul><h2>Sprunki Game Picks</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-puppets\">Sprunki Puppets</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-777\">Sprunki Phase 777</a></li></ul>','Endless Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','endless-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:11:02','2026-07-20 06:11:02','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/endless-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(367,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:04','2026-07-20 06:11:04','','huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box-2','','inherit','open','closed','','huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:04','2026-07-20 06:11:04','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(368,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:05','2026-07-20 06:11:05','','Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box','','inherit','open','closed','','huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:05','2026-07-20 06:11:05','',369,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(369,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:05','2026-07-20 06:11:05','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Welcome to the fantastic realm of <strong>Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box</strong> to experience the excitement of creating music on different stages. This rhythm game introduces you to three exciting musical modes, each with unique soundscapes, themes, and Sprunki appearances. Sharing the same gameplay and mechanics, this platform allows you to create music from an array of sounds. Create music and let your creation express your imagination!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"370\"></span></p><h2>GAMEPLAY DESCRIPTION</h2><h3>How to play</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Right out of the start in <strong>Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box</strong>, you will encounter three music modes: Health, Ice, and Bad man. The very first step is to choose your favorite stages. Each mode features seven characters and enables you to fuse music icons with them. This music game does not offer too many rules and restrictions, encouraging you to showcase your music talents and creativity.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The game contains several hidden sounds, which you must unlock by enjoying the video. Simply click and spend a little time; you can have more choices for your creations.</span></p><h3>Explore Three Modes</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Health:</strong><span> This mode seems to be a version of “<a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-but-everyone-is-alive\">Sprunki But Everyone is Alive</a>” without the horror theme. This is because when you style your character, they will appear with a little white gauze on their body parts.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ice: </strong><span>This version plunges you into the frosty atmosphere. From Sprunki characters to music boxes and stages, bring icy blue colors. Additionally, players create creepy soundtracks due to its horror mode.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong>Bad Man: </strong></strong>The stage immerses your characters in a fresh environment, accompanied by captivating music. Besides, styling any character with a black bowler hat adds eerie elements to the scene.</li></ul><h2>Top Rhythm Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-max-design-pro\">Sprunki Max Design Pro</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends\">Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends</a></li></ul>','Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box','','private','open','closed','','huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box','','','2026-07-20 06:11:05','2026-07-20 06:11:05','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box/',0,'game','',0),(370,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:07','2026-07-20 06:11:07','','squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle-2','','inherit','open','closed','','squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:07','2026-07-20 06:11:07','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(371,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:09','2026-07-20 06:11:09','','Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle','','inherit','open','closed','','squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:10','2026-07-20 06:11:10','',372,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(372,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:10','2026-07-20 06:11:10','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle</strong> is an exhilarating blend of Sprunki characters, Squid Game soldiers, and FNF gameplay. In this rhythm game, you will dive into the electrifying music showdown between Oren (Orange Sprunki) and a squid game soldier. Sharing the same mechanic with FNF mode, the mission is to hit the scrolling arrows in time to score points. Dive into this super-fun music game now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"332\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Charming Stage</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>When you enter this <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game, you will encounter your two characters in front of a beautiful merry-go-round. They are dancing while waiting for you to start your music battles. As you start your game, Oren and the Squid Game Soldier will dance with music, creating a delightful atmosphere.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle</strong> features only two songs: Mingle Song (from Squid Game) and Sprunki Incredibox. You need to choose one between them to start your music battle. In order to play this game, you will use the arrow keys to repeat arrows when they scroll down the screen. When you hit the arrows at the right moment, the game will count your scores. As the game ends, this music game rewards you with coins which can be spent upgrading the heath regeneration, power regeneration, Power bar active start and cash gain.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top Music Picks</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-puppets\">Sprunki Puppets</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-sprunked\">Sprunki Sprunked</a></li></ul>','Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle','','private','open','closed','','squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle','','','2026-07-20 06:11:10','2026-07-20 06:11:10','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle/',0,'game','',0),(373,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:11','2026-07-20 06:11:11','','sprunki-jigsaw-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-jigsaw-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:11','2026-07-20 06:11:11','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-jigsaw-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(374,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:13','2026-07-20 06:11:13','','Sprunki Jigsaw','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-jigsaw-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:14','2026-07-20 06:11:14','',375,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-jigsaw.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(375,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:14','2026-07-20 06:11:14','<p><span><strong>Sprunki Jigsaw</strong> is a simple yet addictive puzzle game that takes you to the colorful and fun world of adorable sprunks. In this game, you will take on the exciting challenge of arranging Sprunki images. With the combination of entertaining and mental exercises, the game aims to enhance your patience and problem-solving skills. Prepare yourself in this exciting game now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-jigsaw-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"294\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Sprunki Jigsaw is a free online platform that allows you to play endlessly. This puzzle game challenges players with a total of 15 groovy Sprunki characters. In order to start your journey, you need to choose a Sprunki image first. This brain game enables you to choose the difficulty form: 16 pieces, then 36 pieces, 64 pieces, and the hardest one, 100 pieces. Your task is to arrange the puzzle into a perfect Spunki picture as fast as possible.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This puzzle does not feature any restrictions, creating you a free playground to explore your problem-solving skills. If you are a beginner, you can start with the easiest stage of 16 pieces and then improve your abilities with higher levels.</span></p><h2>Discover the Game’s Benefits</h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Relax and Unwind: </strong><span>Engage in the free playground with no rules.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Enhance Attention:</strong><span> Train your eye to pick up slight differences in color and shape while collecting pieces to put them together.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Forster Patience:</strong><span> Calm down and be patient as you find the pieces for suitable positions.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong>Improve Problem-solving Skills: </strong></strong>Think strategically to take different approaches to try and solve a problem.</li></ul><h2>Sprunki Fun Zone<strong><br></strong></h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Jigsaw','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-jigsaw','','','2026-07-20 06:11:14','2026-07-20 06:11:14','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-jigsaw/',0,'game','',0),(376,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:16','2026-07-20 06:11:16','','blast-sprunki-2','','inherit','open','closed','','blast-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:16','2026-07-20 06:11:16','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/blast-sprunki-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(377,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:17','2026-07-20 06:11:17','','Blast Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','blast-sprunki-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:17','2026-07-20 06:11:17','',378,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/blast-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(378,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:17','2026-07-20 06:11:17','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Blast Sprunki</strong> is an addictive puzzle game that brings you to the intriguing meeting with Oren (Orange Sprunki). You will assist your “companion” to escape from a vibrant, explosive-filled world. The mission is to strategically place explosives to guide Oren through obstacles, reaching the safe zone in as few attempts as possible. Blast your way to victory now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/blast-sprunki-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"330\"></span></p><h2>What Makes The Game Unique?</h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Face increasingly complex challenges with tricky enemies and intricate puzzles.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Encourages creativity and strategic thinking with well-placed explosions.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>A variety of levels that can retry at any moment. </span></li></ul><h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Blast Sprunki</strong> challenges you with 30 thrilling levels, each offering up to three stars based on your performance. This game allows players to click on the screen to place explosives strategically, launching Oren in the desired direction. Throughout the levels, stages become more challenging with obstacles like towering walls and narrow safe zones. With unlimited retries, you can refine your approach and aim for a perfect score.</span></p><h2>Explore More Sprunki Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle\">Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-sprunki-shooter-game-2\">Squid Sprunki Shooter Game 2</a></li></ul>','Blast Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','blast-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:11:17','2026-07-20 06:11:17','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/blast-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(379,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:19','2026-07-20 06:11:19','','sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:19','2026-07-20 06:11:19','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(380,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:21','2026-07-20 06:11:21','','Sprunki x SepBox – V1 Steel Factory','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:22','2026-07-20 06:11:22','',381,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(381,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:22','2026-07-20 06:11:22','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki x SepBox – V1 Steel Factory</strong> is an innovative music creation game that blends factory elements with creative composition. This game presents a factory-themed experience, allowing players to craft music using available sound effects. Create music and unleash your imagination now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"369\"> </p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki x SepBox – V1 Steel Factory</strong> shares the same mechanics and gameplay with other <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> games. Firstly, you need to select music boxes from a variety of machine-inspired icons, then arrange them onto the characters. Players can switch music boxes freely to create the most pleasant composition. The game also allows you to export your creations and share them with other players.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Who Should Play This Game?</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This music game is not only perfect for music enthusiasts but also for those who want to express their creative minds. Besides, the factory theme also captivates those who are fascinated with machinery and industrial design.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Another Option</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you love more Sprunki games, check out <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-musical-balls\">Sprunki: Musical Balls!</a> or <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-sprinkle\">Sprunki Sprinkle</a>. Have fun!</p>','Sprunki x SepBox – V1 Steel Factory','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory','','','2026-07-20 06:11:22','2026-07-20 06:11:22','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-x-sepbox-v1-steel-factory/',0,'game','',0),(382,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:23','2026-07-20 06:11:23','','sprunki-babies-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-babies-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:23','2026-07-20 06:11:23','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-babies-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(383,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:24','2026-07-20 06:11:24','','Sprunki Babies','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-babies-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:25','2026-07-20 06:11:25','',384,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-babies.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(384,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:25','2026-07-20 06:11:25','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Babies</strong> welcomes you into the world of music and creativity, where your minds can explore the magic of sound. This creation game invites players to craft their own unique melodies, making their imagination the ultimate instrument. Designed with charming graphics, replacing intensity with joy, this game offers an engaging experience filled with bright visuals and lively sounds. Dive into the game and bring music to life with your creativity now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-babies-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"380\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adorable Sprunki Characters and Charming World</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Set in a vibrant and cheerful world, this fan-made version provides a funny and nurturing environment where children can explore their basics of music and rhythm. Instead of overwhelming challenges, the game focuses on pure enjoyment, using colorful visuals and enchanting sounds to captivate young players.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>Sprunki Babies</strong>, you will meet an adorable cast of characters—little <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> with unique voices and distinctive performance styles. The playful movement and captivating sounds create an irresistible musical experience that captivates players from the first note. The fun begins as you mix and match these endearing characters to craft one-of-a-kind musical masterpieces. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This game features 20 music tone icons without the <strong>horror</strong> theme. The black music box will add a little creepy sound to the environment, as you customize any character with this box.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fun Challenges with Sprunki</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-max-design-pro\">Sprunki Max Design Pro</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/huggy-mix-sprunki-music-box\">Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Babies','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-babies','','','2026-07-20 06:11:25','2026-07-20 06:11:25','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-babies/',0,'game','',0),(385,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:27','2026-07-20 06:11:27','','sprunki-playground-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-playground-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:27','2026-07-20 06:11:27','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-playground-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(386,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:28','2026-07-20 06:11:28','','Sprunki Playground','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-playground-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:28','2026-07-20 06:11:28','',387,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-playground.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(387,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:28','2026-07-20 06:11:28','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Playground</strong> is an exhilarating arcade game that transforms the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> universe into a dynamic sandbox. This platform allows players to create their own intense wars using available ingredients. With your creativity, battles between two forces of Sprunki will emerge under your magical hands. Jump into the game and let your imagination create extreme wars. Launch the game and start imaging extreme scenarios.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-playground-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"318\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Novel Features</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Various characters: </strong><span>Choose from a variety of Sprunki characters such as monsters, zombies, and so forth.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>A wide collection </strong><span>of weapons: Equip your characters with guns, shotguns, bombs, rockets and more.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Customization</strong><span>: Style Sprunki characters from different kinds of outfits, such as medic outfits, builder’s cap, and other gear.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Construction</strong><span>: Create strong buildings to protect <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> from the attack.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY<strong> </strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Playground</strong> is an addictive game that features no restrictions and fewer rules to maximize players’ experience. This game combines creativity, strategy and entertainment, allowing you to freely express your imagination. You will start from basic, building two strong forces of Sprunki and monsters , then equip them with in-game weapons to maximize the battles. Besides, this game allows you to customize your characters with virtual clothes and construct buildings, adding exhilaration and thrill to the wars.</span></p>','Sprunki Playground','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-playground','','','2026-07-20 06:11:28','2026-07-20 06:11:28','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-playground/',0,'game','',0),(388,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:30','2026-07-20 06:11:30','','Sprunki Phase 1','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-1-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:36','2026-07-20 06:11:36','',389,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-1-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(389,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:36','2026-07-20 06:11:36','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Phase 1</strong> is an addictive music creation game redesigned from the popular music game Sprunki Incredibox. This version still plunges you into the role of a music producer, crafting music from available dynamic sounds. Besides, this game allows players to immerse themselves in their creations with new character designs and visuals. Utilize your creativity and musical talent to combine music today!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Creepy Elements on a Bright Setting</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This fan-made version does not feature the horror theme. Players will encounter <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> on the bright theme with dynamic and funny sounds. Yet, here are several highlighted features in Sprunki’s design. Some appear with the original appearance, while Raddy, Clukr, Oren, Owakcx, Garnold, Tunner, and Sky have some eerie features.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To play <strong>Sprunki Phase 1</strong>, you need to use the mouse. Your task is to drag and drop the 19 different tone icons listed under the screen for the characters. Players can freely prove their creativity by combining different notes. This game enables you to switch music boxes endlessly without any rules. Then, you can customize your characters until you are pleased with your product.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Another Game</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the Sprunki Phase series, check out <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a> because of its fame. Have a great time!</p>','Sprunki Phase 1','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-1','','','2026-07-20 06:11:36','2026-07-20 06:11:36','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-1/',0,'game','',0),(390,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:38','2026-07-20 06:11:38','','sprunki-retake-deluxe-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-deluxe-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:38','2026-07-20 06:11:38','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-deluxe-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(391,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:39','2026-07-20 06:11:39','','Sprunki Retake Deluxe','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-deluxe-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:39','2026-07-20 06:11:39','',392,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-deluxe.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(392,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:39','2026-07-20 06:11:39','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Get into <strong>Sprunki Retake Deluxe</strong> and brace yourself for the exhilarating music journey! Step into the shoes of a music creator; you take on the mission of expressing your imagination and bringing immersive music to life. Each soundtrack represents your style and personality, adding such an iconic element never found anywhere else. Compose music to become a real musician now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-retake-deluxe-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"325\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Get Lost in the World of Retake Deluxe</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This fan-made music game adds tons of new characters for players to use in the music-making adventure. One of the cool additions is characters stepping out from the FNF game: Boyfriend and Girlfriend. Besides, this game also introduces the appearance of three characters from DeviantSemarys and others.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Retake Deluxe</strong> introduces the participants of 34 musical icons, each featuring unique sounds. To make your music creations, you need to combine these notes with the seven characters to hear the voices and beats. Players can play around by mixing and matching these melodies to create the most beautiful song. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Like most of Sprunki\'s games, this fan-made music game also features an eerie theme. Yet, that time you\'ll notice an icon of a black hat among various music boxes. Drag the sounds to customize any avatar, you can switch into the horror theme.</span></p><h2 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Explore More Games In Sprunki World</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-2\">Sprunki <span>Retake 2</span></a></li></ul>','Sprunki Retake Deluxe','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-retake-deluxe','','','2026-07-20 06:11:39','2026-07-20 06:11:39','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-retake-deluxe/',0,'game','',0),(393,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:41','2026-07-20 06:11:41','','Dandy World Tycoon','','inherit','open','closed','','dandy-world-tycoon-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:41','2026-07-20 06:11:41','',394,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/dandy-world-tycoon.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(394,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:41','2026-07-20 06:11:41','Jump into the vibrant realm of Dandy World Tycoon and get ready to become a real businessman! Start from a production line and go to a giant factory!','Dandy World Tycoon','','private','open','closed','','dandy-world-tycoon','','','2026-07-20 06:11:41','2026-07-20 06:11:41','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/dandy-world-tycoon/',0,'game','',0),(395,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:43','2026-07-20 06:11:43','','sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:43','2026-07-20 06:11:43','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(396,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:43','2026-07-20 06:11:43','','Sprunki: The Musical Coloring Book','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:44','2026-07-20 06:11:44','',397,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(397,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:44','2026-07-20 06:11:44','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/casual.games\">casual</a> game <strong>Sprunki: The Musical Coloring Book</strong> invites you to a world bustling with bright color and endless fun! Step into the boots of a talented artist, you will have the opportunity to experience an exciting journey where every brushstroke brings fabulous characters to life. Your magical touch will unleash colorful and dynamic pictures that showcase your color-matching skills, creativity, and even your personality. Jump into this game and customize Sprunki with available colors now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Check Out the Highlight Elements</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>A diverse color collection: </strong><span>This game presents various colors that aim to expand your choice and explore your matching color ability.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Different kinds of brushes:</strong><span> From pencils and crayons to riggers and more, all are available, proving your painting journey.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>A large number of pictures:</strong><span> You will have the chance to encounter many characters from the Sprunki world. Color and customize them according to their original appearance or express your creativity.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Playing <strong>Sprunki: The Musical Coloring Book</strong> is simple yet addictive, even for your kids.</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Choose your favorite image of Sprunki.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Start your painting journey by selecting colors on the left panel of the screen.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Look at the bottom of the screen to choose your needed brushes.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Adjust the picture size as you want with the “+“ and “-” buttons on the right panel.</span></li></ul><h2>Top Sprunki Games to Try</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle\">Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-poppy-playtime-mod\">Sprunki - POPPY PLAYTIME (MOD)</a></li></ul>','Sprunki: The Musical Coloring Book','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book','','','2026-07-20 06:11:44','2026-07-20 06:11:44','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book/',0,'game','',0),(398,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:46','2026-07-20 06:11:46','','sprunki-launch-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-launch-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:46','2026-07-20 06:11:46','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-launch-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(399,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:47','2026-07-20 06:11:47','','Sprunki Launch','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-launch-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:47','2026-07-20 06:11:47','',400,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-launch.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(400,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:47','2026-07-20 06:11:47','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sprunki Launch</strong> drops players into a wild, addictive arcade ride. A brave hero, Sprunki, soars through creepy landscapes. His bold mission? Smashing zombie heads with style. Each level mixes fast action, smart strategy, and spooky vibes. Players fling Sprunki, dodge sneaky obstacles, and aim for epic combos. Haunted settings grow tougher, but the thrill keeps rising. Victory comes when every zombie head explodes in this casual, skill-packed game.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-launch-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"352\"></p><h2>How Players Win Big</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Players kick off by aiming <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a>’s trusty catapult. A quick mouse drag or finger tap sets the angle. Power builds fast, so they must release at the right moment. Sprunki flies, and zombie heads shatter on impact. Levels get trickier, yet restarts help sharpen skills. Power-ups pop up, and players should grab them for boosts. Precise shots can rack up massive scores in this undead showdown.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sneaky Tips for Top Scores</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Scout each level first, because zombie heads hide cleverly. Adjust angles slowly, or shots might miss completely. Power-ups shine, so players must use them wisely. Rushing fails often, but patience wins big. Obstacles shift, and spotting patterns boosts success. Experimenting works, especially when barriers get wild. Practice makes players unstoppable in this spooky challenge.</p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Why It’s a Blast</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sprunki Launch</strong> blends action and brainy fun seamlessly. Eerie landscapes ramp up fast, keeping players hooked. Physics feel real, so launches stay satisfying. Special boosts shake things up, and obstacles test skills. Mystical vibes pull players into Sprunki’s world. Ready for a casual, thrilling ride? Jump in and smash those zombies now!</p><h2>Other Hot Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/dandy-world-tycoon\">Dandy World Tycoon</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-playground\">Sprunki Playground</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Launch','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-launch','','','2026-07-20 06:11:47','2026-07-20 06:11:47','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-launch/',0,'game','',0),(401,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:49','2026-07-20 06:11:49','','corruptbox-2-but-sprunki-2','','inherit','open','closed','','corruptbox-2-but-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:49','2026-07-20 06:11:49','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/corruptbox-2-but-sprunki-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(402,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:50','2026-07-20 06:11:50','','Corruptbox 2 But Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','corruptbox-2-but-sprunki-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:51','2026-07-20 06:11:51','',403,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/corruptbox-2-but-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(403,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:51','2026-07-20 06:11:51','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Corruptbox 2 But Sprunki</strong> is a perfect music game for horror-seekers and music lovers who are keen on creating music on the eerie theme. This game is an exciting combination between Sprunki Incredibox and Corrupbox, reimagining characters and increasing the level of matchness. Set in a spooky theme and unsettling music, you will take charge as a music producer, creating music from available sounds. Dive into the game and unleash your inner musician now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/corruptbox-2-but-sprunki-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"381\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Corruptbox 2 But Sprunki</strong> provides seven Sprunki characters on the glitchy and eerier stage. Not only will you show off your creativity and musical talent, but you will also demonstrate your bravery with Sprunki\'s creepy appearance. As you customize your characters, they will change from dark colors into an unsettling look with missing body parts and other terrifying features. At the same time, sounds combine and echo to break the quiet atmosphere, adding more creepiness.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To style your characters, players can use the mouse with drag-and-drop mechanics. Simply click on your favorite music tones, and then drag them onto any avatar on the screen. As you feel pleased with your composition, save and share your eerie track for your friends. Your creation can be a perfect choice for the Halloween holiday!</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Who Plays This Game</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Those who are looking for a horror platform can test their bravery due to its unsettling features.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Music lovers who would like to create music from different sounds.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Players who love to express and enhance their imagination.</span></li></ul>','Corruptbox 2 But Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','corruptbox-2-but-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:11:51','2026-07-20 06:11:51','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/corruptbox-2-but-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(404,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:53','2026-07-20 06:11:53','','sprunki-memory-card-match-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-memory-card-match-2','','','2026-07-20 06:11:53','2026-07-20 06:11:53','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-memory-card-match-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(405,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:54','2026-07-20 06:11:54','','Sprunki Memory Card Match','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-memory-card-match-3','','','2026-07-20 06:11:55','2026-07-20 06:11:55','',406,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-memory-card-match.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(406,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:55','2026-07-20 06:11:55','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Memory Card Match</strong> is a simple and intriguing puzzle game that blends relaxing recreation with brain-boosting challenges. This game features addictive captivating players of all ages. With straightforward controls and stunning graphics, this playground offers a chance to unwind from daily stress. Play this casual game or relax today!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-memory-card-match-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"349\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Memory Card Match</strong> offers a task of flipping cards and finding the same to match them together. This game features a variety of levels with increasing challenges, each featuring <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> pictures. Your goal is to match the two same images within a particular time and as few flipping turns as possible to earn stars and unlock the next stage.</span></p><h3>Benefits of the game</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Reinforce your memory</strong><span>: You have to remember the picture\'s position while playing the game. This is because if you haven\'t found the same pictures yet, they will flip back.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong>Release stress: </strong></strong>This game brings you into the colorful realm and features humorous music from the Sprunki game.</li></ul>','Sprunki Memory Card Match','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-memory-card-match','','','2026-07-20 06:11:55','2026-07-20 06:11:55','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-memory-card-match/',0,'game','',0),(407,1,'2026-07-20 06:11:57','2026-07-20 06:11:57','','Sprunki Phase 8','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-8-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:00','2026-07-20 06:12:00','',408,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-8-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(408,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:00','2026-07-20 06:12:00','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Phase 8</strong> is an ideal <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game for both music lovers and horror seekers. This music playground is the eighth version of the <strong>Sprunki Phase</strong> series, offering only the horror mode. With reimagined eerie characters and creepy sounds, this creation game plunges you into an unsettling music experience. Are you brave enough to engage in this game? Start to create music now!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Exciting Features</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px; text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Haunting Setting: Players will encounter special horror versions of the main characters immediately when they enter the game.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Creepy Sprunki Characters: Sprunki will appear with blood-chilling appearances with horrifying pains.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 400;\"><span> Spooky Music: You will compose music from the eerie effects, vocals, melodies, and beats. </span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY<strong> </strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To create music in <strong>Sprunki Phase 8</strong>, you need to use the mouse and apply the drag-and-drop mechanics. As you customize seven characters with tone icons, your favorite Sprunki characters will change their appearance, adding more blood-chilling. Unsettling sounds will echo and combine together, creating an eerie soundtrack that features your style. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>There are no rules or restrictions in this creation game. That means you can endlessly explore your creativity and blend sounds according to your preference. As you are not pleased with any sounds, only one click on your character’s body to remove and switch sounds.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">More Phases?</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-3\">Sprunki Phase 3</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Phase 8','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-8','','','2026-07-20 06:12:00','2026-07-20 06:12:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-8/',0,'game','',0),(409,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:02','2026-07-20 06:12:02','','sprunki-spot-the-5-differences-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-spot-the-5-differences-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:02','2026-07-20 06:12:02','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-spot-the-5-differences-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(410,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:03','2026-07-20 06:12:03','','Sprunki Spot the 5 Differences','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-spot-the-5-differences-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:03','2026-07-20 06:12:03','',411,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-spot-the-5-differences.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(411,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:03','2026-07-20 06:12:03','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Spot the 5 Differences</strong> is a simple and relaxing brain game with a delightful <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> twist. This puzzle game challenges your eye with similar pictures and puts your patience to the test. Your task is to find the difference between two pictures in order to complete each level. Play the game and relax now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-spot-the-5-differences-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"770\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY OVERVIEW</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Spot the 5 Differences</strong> presents 15 levels, each requiring you to find five differences between two pictures of Sprunki. You have to complete every stage at a particular time in three lives. When the timer runs out and you have not found all differences, you need to restart. Besides, the game also ends if you make three mistakes while playing.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Start from the easiest level, the next one will be more difficult, requiring more attention and patience. During your journey, you can watch shorts to use Sprunki hints to uncover a difference or add extra time to stay longer in the game.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">How to play</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Use your mouse to find the 5 differences between two pictures.</p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benefits of the game</h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Foster your patience.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Improve your concentration.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Enhance your attention.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span>Strengthen your brain.</span></li></ul><h2><span>More Sprunki Puzzles</span></h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-memory-card-match\">Sprunki Memory Card Match</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-jigsaw\">Sprunki Jigsaw</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Spot the 5 Differences','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-spot-the-5-differences','','','2026-07-20 06:12:03','2026-07-20 06:12:03','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-spot-the-5-differences/',0,'game','',0),(412,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:05','2026-07-20 06:12:05','','sprunki-baby-phase-3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-baby-phase-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:05','2026-07-20 06:12:05','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-baby-phase-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(413,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:06','2026-07-20 06:12:06','','Sprunki baby PHASE 3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-baby-phase-3-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:06','2026-07-20 06:12:06','',414,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Sprunki-baby-PHASE-3-4.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(414,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:06','2026-07-20 06:12:06','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki baby PHASE 3</strong> is a marvelous combination of the beloved <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a> Mod with <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-babies\">Sprunki Babies</a>. This music game currently introduces you to two exciting modes and challenges you to create music with both cheerful and eerie sounds. As a music composer, you will combine sound effects to release the most beautiful soundtracks. Do you dare to take on this challenge?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-baby-phase-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"317\"></span></p><h2>GAMEPLAY OVERVIEW</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki baby PHASE 3</strong> features two exciting modes with distinct designs and sounds yet they share the same core mechanics.</span></p><h3>Sprunki Babies Mode</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>You will encounter little <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters on the bright and charming landscape. Players will personalize their figures with 20 colorful music boxes to create their own exotic melodies. This mode does not feature a horror theme! As you drag the black bowler icon onto the Sprunki character, the scene will shift to night, adding a new vibe to your composition.</span></p><h3>Sprunki Original Mode</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This mode includes two stages: <em>Normal</em> and <em>Horror</em>, staying true to the original version of Sprunki. You will style your characters by dragging and dropping music boxes on them. If you want to change into an eerie setting, simply combine a character with the black hat icon.</span></p><h3>How to control<strong> </strong></h3><p><span>In addition to using your mouse to blend music, the game adds several outstanding features after customizing your characters.</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Click on the unmute option below your character to turn off its sound.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Click on the headphone icon to listen only to its sounds.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Click twice to remove sounds from your characters.</span></li></ul>','Sprunki baby PHASE 3','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-baby-phase-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:06','2026-07-20 06:12:06','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-baby-phase-3/',0,'game','',0),(415,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:08','2026-07-20 06:12:08','','friday-night-sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','friday-night-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:12:08','2026-07-20 06:12:08','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/friday-night-sprunki.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(416,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:09','2026-07-20 06:12:09','','Friday Night Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','friday-night-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:09','2026-07-20 06:12:09','',417,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/friday-night-sprunki-5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(417,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:09','2026-07-20 06:12:09','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Friday Night Sprunki</strong> is a charming blend of two music series: <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> and Friday Night Funkin. You will engage in a thrilling rhythm-based rap battle with various characters, making sure to hit the arrow notes at the right moment. From the easiest stage, then improve your skills and conquer harder levels. Dive into this game and rap your way to victory now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/friday-night-sprunki.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"384\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">An Enchanting Combination</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In this <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game, not only will you encounter Sprunki characters, but you can also participate in music battles with numerous characters. They step out of varied video games and TV shows, and all already appeared in the FNF mod. Every level will plunge you into a new stage with new, different characters. What you need to do is take on the challenge and do your best to win the game.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY OVERVIEW</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Sharing the core mechanic as an FNF mod, Friday Night Sprunki offers a task of using the arrow keys to press the correct arrows in time when they scroll up on the screen. You will start your journey at level one or two, then increase your skills and unlock the next level by completing the current one. Each lever will introduce a new song and allow you to participate in a musical duel with new opponents. The higher level you reach, the more difficulty you face, requiring you to push your reflexes and eye-hand coordination to the ultimate.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Play With More Sprunkis</h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-cats\">Sprunki Cats</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-2\">Sprunki 2</a></li></ul>','Friday Night Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','friday-night-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:12:09','2026-07-20 06:12:09','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/friday-night-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(418,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:11','2026-07-20 06:12:11','','squid-sprunki-game-2-2','','inherit','open','closed','','squid-sprunki-game-2-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:11','2026-07-20 06:12:11','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-sprunki-game-2-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(419,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:12','2026-07-20 06:12:12','','Squid Sprunki Game 2','','inherit','open','closed','','squid-sprunki-game-2-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:12','2026-07-20 06:12:12','',420,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-sprunki-game-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(420,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:12','2026-07-20 06:12:12','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Squid Sprunki Game 2</strong> is the thrilling combination of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters and exhilarating challenges in Squid Game. This casual game transports you into the exciting blend of survival drama and challenges inspired by childhood recreational activities. As the role of a Sprunki character as well as a Squid Game player, you will take part in exciting games. Each will be an intriguing stage and feature a varied level of difficulty, challenging your carefulness and patience. Do you dare to take on the challenges of this game?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/squid-sprunki-game-2-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"402\"></span></p><h2>Exhilarating yet Thrilling Games</h2><p><span>Inspired by the famous Squid Game, this version simulates most activities, plunging you into the real experience as a Squid Game player.</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Red Light, Green Light</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Sugar Candy Slipting Game in Squid Game</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Tug of War Game</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Play Marbles</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Cross the Glass Bridge</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Squid Game</span></li></ul><h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>Squid Sprunki Game 2</strong>, you will participate in Red Light, Green Light first, and then join others in the order. You need to take on the challenge of completing the level within a particular time under the witness of Spuide Game Soldier. Unless you make even a small mistake or the timer goes out, Squid will remove you from the game with its gun. But don’t worry, this game does not offer limiting attempts, so you can retry endlessly. The next activity will open as you complete the current one effectively.</span></p><h2>More Casual Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-game-sprunki-fnf-battle\">Squid Game Sprunki FNF Battle</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/dandy-world-tycoon\">Dandy World Tycoon</a></li></ul>','Squid Sprunki Game 2','','private','open','closed','','squid-sprunki-game-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:12','2026-07-20 06:12:12','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/squid-sprunki-game-2/',0,'game','',0),(421,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:14','2026-07-20 06:12:14','','sprunki-megalovania2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-megalovania2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:14','2026-07-20 06:12:14','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-megalovania2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(422,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:15','2026-07-20 06:12:15','','Sprunki Megalovania','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-megalovania-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:15','2026-07-20 06:12:15','',423,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-megalovania.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(423,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:15','2026-07-20 06:12:15','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The rhythm game <strong>Sprunki Megalovania</strong> transports you into the role of a composer, starting your music career by crafting your own soundtracks. You will have the chance to unleash your inner musician with unique available ingredients. With the combination of beats, vocals, effects, melodies, and creativity, players will find themselves at the center of the music stage. From funny music to creepy soundtracks, each echoes to highlight your personality and music style. Get ready for some amazing beats to fill your ears and heart!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-megalovania2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"378\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Megalovania Setting</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Inspired by Megalovania, this game allows you to meet your character within the black and white colors. Apart from the musical icons, everything emphasizes two main colors, following the Megalovania setting. Specifically, upon entering the game, you will encounter three black and four white figures on the in-game stage. As you combine tone icons with any characters, they will change their look but still retain the black and white appearance.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Megalovania</strong> still remains two exciting modes with immersive sounds. In the <em>Normal mode</em>, your characters will be two colors, black and white, playing humorous music as you customize them. The <em>Horror mode</em> will immediately run as you customize any figure with the smell icon on the list. All of your avatars will change into a black color with red eyes and mouths. They spotlight on the red backdrop and emit a little creepy music as you style them.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Making Your Own Music</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Check out other Sprunki games to feel your beat:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/dystopia-sprunki-style-incredibox\">Dystopia Sprunki Style (Incredibox)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-deluxe\">Sprunki Retake Deluxe</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Megalovania','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-megalovania','','','2026-07-20 06:12:15','2026-07-20 06:12:15','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-megalovania/',0,'game','',0),(424,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:17','2026-07-20 06:12:17','','Sprunki Bubble Pop','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-bubble-pop-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:17','2026-07-20 06:12:17','',425,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-bubble-pop.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(425,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:17','2026-07-20 06:12:17','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Bubble Pop</strong> is a relaxing yet exhilarating <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/casual.games\">casual</a> game that promises to create endless fun for players. This game lets you encounter a 3D image of Line (Green Sprunki) and accompany this character on the exciting challenge. Your mission is to pop bubbles and enjoy Sprunki dancing with music. Prepare yourself for this straightforward but electrifying journey!</span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>As you enter <strong>Sprunki Bubble Pop</strong>, you will see OWAKCX dancing beneath multicolor bubbles. Your task is to click your mouse twice on any bubble that connects more than two dots. As you remove bubbles, this game will reward you with points. The number of bubbles you can get rid of per time will impact your scores.</span></p><h2>Why Should You Play This Game?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Not only is it an entertaining platform for you to relax, but this game also enhances your observation. This is because you need to find the same color bubbles among hurdles of dots. Besides, you can improve your strategy while playing this title since you have to think logically to create combos and remove as many bubbles as possible per time.</span></p><h2>Other Games</h2><p>Check out more hot casual games such as:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-sprunki-game-2\">Squid Sprunki Game 2</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-the-musical-coloring-book\">Sprunki: The Musical Coloring Book</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Bubble Pop','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-bubble-pop','','','2026-07-20 06:12:17','2026-07-20 06:12:17','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-bubble-pop/',0,'game','',0),(426,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:18','2026-07-20 06:12:18','','jamming-with-sprunki2','','inherit','open','closed','','jamming-with-sprunki2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:18','2026-07-20 06:12:18','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/jamming-with-sprunki2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(427,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:19','2026-07-20 06:12:19','','Jamming with Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','jamming-with-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:20','2026-07-20 06:12:20','',428,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/jamming-with-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(428,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:20','2026-07-20 06:12:20','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Jamming with Sprunki</strong> is a music creation game taking the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/tag/horror\">horror</a> elements as the main focus. This game consists of creepy features in both music and graphics, plunging you into a haunting setting. Not only does the game test your courage, but it also challenges your imagination as you blend music with the unsettling theme. Prove your talent by creating music now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/jamming-with-sprunki2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"438\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Haunting Setting</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Characters: </strong><span>There are seven characters in black standing unmoving, waiting for you to wake the inner horror up.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Stage: </strong><span>This game features a spine-tingling backdrop, seeming to be an abandoned warehouse.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Sprunki: </strong><span>As you combine them with music boxes, they switch into creepy monsters, adding more blood-chilling to the game.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Music:</strong><span> As you craft soundtracks, the quiet atmosphere breaks and emits creepy sounds. </span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Jamming with Sprunki</strong> is a special version that features only 12 music sounds at the bottom of the screen. You will start your music-creating journey by dragging and dropping tones into your characters. This game also introduces one more sound at the top of the screen, sharing the same mechanics without any rule.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">More Music</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-music-scary-beat-box\">Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-pyramixed\">Sprunki Pyramixed</a></li></ul>','Jamming with Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','jamming-with-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:12:20','2026-07-20 06:12:20','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/jamming-with-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(429,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:22','2026-07-20 06:12:22','','sprunki-sprungle-banana-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sprungle-banana-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:22','2026-07-20 06:12:22','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprungle-banana-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(430,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:23','2026-07-20 06:12:23','','Sprunki Sprungle Banana','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sprungle-banana-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:23','2026-07-20 06:12:23','',431,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprungle-banana.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(431,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:23','2026-07-20 06:12:23','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The music creation game <strong>Sprunki Sprungle Banana </strong>brings a whimsical twist to the classic <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> gameplay by immersing players in a charming banana-themed world. In this music game, you will meet your favorite Sprunki characters in a hilarious appearance with banana-inspired outfits and accessories. Using the wild tropical landscape as a stage, you will accompany them to dance and compose your one-of-a-kind tracks. Put on your headphones and immerse yourself in music now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sprungle-banana-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Exciting Features</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Banana characters: </strong><span>This game offers the reimagined design of your Spunki characters with banana outfits.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Two exciting modes: </strong><span>Players have the option of choosing between the normal or horror mode. Each features unique sound effects and visuals.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Pick Your Favorite Sound Effects: </strong><span><strong>Sprunki Sprungle Banana</strong> enables you to choose your favorite sounds from a list of tone icons.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Customize your Banana Builders:</strong><span> Players personalize their characters by dragging and dropping their chosen musical icons onto avatars.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong>Discover Mysterious Surprises: </strong></strong>This game offers the horror theme as you style any avatar with the black icon on the list</li></ul><h2>Game You Might Like</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-2\">Sprunki 2</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Sprungle Banana','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-sprungle-banana','','','2026-07-20 06:12:23','2026-07-20 06:12:23','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-sprungle-banana/',0,'game','',0),(432,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:25','2026-07-20 06:12:25','','sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:25','2026-07-20 06:12:25','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(433,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:26','2026-07-20 06:12:26','','Sprunki but All Mr. Fun Computers','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:27','2026-07-20 06:12:27','',434,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(434,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:27','2026-07-20 06:12:27','<p><strong>Join the fresh version of the music game Sprunki but All Mr. Fun Computers! Accompany Mr. Fun Computers and blend music like a real musician!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki but All Mr. Fun Computers</strong> is a unique and fresh version of the music game Sprunki Incredibox. This music game is a mod based on Mr. Fun Computer, discovering its features deeply. Instead of playing music with seven normal Sprunki characters, you will accompany seven Mr. Fun computers and start your music career with it. Are you ready to join in this exotic innovation?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\"></span></p><h2>Check Outstanding Features</h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>All the characters are Mr. Fun Computer.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>The game introduces both default and horror themes.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Mr. Fun Computers will put on different outfits as you customize them with tone icons. </span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Players can endlessly express their imagination and music talents.</span></li></ul><h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Both modes in <strong>Sprunki but All Mr. Fun Computers</strong> let you encounter Mr. Fun Computers in varied exciting visuals. In the normal mode, you will meet seven Mr. Fun Computers as you enter the game. They will play bright music and wear colorful outfits as you customize them. In contrast, when you launch the horror mode, you will see <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> standing on the screen with dim red light and an eye-themed background. Mr. Fun Computers will surprisingly appear with creepy outfits only if you style them with music boxes.</span></p>','Sprunki but All Mr. Fun Computers','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers','','','2026-07-20 06:12:27','2026-07-20 06:12:27','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-but-all-mr-fun-computers/',0,'game','',0),(435,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:29','2026-07-20 06:12:29','','sprunki-find-the-differences2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-find-the-differences2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:29','2026-07-20 06:12:29','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-find-the-differences2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(436,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:30','2026-07-20 06:12:30','','Sprunki Find The Differences','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-find-the-differences-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:31','2026-07-20 06:12:31','',437,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-find-the-differences.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(437,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:31','2026-07-20 06:12:31','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Find The Differences</strong> is a captivating puzzle game that challenges your ability to observe and pay attention. This brain game transports you into 15 challenges, each requiring you to show off your skills to spot all differences in both similar pictures. How long does it take you? Let’s play now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-find-the-differences2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY OVERVIEW</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Each level in <strong>Sprunki Find The Differences</strong> presents two vibrant and colorful pictures of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters. Players are in charge of spotting ten small differences within a particular time. This game offers two lives for each stage! As you complete your current level effectively within limitation time, you win the game and take the ticket for the next exhilarating stage. On the other hand, you need to start over if the timer goes out while falling to find all differences or make more than two mistakes.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benefits of this Puzzle Game</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Improve your concentration:</strong><span> Sharpen your attention to detail by finding subtle differences.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Foster your patience:</strong><span> Stay focused and patient as players carefully analyze each picture.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Enhance your observation: </strong><span>Train your eyes to detect small changes and improve visual memory.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Workout your brain: </strong><span>Engage in a fun mental exercise that improves cognitive skills.</span></li></ul><h2><span>More Fun Options</span></h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/blast-sprunki\">Blast Sprunki</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-jigsaw\">Sprunki Jigsaw</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Find The Differences','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-find-the-differences','','','2026-07-20 06:12:31','2026-07-20 06:12:31','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-find-the-differences/',0,'game','',0),(438,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:33','2026-07-20 06:12:33','','Sprunki Scratch','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-scratch-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:35','2026-07-20 06:12:35','',439,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-scratch2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(439,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:35','2026-07-20 06:12:35','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Scratch</strong> is the most addictive <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/music-creation.games\">music creation</a> game that combines creative gameplay and music. More than just a game, it is also an opportunity for players to express their imagination through creating music. You will have the chance to immerse yourself in your own unique soundtracks created from charming music or even creepy sounds. Get ready to join the enchanting music realm now!</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The gameplay in <strong>Sprunki Scratch</strong> focuses on players crafting songs by customizing <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/tag/sprunki-characters\">Sprunki characters</a> with music boxes. With your creativity, you will style your characters’ outfits and change their accessories by dragging and dropping tone icons on them. Under your magical hands and rich imagination, your own musical <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> releases marked your personality.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Not only that, this music creation game also takes players into fascinating, eerie modes. Customizing your characters with the icon of a black bowler, you can engage in the ultimate journey of crafting creepy soundtracks on spine-tingling themes.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">What Types of Players Are There?</h3><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Music Enthusiasts: </strong><span>Players who are into listening to and playing music.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Music-creating Lovers</strong><span>: Those who own a rich imagination and want to share their ability through music.</span></li></ul><h2><span>Similar Games to Try</span></h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-2\">Sprunki 2</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Scratch','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-scratch','','','2026-07-20 06:12:35','2026-07-20 06:12:35','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-scratch/',0,'game','',0),(440,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:37','2026-07-20 06:12:37','','Sprunki Phase 100','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-100-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:43','2026-07-20 06:12:43','',441,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-100-4.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(441,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:43','2026-07-20 06:12:43','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Welcome to <strong>Sprunki Phase 100</strong>, the ultimate evolution of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> that is infused with eerie elements and horror-inspired sounds. Unlike previous phases, this music creation game takes a darker, more atmospheric turn, crafting the perfect platform for horror enthusiasts. You will face unsettling monsters and compose haunting soundtracks by using spine-chilling effects. Prepare yourself for a thrilling musical journey into the unknown!</span></p><h2>A Haunting Theme</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This music game redesigns the music and image that sends shivers down your spine. From the moment you enter, seven black, motionless monsters will loom on the screen. They are standing on the stage where the backdrop showcases ghostly eyes, drifting toward the right edge, enhancing the ominous atmosphere. As you begin your music-creating journey, eerie twists echo through the air, transforming your characters into haunting figures that emit unsettling sounds. Every note deepens the chilling experience, immersing you in an unforgettable, spine-tingling world.</span></p><h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Phase 100</strong> features a single horror mode, where you craft eerie soundtracks by customizing monsters with musical icons at the bottom of the screen. With 20 distinct music boxes, each producing unique and haunting sounds, you can mix and match them to create an otherworldly experience. This game allows you to endlessly switch music icons without any rules, creating a free playground where you can showcase your creativity.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Games in the Same Style</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-777\">Sprunki Phase 777</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-3\">Sprunki Phase 3</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Phase 100','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-100','','','2026-07-20 06:12:43','2026-07-20 06:12:43','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-100/',0,'game','',0),(442,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:45','2026-07-20 06:12:45','','sprunki-night-time-phase-3-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-night-time-phase-3-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:45','2026-07-20 06:12:45','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-night-time-phase-3-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(443,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:46','2026-07-20 06:12:46','','Sprunki Night Time Phase 3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-night-time-phase-3-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:47','2026-07-20 06:12:47','',444,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-night-time-phase-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(444,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:47','2026-07-20 06:12:47','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Night Time Phase 3</strong> is a captivating music creation game that throws you into an enchanting world filled with rhythm and harmony. Designed for music enthusiasts of all ages, this rhythm game offers a unique experience where you can compose mesmerizing tunes and bring charming creatures to life. Step into a starlit world, where every note you play contributes to an ever-evolving symphony, creating on-of-a-kind twists!</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">An Appealing Music World</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Set in a starry night, this music game immerses you in a mysterious world where seven adorable creatures await your arrival. Standing in front of a charming forest adorned with glowing mushrooms, these little beings are silent until you step in and ignite the magic of music. As your journey unfolds, beautifully dressed music players appear, each resonating with immersive melodies. Together, they join you on a sparkling stage, ready to create an unforgettable performance.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-night-time-phase-3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"430\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY OVERVIEW</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Night Time Phase 3</strong> features 20 exhilarating music boxes, each offering a unique musical experience. This version presents a single classic mode, allowing you to interact with your favorite Sprunki characters in their most charming appearances. As you explore the game, you can style these characters with delightful music boxes, enhancing both their look and the melodies they produce.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Sharing the same intuitive mechanics as other <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> games, this version lets you style your characters endlessly. By simply dragging and dropping your preferred sounds, you can create a symphony that is uniquely yours. With just a few clicks, your personalized musical masterpiece will come to life, making every session a fresh and delightful experience.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Similar Game</span></h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Love this game? Try <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-night-time\">Sprunki Night Time</a> as a related night time version. Have a great time!</span></p>','Sprunki Night Time Phase 3','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-night-time-phase-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:47','2026-07-20 06:12:47','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-night-time-phase-3/',0,'game','',0),(445,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:50','2026-07-20 06:12:50','','Ratomilton Meets Sprunki Physics Puzzle Adventure','','inherit','open','closed','','ratomilton-meets-sprunki-physics-puzzle-adventure-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:52','2026-07-20 06:12:52','',446,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/ratomilton-meets-sprunki-physics-puzzle-adventure.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(446,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:52','2026-07-20 06:12:52','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Step into the delightful world of <strong>Ratomilton Meets Sprunki Physics Puzzle</strong> <strong>Adventure</strong>, a physics-based puzzle adventure that blends strategy and creativity. This game offers the mission of helping an animated mouse named Rato Milton reunite with OWAKCX from <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> world. This brain game introduces you to various levels, each featuring different challenges and requiring your strategy to solve. Are you ready to test your skills and guide Roto Milton to meet his friend?</span></p><h2>Who is Rato Milton?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Roto Milton is inspired by a Brazilian YouTuber known for their 3D animation videos. His popularity skyrocketed with the viral “Rat Dance” meme, outstanding with hilarious dance. In this game, you will experience the Rat Dance in a fresh new way, offering a delightful playground for players of all ages.</span></p><h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Ratomilton Meets Sprunki Physics Puzzle Adventure</strong> features multiple levels filled with physics-based obstacles. To advance, you have to solve each challenge step by step, unlocking new stages as you progress.</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Use your mouse to click and get rid of in-game wooden blocks strategically. </span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Ensure Rato Milton reaches his friend to complete each level.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Click the retry button at the top right corner to restart and try a new approach as you get stuck.</span></li></ul>','Ratomilton Meets Sprunki Physics Puzzle Adventure','','private','open','closed','','ratomilton-meets-sprunki-physics-puzzle-adventure','','','2026-07-20 06:12:52','2026-07-20 06:12:52','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/ratomilton-meets-sprunki-physics-puzzle-adventure/',0,'game','',0),(447,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:53','2026-07-20 06:12:53','','htsprunkis-retake','','inherit','open','closed','','htsprunkis-retake','','','2026-07-20 06:12:53','2026-07-20 06:12:53','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/htsprunkis-retake.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(448,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:55','2026-07-20 06:12:55','','HTSprunkis Retake','','inherit','open','closed','','htsprunkis-retake-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:56','2026-07-20 06:12:56','',449,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/htsprunkis-retake3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(449,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:56','2026-07-20 06:12:56','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>HTSprunkis Retake</strong> is a fascinating music creation game that delivers an enchanting realm and a little creepy atmosphere. This playground allows you to explore your imagination while engaging the fascinating music world. With its captivating soundtrack and immersive visuals, this rhythm game encourages players to experiment with different musical styles and compositions, making each session a delightful adventure.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/htsprunkis-retake.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"349\"></span></p><h2>What Makes the Game Stand Out?</h2><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>New Characters:</strong><span> Instead of Sprunki characters, this game introduces charming creatures from Happy Tree Friends.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Adorable Music Boxes and Fresh Sounds: </strong><span>This version reimagines musical tones with lovely animated visuals and adds fresh sounds in both classic and horror mode.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Core Mechanics: </strong><span>Players can effortlessly create music with creative gameplay.</span></li></ul><h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>As you enter <strong>HTSprunkis Retake</strong>, you will be greeted by seven little adorable creatures with quirky faces, two long teeth, and heart-shaped noses. They are sitting on the mesmerizing stage and waiting for your arrival. Your task is to help them put on colorful outfits and compose immersive melodies using an array of sound effects.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Simply dragging musical boxes onto these figures, you can watch the enchanting world come to life with vibrant colors and delightful tunes. But be careful with the last icon in the list! If you style any character with this tone, the horror mode will activate, transforming both visuals and sounds into a spine-chilling experience.</span></p><h2>Related Games to Play</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-happy-three-friends\">Sprunki Retake: Happy Three Friends</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake-deluxe\">Sprunki Retake Deluxe</a></li></ul>','HTSprunkis Retake','','private','open','closed','','htsprunkis-retake','','','2026-07-20 06:12:56','2026-07-20 06:12:56','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/htsprunkis-retake/',0,'game','',0),(450,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:56','2026-07-20 06:12:56','','sprunki-oc-v3-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-oc-v3-2','','','2026-07-20 06:12:56','2026-07-20 06:12:56','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-oc-v3-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(451,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:57','2026-07-20 06:12:57','','Sprunki OC v3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-oc-v3-3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:59','2026-07-20 06:12:59','',452,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-oc-v32.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(452,1,'2026-07-20 06:12:59','2026-07-20 06:12:59','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sprunki OC v3</strong> is a special innovative music creation game released by BIZorg that reimagines sound design with fresh effects and limitless possibilities. This interactive playground allows you to embark on the most exciting music-making journey ever, composing music from numerous sounds. With over 50 unique musical icons, you can experiment freely with rhythms, melodies, and tracks to perfection. Unleash your creativity and compose music like never before now!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-oc-v3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"251\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uncover Fresh Features</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This game offers an extensive library of more than 50 sound effects, displayed at the top and bottom of the screen.</li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can enhance your compositions by layering up to 11 different sounds simultaneously, allowing for diverse and dynamic music creation. </li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In order to create music in <strong>Sprunki OC v3</strong>, you can follow basic steps:</p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Choose sounds: </strong>Select your favorite tunes from a diverse collection of unique sound effects.</li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Customize your characters:</strong> Drag and drop music icons onto 11 characters on the screen.</li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Refine your soundtracks: </strong>Switch and adjust music boxes to create your perfect mix. </li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Switch horror mode:</strong> Drag the last icon at the bottom of the avatar to turn into the creepy mode.</li></ul>','Sprunki OC v3','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-oc-v3','','','2026-07-20 06:12:59','2026-07-20 06:12:59','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-oc-v3/',0,'game','',0),(453,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:01','2026-07-20 06:13:01','','sprunki-beats','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-beats','','','2026-07-20 06:13:01','2026-07-20 06:13:01','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-beats.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(454,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:02','2026-07-20 06:13:02','','Sprunki Beats','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-beats-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:02','2026-07-20 06:13:02','',455,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-beats2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(455,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:02','2026-07-20 06:13:02','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Beats</strong> is an addictive, innovative <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game that delivers you into the mesmerizing realm. This music game invites you into the role of a pro music creator and puts you in charge of crafting music. With an extensive library of dynamic sound effects, you can prove your music talents and release the most immersive twists. Jump into this creation game and start your music career now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-beats.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uncover Fresh Elements</h2><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Provide appealing music modes with various effects, melodies, vocals, and beats for you to access.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Feature the classic and creepy theme for both music lovers and horror seekers.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Offer the creative gameplay, allowing players to endlessly create soundtracks.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY OVERVIEW</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Beats</strong> introduces players to four exciting music modes, each presenting different sounds and exciting visuals.</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>First mode:</strong><span> Set on the beach with the classic theme, you will encounter your favorite <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters both on the sandy beach and in the boat. </span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Second mode</strong><span>: Your characters standing in front of the mysterious city will immediately change into an unsettling appearance as you start customizing them.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Third mode:</strong><span> Like the second stage, this mode lets you meet your Sprunki characters in the wild and eerie place with a little red dim light in the backdrop.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Fourth mode: </strong><span>It seems that your characters are throwing a music party in a luxury place and performing music on a sparkling stage.</span></li></ul>','Sprunki Beats','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-beats','','','2026-07-20 06:13:02','2026-07-20 06:13:02','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-beats/',0,'game','',0),(456,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:03','2026-07-20 06:13:03','','sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:03','2026-07-20 06:13:03','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(457,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:05','2026-07-20 06:13:05','','Sprunki Squid Rocket Launcher','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:05','2026-07-20 06:13:05','',458,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(458,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:05','2026-07-20 06:13:05','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Squid Rocket Launcher</strong> takes you on the most thrilling adventure where action meets precision. In this endless game, you will step into the shoes of a Sprunki shooter, participating in the exhilarating competition with Squid Game Soldiers. Equipped with an in-game rocket, you are in charge of defeating your opponents to earn coins. Play this action game and see how many Squid Game Soldiers you can shoot!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Squid Rocket Launcher</strong> puts your timing and aiming skills to the ultimate test with a never-ending adventure. As you click the start button on the screen, you will step into the lifelike competition with countless Squid Game soldiers. In order to defeat the enemies, you need to aim strategically and click the mouse to shoot. Defeating one opponent means you get rewards to unlock new Sprunki characters with distinct powers. The game will keep going until you fail to shoot any opponents.</span></p><h3>What Makes This Game Intriguing?</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Stunning Music:</strong><span> Immerse yourself in the Squid Game Soldier with upbeat melodies, motivating you to continue your journey!</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Easy Controls:</strong><span> Feature intuitive controls that allow players of all skill levels to jump right in without a steep learning curve.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Intriguing Gameplay:</strong><span> Combine strategy and quick reflexes to keep players engaged as they navigate through opponents.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Endless Challenges: </strong><span>Presents unique obstacles and increasingly difficult foes, ensuring that no two sessions are ever the same.</span></li></ul>','Sprunki Squid Rocket Launcher','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher','','','2026-07-20 06:13:05','2026-07-20 06:13:05','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher/',0,'game','',0),(459,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:07','2026-07-20 06:13:07','','sprunki-new-songs-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-new-songs-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:07','2026-07-20 06:13:07','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-new-songs-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(460,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:09','2026-07-20 06:13:09','','Sprunki New Songs','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-new-songs-3','','','2026-07-20 06:13:11','2026-07-20 06:13:11','',461,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-new-songs.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(461,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:11','2026-07-20 06:13:11','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>If you are seeking a delightful music game for the Christmas holiday, <strong>Sprunki New Songs</strong> is a perfect idea for the unforgettable festival. This music game puts you in the shoes of a professional music maker and allows you to unleash your musician. You will create music using the available sounds to create the most beautiful song with a festive atmosphere. Are you ready for this exciting rhythm journey? Let Christmas envelop you in its snowy embrace and swirl you in a whirlpool of festive mood now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-new-songs-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\"></span></p><h2>CREATE MUSIC WITH A FESTIVE THEME</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki New Songs</strong> is a fascinating playground where you explore your music talent and imagination. In this rhythm game, you will use the drag-and-drop mechanics to create songs. By simply clicking on the musical icons and then dragging them onto seven characters on the screen, you can release your unique songs.</span></p><h3>Create Music Combos with Accessible Suggestions</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In addition to creating music with your own style, this music playground also provides you with intriguing challenges. This game offers several Christmas combos, guided by the example on the mini panel. Your task is to follow the suggestion to create songs with the right combination and unlock the next set of sounds. Mistakes make the composition funny and chaotic but will not allow you to advance to the next level and new melody.</span></p><h2>Explore More Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-baby-phase-3\">Sprunki baby PHASE 3</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-night-time-phase-3\">Sprunki Night Time Phase 3</a></li></ul>','Sprunki New Songs','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-new-songs','','','2026-07-20 06:13:11','2026-07-20 06:13:11','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-new-songs/',0,'game','',0),(462,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:12','2026-07-20 06:13:12','','one-bullet-to-sprunki2','','inherit','open','closed','','one-bullet-to-sprunki2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:12','2026-07-20 06:13:12','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/one-bullet-to-sprunki2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(463,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:14','2026-07-20 06:13:14','','One Bullet To Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','one-bullet-to-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:15','2026-07-20 06:13:15','',464,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/one-bullet-to-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(464,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:15','2026-07-20 06:13:15','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>One Bullet To Sprunki</strong> delivers dexterity, reaction, and accuracy into the electrifying shooting game. You will play the role of an experienced Cameraman equipped with an ultimate weapon, joining the world of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a>. With your powerful gun, you will aim for your shots to destroy Sprunki monsters and win the game. Get ready for the thrilling shooting experience now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/one-bullet-to-sprunki2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"281\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">EXPLORE EXHILARATING GAMEPLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>One Bullet To Sprunki</strong>, your character—Cameraman—will stand on the top of a high-rise building with a gun in its hands. Your noble goal is to eliminate Sprunki in each round with one shot to win. In this game, you do not control your character but guide the bullet to navigate the road. The challenges lie in the fact that there are various obstacles during the air road, allowing you to prove your aiming and controlling skills. As soon as the bullet hits the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> character, you will win the game and get the key to unlock the next level with more hurdles. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Who Plays This Game?</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The arcade game is for thrill-seekers, who are looking for fast-paced action playgrounds. You will find excitement in the arcade game as you maneuver through increasingly difficult terrains. Moreover, if you are a fan of Sprunki, this game is an opportunity to meet your favorite Sprunki character in a completely new outfit and take on new challenges.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Other Shooting Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-squid-rocket-launcher\">Sprunki Squid Rocket Launcher</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-playground\">Sprunki Playground</a></li></ul>','One Bullet To Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','one-bullet-to-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:13:15','2026-07-20 06:13:15','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/one-bullet-to-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(465,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:17','2026-07-20 06:13:17','','Sprunki Phase 5 Definitive','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-5-definitive-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:24','2026-07-20 06:13:24','',466,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-5-definitive1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(466,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:24','2026-07-20 06:13:24','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Phase 5 Definitive</strong> is a thrilling music creation game that delivers the creepy elements into a <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> playground. This game is an updated version of the original <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a>, offering reimagined graphics and new sounds while refining gameplay. Players will have the chance to experience the feeling of creating music with available spooky sounds, unlike others before. Are you brave enough to face spine-chilling Sprunki characters and compose soundtracks on an eerie theme?</span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Stepping into the world of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> in <strong>Sprunki Phase 5 Definitive</strong>, you will see seven normal characters standing on the dark stage. Behind them, the night sky park is illuminated with a soft glow. The atmosphere is quiet and seems to be peaceful with no sound and movement. In order to wake your characters up, you need to customize them with the sounds at the bottom of the screen. As soon as you style the figures with musical boxes, they will change their appearance immediately, putting on spooky outfits and echoing creepy sounds. The game allows you to personalize a maximum of seven characters and switch without any rules.</span></p><h3>Warnings</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This music playground features only a single horror mode with unsettling graphics and spine-chilling sounds. Then if you are a horror fan and want to play music with an eerie theme, this game is perfect for you.</span></p>','Sprunki Phase 5 Definitive','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-5-definitive','','','2026-07-20 06:13:24','2026-07-20 06:13:24','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-5-definitive/',0,'game','',0),(467,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:26','2026-07-20 06:13:26','','sprunki-sinner2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sinner2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:26','2026-07-20 06:13:26','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sinner2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(468,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:27','2026-07-20 06:13:27','','Sprunki Sinner','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-sinner-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:28','2026-07-20 06:13:28','',469,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sinner.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(469,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:28','2026-07-20 06:13:28','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Sinner</strong> is a charming music creation game that delivers a gothic twist and a mysterious storyline. This game opens the enchanting music realm where you play the role of a pro musician and create your own immersive songs. While playing music, you will have the opportunity to witness a romantic plot that is sure to surprise you. It\'s a truly unique \"dark\" mode that you\'ve never experienced before. Embark on the music journey and explore this mystery now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sinner2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"378\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">GAMEPLAY INSTRUCTION</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Sinner</strong> refines the drag-and-drop mechanics and creative gameplay as part of the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/\">Sprunki game</a> universe. In this version, you will meet your <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> character in the delightful and fresh atmosphere. As you combine music and the avatar, they will sing and dance with music, adding more joy to the music party. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This game introduces you to 20 musical icons with the appearance of the black bowler hat. Yet, there is only the classic mode with lovely music and stunning graphics. As you customize a character with its icon, apart from this avatar putting on a new outfit, everything still remains. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Explore the “Dark” Mode</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>While crafting your soundtrack in this <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game, you will witness a heartfelt love story between Tunner (Tan) and Simon (Yellow). This special moment happens as you place Simon to the left of Tunner. While other characters continue to sing and dance, Simon pauses, then leans in to kiss Tunner. The unexpected gesture stuns everyone, and in that moment, the stage transforms into an intimate world of this musical couple, echoing their love through melody.</span></p>','Sprunki Sinner','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-sinner','','','2026-07-20 06:13:28','2026-07-20 06:13:28','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-sinner/',0,'game','',0),(470,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:29','2026-07-20 06:13:29','','sprunkilairity2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkilairity2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:29','2026-07-20 06:13:29','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkilairity2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(471,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:30','2026-07-20 06:13:30','','Sprunkilairity','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkilairity-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:31','2026-07-20 06:13:31','',472,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkilairity.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(472,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:31','2026-07-20 06:13:31','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunkilairity</strong> is a horror <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> creation game inspired by the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/\">Sprunki game</a>. This music game provides the fusion of music-making with a scary twist. In this version, your favorite Sprunki characters stand out with their spooky appearance. The joyful music is now spooky sounds, and the bright stage turns into the unsettling dark theme. Do you dare to immerse yourself in the scary music game? Join the game to show off your music talent as well as bravery now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkilairity2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"263\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunkilairity</strong> refines the core mechanics and same gameplay as other <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> versions. In this rhythm game, you will be in charge of creating music from the available spooky sounds. Players can completely adjust, save, and share their creation as they want. With no limitation, you can express your emotion and creativity endlessly through creepy music.</span></p><h3>How to Create Good Tracks</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>The game is a playground for your creativity with no restrictions. The soundtracks with your personality are perfect creations.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Players can join the Spurnki communities via the internet, where Sprunki fans usually share effective tips and exciting music combos.</span></li></ul>','Sprunkilairity','','private','open','closed','','sprunkilairity','','','2026-07-20 06:13:31','2026-07-20 06:13:31','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunkilairity/',0,'game','',0),(473,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:32','2026-07-20 06:13:32','','sprunked-final-version2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunked-final-version2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:32','2026-07-20 06:13:32','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunked-final-version2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(474,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:34','2026-07-20 06:13:34','','Sprunked Final Version','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunked-final-version-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:35','2026-07-20 06:13:35','',475,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunked-final-version1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(475,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:35','2026-07-20 06:13:35','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunked Final Version</strong> is a joyful and quirky music game that lets you make your own unique soundtracks. In this <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game, you have the opportunity to throw a music party and host a sparkling stage as a real talented musician. In the company of funny characters, you will craft immersive melodies that stand out in your style and creativity. So what are you waiting for? Jump into the music game and perform your creation on your own stage now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunked-final-version2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"305\"></span></p><h2>DISCOVER GAMEPLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Besides the 20 music boxes in the bottom center of the screen, <strong>Sprunked Final Version</strong> introduces you to additional sounds, expanding choices for your soundtracks. These exciting new choices are visible right on the screen, ready for you to create music anytime.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In this game, styling your characters with different music boxes not only changes their outfits but also adds to the chaotic energy of the stage. The more you customize, the wilder the performance becomes, turning your session into a true music party. But be careful with the black box! There is a dark force hiding under its tone. If you equip any characters with this icon, the creepy mode will activate.</span></p><h3>What Makes This Game Stand Out?</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Easy Music Making:</strong><span> This game provides simple control and easy-to-learn gameplay, so players of all ages can enjoy it.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Two Exciting Modes: </strong><span>Players can create music in both normal and eerie stages. </span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>A Variety of Soundtracks:</strong><span> You can engage in the music-making experience with around 28 sounds in both classic and horror mode.</span></li></ul><h2>Check Out More Sprunki Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-2\">Sprunki 2</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li></ul>','Sprunked Final Version','','private','open','closed','','sprunked-final-version','','','2026-07-20 06:13:35','2026-07-20 06:13:35','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunked-final-version/',0,'game','',0),(476,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:36','2026-07-20 06:13:36','','kino-sprunked2','','inherit','open','closed','','kino-sprunked2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:36','2026-07-20 06:13:36','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/kino-sprunked2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(477,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:37','2026-07-20 06:13:37','','Kino Sprunked','','inherit','open','closed','','kino-sprunked-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:38','2026-07-20 06:13:38','',478,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/kino-sprunked.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(478,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:38','2026-07-20 06:13:38','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Kino Sprunked</strong> opens the enchanting realm where you immerse yourself in the mesmerizing music world. This game delivers creative gameplay with energetic music and lovely hand-drawn characters. All generate a lovely playground paired with a little eeriness. Whether you are a music enthusiast or finding a delightful platform, playing this game is an ideal choice. Dive into the rhythm-based game and explore your music creation now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/kino-sprunked2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"345\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Crafting music in <strong>Kino Sprunked</strong> is easier than ever. All you need to do is click the mouse to style seven characters on the screen with music boxes. Everything is available and allows you to access it at any moment as you want. The music track will truly depend on your creativity and musical talent. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game offers both classic and horror themes for all ages. You can enjoy the normal theme with colorful graphics and cheerful music as soon as you enter the game. If you want to explore the dark stage, simply click and drag the black onto one figure to activate the horror mode.</span></p><h3>Who Plays This Game?</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This rhythm-based game appeals to a wide audience, including casual gamers looking for a relaxing escape and hardcore enthusiasts seeking a challenge. With its diverse themes and engaging gameplay, this title attracts players who appreciate both the light-hearted and the eerie aspect of rhythm gaming.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>More Choices</span></h2><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-new-songs\">Sprunki New Songs</a></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-scratch\">Sprunki Scratch</a></li></ul>','Kino Sprunked','','private','open','closed','','kino-sprunked','','','2026-07-20 06:13:38','2026-07-20 06:13:38','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/kino-sprunked/',0,'game','',0),(479,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:41','2026-07-20 06:13:41','','Draw and Create Sprunki Road','','inherit','open','closed','','draw-and-create-sprunki-road-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:41','2026-07-20 06:13:41','',480,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/draw-and-create-sprunki-road.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(480,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:41','2026-07-20 06:13:41','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Draw and Create Sprunki Road</strong> is a unique fusion of Sprunki characters and engaging puzzle games. In this playground, you will have the chance to unleash your creativity through exhilarating puzzles. Your mission is to create hand-drawn bridges, leading Sprunki to reach the destination at every level. Jump into this charming world and start your journey now!</span></p><h3>Discover Unique Features</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>It is an exciting fusion of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters and puzzle gameplay.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Different levels, each with its own unique puzzles, challenge your brain.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Engaging gameplay and easy-to-learn control make the game suitable for players of all ages.</span></li></ul><h2><strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Draw and Create Sprunki Road</strong> challenges your strategic thinking with a variety of tricky levels. Each stage features its specific puzzles and requires players to unlock them in turn. They share the same mission of drawing paths on the screen, ensuring Sprunki can safely collect the coin. This interactive element encourages players to think critically about their moves while navigating through the challenges.</span></p>','Draw and Create Sprunki Road','','private','open','closed','','draw-and-create-sprunki-road','','','2026-07-20 06:13:41','2026-07-20 06:13:41','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/draw-and-create-sprunki-road/',0,'game','',0),(481,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:42','2026-07-20 06:13:42','','sprunki-the-definitive-phase-31','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-the-definitive-phase-31','','','2026-07-20 06:13:42','2026-07-20 06:13:42','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-definitive-phase-31.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(482,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:43','2026-07-20 06:13:43','','Sprunki The Definitive Phase 3','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-the-definitive-phase-3-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:49','2026-07-20 06:13:49','',483,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-definitive-phase-3-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(483,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:49','2026-07-20 06:13:49','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki The Definitive Phase 3</strong> is an intriguing creation game that invites you into the role of a music producer. In this game, you will take on the challenge of composing your own unique masterpieces from available haunting sounds. Will your composition send shivers down spines or summon some things even darker? The choice is yours! Play the game now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-the-definitive-phase-31.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"259\"></span></p><h3>Uncover Eerie Music Vibes</h3><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Dark Vibe: This game features a shadowy theme and unsettling visuals. </span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Monster Characters: From normal status to customizing characters, each looks unique with its spine-chilling appearance.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Unique Sounds: Each character stands out with its creepy sounds and echo music as you style them.</span></li></ul><h2>HOW TO PLAY </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Creating music in <strong>Sprunki The Definitive Phase 3</strong> is as eerie as it is exciting. Your mission is to drag and drop different sound elements onto your monster avatars and watch them transform before your eyes. Each sound you choose doesn’t just shape the music—it alters the creatures, morphing them into even creepier forms. After creating the most pleasant masterpieces, players can save and share their creation with other players.</span></p><h2 data-start=\"216\" data-end=\"264\">Love Sprunki? Try These Awesome Games!</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><span><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-777\">Sprunki Phase 777</a><br></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-night-time-phase-3\">Sprunki Night Time Phase 3</a></li></ul>','Sprunki The Definitive Phase 3','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-the-definitive-phase-3','','','2026-07-20 06:13:49','2026-07-20 06:13:49','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-the-definitive-phase-3/',0,'game','',0),(484,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:51','2026-07-20 06:13:51','','sprunki-s-world-all-mod-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-s-world-all-mod-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:51','2026-07-20 06:13:51','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-s-world-all-mod-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(485,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:52','2026-07-20 06:13:52','','Sprunki\'s WORLD All MOD','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunkis-world-all-mod-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:52','2026-07-20 06:13:52','',486,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunkis-world-all-mod.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(486,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:52','2026-07-20 06:13:52','<p><span>Welcome to <strong>Sprunki’s WORLD ALL MOD</strong>, an impressive music creation game inspired by Sprunki Incredibox. This innovation is a fan-made musical adventure that consists of a variety of Sprunki versions. Step into this game, and you will turn into a real musician and have the chance to immerse yourself in the vast music world. Dive into this game and start your music journey now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-s-world-all-mod-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"340\"></span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>To start your music-making journey in <strong>Sprunki’s WORLD ALL MOD</strong>, you need to choose your favorite stages first. This music game offers various <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> themes that you might have enjoyed before. After choosing your preferred mode, players follow the core mechanics of the original music game to compose music. This game features both classic and horror themes in almost all stages to enhance your gaming experience. Simply click and drag the last icon in each stage, you can start to create eerie soundtracks.</span></p><h3>Uncover Several Modes</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>1_Original: </strong><span>Meet Sprunki characters in their original appearance and sounds.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>ParaSprunki: </strong><span>Set in the desert theme with more sounds</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Sprunked: </strong><span>Immerse yourself in the enchanting world with hand-drawn characters.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Babies: </strong><span>Accompany baby Sprunki in the charming realm in both classic and eerie mode.</span></li></ul><h2><span>Sprunki Fans, Don’t Miss These!</span></h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-retake\">Sprunki Retake</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-oc\">Sprunki OC</a></li></ul>','Sprunki\'s WORLD All MOD','','private','open','closed','','sprunkis-world-all-mod','','','2026-07-20 06:13:52','2026-07-20 06:13:52','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunkis-world-all-mod/',0,'game','',0),(487,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:54','2026-07-20 06:13:54','','sprunki-paper-education2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-paper-education2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:54','2026-07-20 06:13:54','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-paper-education2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(488,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:55','2026-07-20 06:13:55','','Sprunki Paper Education','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-paper-education-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:55','2026-07-20 06:13:55','',489,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-paper-education.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(489,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:55','2026-07-20 06:13:55','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Paper Education</strong> is an intriguing <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> game that blends the Paper Education world with the iconic <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> series. This fan-made version introduces a fresh take on music gameplay, where players interact with dynamic paper-based characters instead of the usual Sprunki figures. WIth its unique combination, the game offers an immersive experience filled with surprising transformations and eerie surprises. Let’s engage in this one-of-a-kind musical adventure now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-paper-education2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"206\"></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Discover Iconic Features</h3><ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>This game introduces the appearance of paper characters with cool looks.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Some characters change their appearance constantly while playing music.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Fun Bot still stays on the screen as you remove it.</span></li></ul><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>In <strong>Sprunki Paper Education</strong>, each student character has a set of unique sounds with super cool looks hiding under the charming music boxes. To wake them up, players need to click on the music icon and apply seven characters on the screen. At the moment the boxes merge with avatars, paper characters will appear and start to sing and dance.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This game offers both normal and horror modes. Like most <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> games, players need to customize an avatar with the last icon on the list to activate the horror theme. In this mode, everything will change, plunging you into the haunting atmosphere. That time, you will encounter creepy monster characters, listen to eerie music, and play music on the dark theme.</span></p>','Sprunki Paper Education','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-paper-education','','','2026-07-20 06:13:55','2026-07-20 06:13:55','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-paper-education/',0,'game','',0),(490,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:57','2026-07-20 06:13:57','','Sprunki Phase 11','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-11-2','','','2026-07-20 06:13:57','2026-07-20 06:13:57','',491,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-phase-11-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(491,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:57','2026-07-20 06:13:57','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Phase 11</strong> takes rhythm games to a new level where you immerse yourself in the spine-chilling experience. This playground blends eerie visuals, disturbing soundscapes, and monstrous characters. With creative gameplay and unsettling settings, this game immerses you in the world of darkness and allows you to unleash your inner musician. Get ready for an exhilarating music-making journey now!</span></p><h3>Uncover Horror Setting </h3><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Monster Characters:</strong><span> Grotesque creatures with eerie faces and wounds add haunting sounds to your eerie compositions.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Creepy Sounds:</strong><span> Unsettling whispers, screams, and distorted instruments create an immersive horror experience.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Dark Atmosphere: </strong><span>Shadowy landscapes and dim lighting enhance the spine-chilling theme.</span></li></ul><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Step into <strong>Sprunki Phase 11</strong>, you will take on the challenge of creating haunting compositions by layering eerie sounds assigned to monstrous characters. Each character brings its own unique sound palette, allowing you to experience and craft truly unsettling auditory experience. As you progress, dark masterpieces with your  personal style will echo, creating the most chilling atmosphere.</span></p><h2>More Sprunki, More Excitement!</h2><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-777\">Sprunki Phase 777</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px;\"><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-phase-5\">Sprunki Phase 5</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Phase 11','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-phase-11','','','2026-07-20 06:13:57','2026-07-20 06:13:57','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-phase-11/',0,'game','',0),(492,1,'2026-07-20 06:13:59','2026-07-20 06:13:59','','sprunki-dash-2-0','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-dash-2-0','','','2026-07-20 06:13:59','2026-07-20 06:13:59','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-dash-2-0.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(493,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:00','2026-07-20 06:14:00','','Sprunki Dash 2.0','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-dash-2-0-2','','','2026-07-20 06:14:00','2026-07-20 06:14:00','',494,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-dash-20.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(494,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:00','2026-07-20 06:14:00','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Dash 2.0</strong> opens the thrilling world of musical creativity and <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/rhythm.games\">rhythm</a> adventures. This music game introduces the appearance of unique elements of the popular game <strong>Geometry Dash</strong>. You will encounter adorable cubes on the screen with the role of music players instead of <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> characters. Are you ready for this exotic coordination? Enter the game, blend the music, and craft unique masterpieces immediately!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-dash-2-0.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"366\"></span></p><h3>Explore Fresh Features</h3><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>This game is a perfect fusion of the Sprunki Incredibox music game and the popular series Geometry Dash.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>Players can endlessly express their talents through more than 20 music icons.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>You have the chance to encounter hilarious characters in both horror and normal modes.</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span>This game encourages community with sharing features that mean you can share your creation with other players.</span></li></ul><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>As you enter <strong>Sprunki Dash 2.0</strong>, you will encounter seven cube-shaped characters on the screen with hilarious faces. The characters remain motionless with smiles, eagerly awaiting your contribution to create a chaotic atmosphere. To create songs, you show off your music ability, combining sounds by dragging boxes onto the characters. Each combination will showcase your music talents and the evidence for your creativity.</span></p><h2>Love Sprunki? Play More Like It!</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-2\">Sprunki 2</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/\">Sprunki Game</a></li></ul>','Sprunki Dash 2.0','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-dash-2-0','','','2026-07-20 06:14:00','2026-07-20 06:14:00','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-dash-2-0/',0,'game','',0),(495,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:02','2026-07-20 06:14:02','','sprunki-murder-drones-2','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-murder-drones-2','','','2026-07-20 06:14:02','2026-07-20 06:14:02','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-murder-drones-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(496,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:03','2026-07-20 06:14:03','','Sprunki Murder Drones','','inherit','open','closed','','sprunki-murder-drones-3','','','2026-07-20 06:14:04','2026-07-20 06:14:04','',497,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-murder-drones.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(497,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:04','2026-07-20 06:14:04','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Murder Drones</strong> is an intriguing creation game that brings a quirky and chaotic character from Murder Drones to the music world. This game delivers exhilarating rhythm-based challenges, creating a unique and wild musical experience. Players have the chance to play the role of a musician to compose the most immersive soundtracks with their own style. Dive into the game and embark on your music journey now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-murder-drones-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"441\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Sprunki Murder Drones</strong>, like most <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> games, allows you to showcase your musical skills through drag-and-drop mechanics. This means players need to drag music icons from the bottom of the screen to style the seven characters on it. As you experiment with different combinations, you\'ll discover unique melodies and rhythms that reflect your personal flair.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Two Exciting Modes</h3><ul style=\"padding-left: 24px; margin: 0 0 10px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Normal mode introduces seven humanoid figures with black, featureless heads and glowing white eyes on the screen. Your mission is to customize them with delightful melodies to create beautiful soundtracks. In the mode, you\'ll find several characters with the same white appearance, each with a different sound after customization.</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: justify; font-weight: 400;\"><span>Horror mode showcases several differences. The initial character will be the original Sprunki, standing motionless on the stage. Like the normal mode, there are several music boxes sharing the same looks. However, during that period, your character will remain unchanged in the absence of any echoed music.</span></li></ul>','Sprunki Murder Drones','','private','open','closed','','sprunki-murder-drones','','','2026-07-20 06:14:04','2026-07-20 06:14:04','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/sprunki-murder-drones/',0,'game','',0),(498,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:06','2026-07-20 06:14:06','','scream-sprunki-2','','inherit','open','closed','','scream-sprunki-2','','','2026-07-20 06:14:06','2026-07-20 06:14:06','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/scream-sprunki-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(499,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:07','2026-07-20 06:14:07','','Scream Sprunki','','inherit','open','closed','','scream-sprunki-3','','','2026-07-20 06:14:07','2026-07-20 06:14:07','',500,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/scream-sprunki.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(500,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:07','2026-07-20 06:14:07','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Scream Sprunki</strong> is a delightful arcade game that throws you into an exhilarating jumping journey. You will accompany an exciting character from the <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki.games\">Sprunki</a> universe, Oren. The mission is to guide you to conquer the tricky track and reach the destination without falling into the water or colliding. Oren is waiting for your arrival! Dive into this platformer game and start your journey now!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/scream-sprunki-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"481\" height=\"687\"></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Step into <strong>Scream Sprunki</strong>, and players will encounter Oren standing on a platform in the middle of the digital sea. It is your responsibility to steer your character towards the completion line. As you progress, you will encounter numerous challenges, including sharp skills, broken bridges, fish, and more. Players have to make sure that their characters jump high enough to reach the next platform safely. If you accidentally fail to pass any obstacles, you lose the level and have to start over. Additionally, to make the journey more engaging, players can gather rewards, which are oranges scattered on the platform. </span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Control Your Characters</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>This platform game introduces players to two main ways to guide Oren: click and voice. With the click mechanic, you maneuver Oren with the mouse to jump from platform to platform. The voice mechanic, on the other hand, lets you control your character by screaming loudly.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Other Arcade Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-launch\">Sprunki Launch</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/endless-sprunki\">Endless Sprunki</a></li></ul>','Scream Sprunki','','private','open','closed','','scream-sprunki','','','2026-07-20 06:14:07','2026-07-20 06:14:07','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/scream-sprunki/',0,'game','',0),(501,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:09','2026-07-20 06:14:09','','dandy-and-barry-police-2','','inherit','open','closed','','dandy-and-barry-police-2','','','2026-07-20 06:14:09','2026-07-20 06:14:09','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/dandy-and-barry-police-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(502,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:10','2026-07-20 06:14:10','','Dandy and Barry Police','','inherit','open','closed','','dandy-and-barry-police-3','','','2026-07-20 06:14:10','2026-07-20 06:14:10','',503,'https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/dandy-and-barry-police.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(503,1,'2026-07-20 06:14:10','2026-07-20 06:14:10','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span><strong>Dandy and Barry Police</strong> is a hilarious <a href=\"https://musicgames.io/casual.games\">casual</a> game that transports you into the thrilling escape adventure. Players will guide a criminal named Dandy to find the brilliant way to escape from the tight jail. Will you be able to avoid the guard watching over the bars outside and successfully escape?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/dandy-and-barry-police-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\"></span></p><h3>A Intriguing Storyline</h3><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Dandy is a criminal being held under the strict supervision of a police officer, Barry. Dandy intends to escape from the prison, but the policeman is always guarding outside the bards with his powerful weapon. To escape that surveillance, your character needs the support. Your control skills and patience will be the key to help him find freedom!</span></p><h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The mission in <strong>Dandy and Barry Police</strong> is simple: guide Dandy escape from the jail within as quickly as possible. To do that, players use the arrow keys to control their character moving around the prison and find the intelligent ways. This game will offer you directional arrows on the digital floor and the wall. Players need to follow these instructions to dodge the guard and successfully complete the mission.</span></p><h2>Casual Games</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/sprunki-bubble-pop\">Sprunki Bubble Pop</a></li><li><a href=\"https://musicgames.io/squid-sprunki-game-2\">Squid Sprunki Game 2</a></li></ul>','Dandy and Barry Police','','private','open','closed','','dandy-and-barry-police','','','2026-07-20 06:14:10','2026-07-20 06:14:10','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/game/dandy-and-barry-police/',0,'game','',0);
